hadiths[959]{hadithnumber,text}:
564,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab kabeera gunahon se bacha jaey to paanch namazein , ek Juma sey doosrey Juma tak aur ek Ramazan sey doosrey Ramazan tak honey waley sagheera gunahon ka kaffara hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
565,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey bataao agar tum mein se kisi shakhs ke ghar ke samney nehar ho aur wo her roz is mein paanch martaba ghusl karta ho to kya uskey jism par koi mail baqi reh jaeyga? '' Sahaba ne arz kya, uskey jism par koi mail baqi nahin rahega, aapney farmaya : ''yehi paanch Namazon ki misal hai, Allah unke zariey khataeyn mita deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
566,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi aadmi ne kisi aurat ka bosa ley liya phir usney aa kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya, to Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai: '' din ke dono atraaf aur raat ki chand ghadiyon mein Namaz padha karen, yaqinan nekiyan buraiyon ko door kar deti hain.'' us aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye merey liye khas hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri sari ummat ke liye hai.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : '' jisney meri ummat mein se is par amal kya. '' muttafaq aleh."
567,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi aaya, usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main wo amal kar baitha hun jis par had (saza) wajib ho jati hai, lihaza aap mujhey saza dein. raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se us ( amal (ke mutalliq kuch daryaft na kya, itney mein Namaz ka waqt ho gaya, to usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi , jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ada kar chukey to wo aadmi khada hua aur arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main ( ne aisa kaam kya hai ke) had ko pahunch chuka hun, lihaza aap merey mutalliq Allah ka hukm nafiz farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne hamarey sath Namaz nahin padhi ?'' usney arz kya, ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne tumharey gunah ya tumhari had ko maaf farma diya .'' muttafaq aleh."
568,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke Allah ko kon sa amal sab se ziyada mehbub hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' waqt par Namaz ada karna.'' maine arz kya, phir kon sa ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' waliden se achcha sulook karna.'' maine arz kya, phir kon sa ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein jihad karna.'' ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, aapney mujhey ye baaten bataain, agar main mazeed daryaft karta to aap mujhey aur ziyada batatey . muttafaq aleh."
569,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( momin ( bandey aur kufr ke darmiyan farq Namaz ka tarak karna hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
570,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ne paanch namazein farz ki hain, jis shakhs ne unke liye achi tarah wuzu kya, unhen unke waqt par ada kya, aur unke rukoo w khushu ko mukammal kya to Allah ka uskey liye ehad hai ke wo usey maaf farma dega aur jisney aisey na kya to us se Allah ka koi ehad nahin, agar wo chahey to usey maaf farma dey , aur agar chahey to usey saza dey .'' Ahmed, Abu-Dawood . jabkey Malik aur Imam Nasai ne bhi uski manind riwayat kya hai."
571,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni paanch ( farz ( namazein padho , apney maah ( Ramazan (ke rozey rakho , apney amwaal ki zakat do , aur ameer ki itaat karo to is tarah tum apney rab ki jannat mein dakhil ho jaaogey .'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
572,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumharey bachey saat baras ke ho jaeyn to unhen Namaz ke mutalliq hukm do , aur jab wo das baras ke ho jaeyn (aur wo is mein kotahi karen ( to unhen is par saza do , aur unke bistar alag kar do .'' Abu-Dawud, aur Sharahus-sunnah mein bhi is tarah riwayat kya hai."
573,Hazrat masaabeh mein sabra bin mabad (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai.
574,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hamarey aur un (munafiq) ke beech Namaz ehad hai pas jisney usey tarak kya to usney kufr kya. '' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
575,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine Madina ke doosrey kinarey eik aurat se tabiat aazmaai ki, maine jima ke ilawa uskey sath sab kuch kya, chunanche main hazir hun, aap merey mutalliq jo chahen faisla farmaeyn, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey kaha, Allah ne tumhari parda-poshi ki thi kaash! ke tum bhi apni parda poshii kartey, raawi bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey koi jawab na diya, aur wo aadmi khada hua aur chala gaya, chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi aadmi ko uskey peechey bheja to usey bula kar ye aayat sunai : ''din ke dono atraaf aur raat ki chand ghadiyon mein Namaz padha karen, yaqinan nekiyan buraiyon ko door kar deti hain aur ye nasihat qubul karney walon ke liye nasihat hai.'' haazirin mein se kisi ne arz kya : Allah ke Nabi ! ye uskey liye khas hai? to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, balke tamam logon ke liye hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
576,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mausame-khizaan mein bahar tashrif laye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do shaakhon ko pakda, raawi ne bayan kya ke pattey girney lagey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : ''aey abu-Zar! maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! hazir hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beshak musalman banda Allah ki raza ke liye Namaz padhta hai to us se gunah aisey jhad jatey hain jaisey us darkht se pattey girtey hain.''"
577,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs huzure-qalb se do rakatein padhta hai to Allah uskey sabiqa gunah maaf farma deta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
578,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik roz Namaz ka zikr kartey huey farmaya : ''jisney Namaz ki hifazat w pabandi ki to wo us shakhs ke liye roze-qiyamat Noor, daleel aur najat hogi, aur jisney uski hifazat w pabandi na ki to roze-qiyamat uskey liye Noor, daleel aur najat nahin hogi aur wo Qarun , Firon, Haman aur Ubai bin khalaf ke sath hoga .'' ( rawahu Ahmed w Darmi w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
579,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaqiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba aamaal mein sirf tarake-Namaz ko kufr tasawwur kya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi ."
580,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, merey khaleel ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ne mujhey wasiyat farmaai ke Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek na banana chaahey tumhen tukdey-tukdey kar diya jaey aur chaahey tumhen jala diya jaey, aur jaan-bojh kar farz Namaz tarak na karna, jisney jaan-boojhkar usey tarak kar diya to us se zimma uth gaya, aur sharab na peena kyonkey wo tamam buraiyon ki chaabi hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
581,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' namaze-Zohar ka waqt , zawal aaftaab se shuru hota hai aur aadmi ka saya uskey qad ke barabar ho janey aur Asr ka waqt na honey tak rehta hai, aur Asr ka waqt Suraj ke zard ho janey se pehley tak rehta hai, aur maghrib ka waqt shafaq ( ghurub aaftaab ke baad ufuq par jo surkhi hoti hai) ke rehney tak rehta hai, aur Isha ka waqt nisf shab tak rehta hai jabkey namaze-Fajr ka waqt tulu Fajr se tulu aaftaab se pehley tak rehta hai, aur jab Suraj tulu honey lagey to phir Namaz na padho kyonkey wo shetan ke seengon ke darmiyan se tulu hota hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
582,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi aadmi ne namazon ke oqaat ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''tum do din hamarey sath Namaz padho .'' jab Suraj dhal gaya to aapney Bilal ko hukm farmaya to unhoney Azan di, phir aapney hukm diya to unhoney iqaamat kahi , phir aapney unhen hukm diya to unhoney Asr ke liye iqaamat kahi jabkey Suraj buland, saaf aur chamakdaar tha, phir aapney unhen hukm diya to unhoney Suraj ghurub ho janey par maghrib ke liye iqaamat kahi, aur phir jab shafaq ghayeb ho gaee to aapney unhen Namaz Isha ke liye iqaamat kehney ka hukm farmaya, phir jab Fajr tulu ho gaee to aapney unhen namaze-Fajr ke liye iqaamat kehney ka hukm farmaya, doosrey roz aapney unhen Zohar ko thanda karney ka hukm farmaya to unhoney usey khub muakhkhar kya, aapney Asr padhi jabkey Suraj buland tha, aapney guzishta roz se usey muakhkhar kya, aapney shafaq ghayeb ho janey se pehley maghrib padhi aur tihai raat guzar janey ke baad Isha padhi, aur Fajr, tulu Fajr ke roshan ho janey par padhi, phir farmaya : ''namazon ke oqaat malum karney wala shakhs kahan hai? ''to us aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! main hazir hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhari namazon ka waqt un oqaat ke beech hai jis ka tum mulaahaza kar chukey ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
583,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne Baitullah ke qarib mujhey do martaba Namaz padhaai (eik martaba) jab Suraj tasme ke barabar dhal gaya to unhoney mujhey Zohar padhaai, aur jab her chiz ka saya us (chiz) ke misl ho gaya to unhoney mujhey Asr padhaai, jis waqt roze daar iftaar karta hai us waqt mujhey maghrib padhaai, aur shafaq khatam ho janey par mujhey Isha padhaai, aur jis waqt roze daar par khana-peena haram ho jata hai us waqt mujhey Fajr padhaai. pas aglaa roz hua to unhoney mujhey Zohar us waqt padhaai jab her chiz ka saya us (chiz) ke misl ho gaya, aur jab her chiz ka saya do misl ho gaya to mujhey Asr padhaai, aur jis waqt roze daar iftaar karta hai us waqt mujhey maghrib padhaai, aur tihai raat guzarney par mujhey Isha padhaai, aur subh roshan ho janey par namaze-Fajr padhaai, phir wo meri taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : Muhammad ! (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye aap se pehley Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) ka waqt hai aur namazon ka waqt unhi do oqaat ke beech hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
584,"Hazrat ibne-Shahab ( Zohri (rh) ( se riwayat hai ke umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Raziallahu anhu) ne namaze-Asr mein kuch takheer ki to Urwa (bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu)) ne unhen kaha : aagah raho ke Jibrael (Alaihissalam) tashrif laye to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aagey Namaz padhi , to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Urwa ! tumhen pata hona chahiye ke tum kya kar rahey ho, unhoney kaha : maine Bashir bin abi Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna, unhoney kaha maine abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' Jibrael (Alaihissalam) tashrif laye to unhoney meri imaamat karaai , to maine unke sath Namaz padhi , phir maine unke sath (dusri ( Namaz padhi , phir maine unke sath Namaz padhi , phir maine unke sath Namaz padhi , phir maine unke sath Namaz padhi .'' yun paanch dafa apni ungliyon par shumar kya. muttafaq aleh."
585,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aapney apney ameeron (governors) ke naam khat likha ke merey nazdik tumhara sab se aham kaam Namaz hai, jisney uski hifazat w pabandi ki usney apney Deen ki hifazat ki, aur jisney usey zaya kya to phir wo uskey ilawa Deen ki dusri baaton ko ziyada zaya karney wala hai, phir aapney likha ke namaze-Zohar ka waqt ye hai ke saya eik haath ho aur ye us waqt tak rehta hai ke tum mein se her eik ka saya us ( aadmi (ke saye ke barabar ho jaey, aur namaze-Asr ka waqt ye hai ke Suraj buland , safed aur chamak daar ho aur itna waqt ho ke Sawar ghurub aaftaab se pehley do ya teen farsakh ( taqriban 10 ya 15 kilometre) ka fasla tey kar sakey, aur namaze-Maghrib ka waqt wo hai jab Suraj ghurub ho jaey, aur Namaz Isha ka waqt shafaq khatam honey se shuru hota hai aur tihai raat tak rehta hai, pas jo shakhs so jaey to (Allah karey) uski aankh ko aaram hasil na ho, jo shakhs so jaey to uski aankh ko aaram hasil na ho, jo so jaey to ( Allah karey ( uski aankh ko aaram hasil na ho aur subh ka waqt wo hai ke jab subh saadiq ho jaey lekin sitarey abhi numaya hun. rawahu Malik."
586,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) garmi key mausam mein namaze-Zohar us waqt padhtey they jab aadmi ka saya teen qadam se paanch qadam tak hota jabkey sardi key mausam mein saya paanch se saat qadam tak hota. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
587,"Hazrat Sayyar bin Salama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main aur merey walid abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey to merey walid ne un se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki farz Namaz ki keyfiyat ke barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : aap namaze-Zohar, jisey tum pehli Namaz kehtey ho, us waqt padha kartey they jab Suraj dhal jata, aap namaze-Asr padhtey to phir ham mein se koi Madina ke aakhiri kinarey waqey apni rihaaish gaah par wapis jata to Suraj bilkul safed aur chamak daar hota tha, raawi bayan kartey hain, main maghrib ke barey mein bhool gaya ke unhoney kya kaha tha, aur jab aap Namaze-Isha jisey tum ( عَتَمَہ ( kehtey ho, ko takheer se padhna pasand farmatey they, aap us (Namaz Isha) se pehley so jana aur uskey baad baaten karna, na pasand farmatey they, aur aap namaze-Fajr mein salam pher kar namaaziyon ki taraf rukh farmatey to us waqt her namazi apney sath waley namazi ko pehchan leta tha, aur aap saath se so aayaat tak tilawat farmaya kartey they. aur eik riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Alaihissalam) Namaz Isha ko tihai raat tak baghair kisi parwah ke muakhkhar kar diya kartey they. aur aap Namaz Isha se pehley sona aur uskey baad baaten karney ko na pasand kya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
588,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Amr bin Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namazon ke barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : aap namaze-Zohar zawal aaftaab ke fauran baad jabkey Asr us waqt padhtey jab Suraj khub roshan aur chamak daar hota, aur maghrib us waqt padhtey jab Suraj ghurub ho jata, jabkey Isha ke barey mein aisey tha ke jab log ziyada ikhattey ho jatey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jaldi padh letey aur jab namazi kam hotey to usey takheer se padhtey aur Fajr ki Namaz taareeki mein padha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
589,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey namaze-Zohar padha kartey they to ham garmi se bachney ke liye apney kapdon par (sar rakh kar) sajda kya kartey they. Bukhari, Muslim, aur mazkura alfaz sahih Bukhari ke hain. muttafaq aleh."
590,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab garmi shadeed ho to phir Namaz ( Zohar ( padhney mein takheer karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
591,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se Zohar ke mutalliq Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai : '' kyonkey garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki bhap ki wajeh se hai, jahannam ne apney rab se shikayat kartey huey arz kya, merey rab! merey baaz hissey ne baaz ko kha liya, chunanche Allah Taala ne usey do saans, eik saans mausame-sarma mein aur eik saans mausame-garma mein, leney ki ijazat farmaey, tum jo ziyada garmi aur ziyada sardi paatey ho wo usi wajeh se hai.'' Bukhari, Muslim. muttafaq aleh. aur Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai, ''pas tum jo garmi ki shiddat paatey ho to wo uski garm hua ki wajeh se hai, aur tum jo ziyada sardi paatey ho to wo uski thandak ki wajeh se hai.''"
592,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Asr padha kartey they jabkey Suraj buland chamak daar hota tha, janey wala shakhs (namaze-Asr masjide-nabawi mein ada karney ke baad) '' awaalii '' ( Madina ki aas-paas bastiyon mein) jata to Suraj buland hota, aur baaz bastiyan Madina se taqriban chaar mail ki masafat par thin. muttafaq aleh."
593,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye munafiq shakhs ki Namaz hai jo beth kar Suraj ka intizar karta rehta hai yahan tak ke jab wo zard aur shetan ke seengon ke beech pahunchney ke qarib ho jata hai to wo khada ho kar chaar thongein maarta hai aur un mein Allah Taala ka bahut kam zikr karta hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
594,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ki namaze-Asr faut ho gaee to goya uska ghar-baar lut gaya.'' muttafaq aleh."
595,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne namaze-Asr tarak kar di to uska amal zaya ho gaya.'' Bukhari ."
596,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath maghrib padha kartey they, to ham mein se koi wapis jata to wo apney teer ke girney ki jagah ko dekh leta tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
597,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Sahaba kiram ghurub shafaq aur raat ke tihai awwal ke beech Namaz Isha padha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
598,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-Fajr padhtey to khawatin apni chaadaron mein lipti hui wapis jatin aur wo taareeki ki wajeh se pehchani nahin jati thin. muttafaq aleh."
599,"Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Zaid bin Sabit ne sehri khai, pas jab wo apni sehri khaney se farigh huey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ke liye khadey huey to aapney Namaz padhaai, ham ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : unke sehri kha kar Namaz shuru karney ke beech kitney waqt ka waqfa tha? unhoney farmaya : jitney waqt mein aadmi pachas aayaat ki tilawat kar leta hai. Bukhari ."
600,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum par aisey ameer hongey jo namazein zaya karengey ya farmaya : wo namazon ko un waqton se muakhkhar (deri) karengey to us waqt tumhari kya keyfiyat hogi ?'' maine arz kya : aap mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Namaz ko uskey waqt par padhna , aur agar tum unke sath bhi pa lo to phir ( Namaz ( padh lo, to wo tumharey liye bataur nafl hogi.'' rawahu Muslim ."
601,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne tulu aaftaab se pehley namaze-Fajr ki eik rakat pa li to usney namaze-Fajr pa li, aur jisney ghurub aaftaab se pehley, namaze-Asr ki eik rakat pa li to usney namaze-Asr pa li.'' muttafaq aleh."
602,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi ghurub aaftaab se pehley namaze-Asr ki eik rakat pa ley to wo apni Namaz mukammal karey, aur jab wo tulu aaftaab se pehley namaze-Fajr ki eik rakat pa ley to wo apni Namaz mukammal karey.'' Bukhari ."
603,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs koi Namaz padhna bhool jaey ya wo us waqt so jaey to uska kaffara ye hai ke jab yad aaye usey padh ley.'' muttafaq aleh. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' us (Namaz padh leney) ke siwa uska koi kaffara nahin .''"
604,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haalate-neend mein) Namaz mein takheer ho janey par) koi taqseer w gunah nahin, taqseer to mehaz haalate-bedaari mein (Namaz muakhkhar karney mein) hai, jab tum mein se koi shakhs Namaz padhna bhool jaey ya wo us waqt so jaey to jab usey yad aaye padh ley.'' kyonkey Allah Taala ne farmaya : ''mujhey yad karney ke liye Namaz padha karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
605,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Ali! teen chizon mein takheer na karna , eik Namaz jab uska waqt aa jaey, janaza jab tayyar ho jaey aur bewa, mutallaqa aur kanwari khatoon (ke nikah mein) jab tumhen uska kufu mil jaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
606,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''awwal waqt Namaz padhna Allah ki razamandi aur aakhir waqt Allah ke afu darguzar ka baais hai.''"
607,"Hazrat umme-Farwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se afzal amal ke barey mein puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''awwal waqt mein Namaz ada karna.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood . Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees sirf Abdullah (bin Hafs bin Aasim bin umr bin Khattab madni) se marwi (bayan) hai, aur wo muhaddeseen ke yahan qawi nahin."
608,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni puri zindagi mein sirf do martaba Namaz ko aakhir waqt mein padha hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
609,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat hamesha khair w bhalai par rahegi.'' ya farmaya : ''fitrat par rahegi, jab tak wo sitarey zahir honey se pehley namaze-Maghrib padhti rahegi.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
610,Darmi ne usey Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai.
611,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar mujhey apni ummat par mashaqqat ka andesha na hota to main unhen, Namaz Isha ko tihai raat ya aadhi raat tak muakhkhar karney ka hukm farmata .'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
612,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us Namaz (yani Isha ( ko der se padho , kyonkey uski wajeh se tumhen deegar ummaton par fazilat di gaee hai, tum se pehley kisi ummat ne ye Namaz nahin padhi .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
613,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main us Namaz yani Namaz ishaa ke waqt ke barey mein khub janta hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) teesri raat ke chaand ke ghurub honey ke waqt usey padha kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Darmi ."
614,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' namaze-Fajr , roshan ho janey par padho kyonkey wo ziyada baaise-ajr hai.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Darmi , Nasai mein ye alfaz nahin : '' ke wo ziyada baais ajr hai.'' ."
615,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath namaze-Asr ada kartey, phir oont nahar kya jata, uskey das hissey kiye jatey , phir usey pakaaya jata to ham ghuroobe-aaftab se pehley pakka hua gosht kha letey they. muttafaq aleh."
616,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik raat ham Namaz Isha ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka intizar kar rahey they, pas aap tihai raat guzar janey ya uskey baad tashrif laye, ham nahin jantey ke kisi kaam ne aap ko apney ehle-khana mein masroof rakha ya uskey ilawa koi kaam tha, pas jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (apney hujrey sey) bahar tashrif laye to farmaya : ''tum Namaz ka intizar kar rahey ho, tumharey ilawa koi ehle-deen uska intizar nahin kar raha, agar ummat ke liye giraan na hota mein unhen usi waqt padhata.'' phir aapney muazzan ko hukm diya to usney iqaamat kahi aur aapney Namaz padhaai . rawahu Muslim ."
617,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhari namazon ke oqaat ke mutabiq hi namazein padha kartey they, lekin aap Namaz Isha tumhari Namaz se kuch takheer se padha kartey they, aur aap Namaz halki padhaya kartey they. rawahu Muslim."
618,"Hazrat abu Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz Isha padhney ka irada kya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) taqriban aadhi raat guzar janey ke baad tashrif laye to farmaya : ''apni jagah par bethey raho.'' chunanche ham apni jagah par beth gaey, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be shak log Namaz padh kar so chukey, aur jabke tum us waqt tak Namaz hi mein rahogey jab tak tum Namaz ke intizar mein rahogey aur agar zaeef ke zauf, bimar ki bimari ka andesha na hota to main us Namaz ko aadhi raat tak muakhkhar karta.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
619,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, namaze-Zohar jald padhney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tum se ziyada sakht they aur namaze-Asr jaldi padhney main tum un se ziyada sakht ho.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
620,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye mamool tha ke garmi hoti to aap Namaz ( Zohar ( der se padhtey aur jab sardi hoti to jaldi farmatey they. rawahu Nasai ."
621,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''merey baad tumharey kuch aisey ameer hongey ke chand chizen unhen waqt par Namaz padhney se ghafil kar dengi yahan tak ke uska waqt guzar jaeyga chunanche ( jab ye soorate-haal ho to) tum namazein waqt par ada karna.'' kisi shakhs ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya main unke sath bhi padh lun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
622,"Hazrat Qabisa bin Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey baad tumharey kuch aisey hukmran hongey jo namazein der se padhengey, chunanche wo tumharey liye baaise-sawab aur unke liye gunah ki wajah hongi, pas jab tak wo qibla rukh namazein padhtey rahen to tum unke sath Namaz padho.''"
623,"Hazrat Ubaidullah bin Adi bin khiyaar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey jabkey wo mehsoor they, to unhoney kaha : aap ameerul-momeneen hain aur aap pareshani mein mubtala hain, jabkey fitney ka sarghana hamen Namaz padhata hai, aur ham usey gunah samajhtey hain, unhon (Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : Namaz musalmanon ka behtareen amal hai, jab log achcha kaam karen, to tum bhi unke sath mil kar achcha karo, aur jab wo bura karen to tum unki burai se door raho. Bukhari ."
624,"Hazrat Umara bin Rubiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs tulue-aaftab se pehley aur ghurub aaftab se pehley yani Fajr aur namaze-Asr padhey to wo jahannam mein nahin jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim ."
625,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs do thandi namazein (Fajr w asr) padhega wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
626,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' raat aur din ke waqt farishtey eik baad eik tumharey paas aatey rehtey hain aur wo namaze-Fajr aur namaze-Asr mein ikatthey hotey hain, phir wo farishtey, jinhon ne tumharey yahan raat basar ki hoti hai, ooper chadhtey hain, unka rab un se poochhta hai, halanke wo unke mutalliq behtar janta hai, tum ne merey bandon ko kis haal (yani aakhiri amal ( par chhod kar aaye ho? wo arz kartey hain, jab ham unke paas se aaye to wo us waqt Namaz padh rahey they, aur jab unke paas gaey they tab bhi wo Namaz padh rahey they.'' muttafaq aleh."
627,"Hazrat Jundub Qasri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs namaze-Fajr padh leta hai to wo Allah ke ahde-aman mein aa jata hai, chunanche tum aisa koi kaam na karna jiski wajeh se Allah apney ahde-aman ke barey mein tumhari pakad karey, kyonkey wo apney ahdo-aman ke barey mein jis shakhs ki pakad kerega to wo usey pakad kar ondhey munh jahannam mein dal dega. muttafaq aleh. aur Masaabeh ke baaz nuskhon mein al-Qasri ke bajaey al-Qusheiri mazkur hai."
628,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar log Azan aur saf awwal ki fazilat ke barey mein jaan lein phir agar unhen uskey husool ke liye qura-andazi kerni padey to wo zarur qura andazi karen, aur agar wo Namaz ke liye jaldi aaney ki fazilat ke barey mein jaan lein to wo uski taraf zarur sabqat hasil karen, aur agar unhen Namaz Isha aur namaze-Fajr ki ahmiyat ka pataa chal jaey to wo unhen padhney ke liye zarur (masjid mein) ayen chaahey unhen peeth ya paaon aur ghutnon ke bal chal kar aana padey.'' muttafaq aleh."
629,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''namaze-Fajr aur Namaze-Isha munafiqon par sab se ziyada bhari namazein hain, lekin agar unhen unke ajr w sawab ka pata chal jaey to wo unhen padhney ke liye zarur (masjid mein) ayen, chaahey unhen peeth ya paaon aur ghutnon ke bal chal kar aana padey.'' muttafaq aleh."
630,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Namaz Isha ba-jamaat ada ki to goya usney aadhi raat ka qiyam kya aur jisney Namaze-subh ba-jamaat ada ki to goya usney puri raat ka qiyam kya. '' rawahu Muslim ."
631,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dehati log, tumhari namaze-Maghrib ke naam ke barey mein, tum par ghalib na aa jaeyn.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : dehati usey Isha ke naam se jaantey hain."
632,"aur farmaya : '' dehati log, tumhari Isha ke naam ke barey main tum par ghalib na aa jaeyn, kyonkey uska naam to Allah Taala ki kitab mein Isha hai, kyonkey wo oonton ka doodh dohney ki wajeh se usey utma kehtey hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
633,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwa khandaq ke roz farmaya : '' unhoney hamen namaze-Asr se rok diya, Allah unke gharon aur unki qabron ko aag se bhar dey .'' muttafaq aleh."
634,"Hazrat ibne-Masood aur Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' darmiyani Namaz se murad namaze-Asr hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
635,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Allah Taala ke farman : '' be-shak namaze-Fajr ka padhna ( farishton ki) haziri ka waqt hai.'' ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo raat aur din ke farishton ki haziri ka waqt hai.'' sahih rawahu Tirmizi ."
636,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan kartey hain, darmiyan wali Namaz se murad namaze-Zohar hai. Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne un dono se muallaq riwayat kya hai."
637,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-Zohar bahut jald padha kartey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba par sab se ziyada mashaqqat wali Namaz yehi thi, pas ye aayat nazil hui '' namazon ki pabandi w hifazat karo aur bil-khusus Namazw-wusta ki .'' raawi ne kaha : kyonkey us se pehley bhi do namazein hain, aur uskey baad bhi do namazein hain. rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood."
638,Hazrat Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhen Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutalliq pata chala ke wo kaha kartey they ke darmiyan wali Namaz se murad namaze-Fajr hai.
639,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se usey muallaq riwayat kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi .
640,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs namaze-Fajr ke liye jata hai to wo eman ka parcham utha kar jata hai, aur jo shakhs baazar ki taraf jata hai, to wo iblees ka parcham utha kar jata hai.''"
641,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kuch Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( aelan Namaz ke liye ( aag jalaney aur naaqus bajaney ka zikr kya aur baaz Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne yahood w Nasara (se mushaabihat (ka zikr kya, to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya gaya ke wo kalmaate-azaan do-do martaba aur kalmaate-iqaamat eik-eik martaba kahen. muttafaq aleh. Ismail bayan kartey hain, maine Ayub se is hadees ka zikr kya to unhoney farmaya : magar ( قد قامت الصلٰوۃ) ke alfaz do martaba kahey."
642,"Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khud mujhey Azan sikhai chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kaho : Allah sab se bada hai, Allah sab se bada hai, Allah sab se bada hai, Allah sab se bada hai, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, mein gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, phir tum dobara kaho : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, mein gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, Namaz ki taraf aao Namaz ki taraf aao, falah w kamiyabi ki taraf aao, falah w kamiyabi ki taraf aao, Allah sab se bada hai, Allah sab se bada hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin.'' rawahu Muslim ."
643,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein Azan ke kalmaat do do martaba aur iqaamat ke kalmaat (قد قامت الصلٰوۃ) (قد قامت الصلٰوۃ) ke siwa eik eik martaba they.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai w Darmi ."
644,Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Azan ke Unais kalmaat aur iqaamat ke satrah kalmaat sikhaey . rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w Darmi w ibne-Maja .
645,"Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khud mujhey Azan sikhai chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kaho : Allah sab se bada hai, Allah sab se bada hai, Allah sab se bada hai, Allah sab se bada hai, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, mein gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, phir tum dobara kaho : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, mein gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, apni aawaz buland karo, Namaz ki taraf aao Namaz ki taraf aao, falah w kamiyabi ki taraf aao, falah w kamiyabi ki taraf aao, Allah sab se bada hai, Allah sab se bada hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin.''"
646,"Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' namaze-Fajr ( ki Azan (ke ilawa kisi Namaz ( ki Azan ( mein (الصلوٰۃ خیر من النوم) na kehna.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : abu-Israel raawi muhaddeseen ke nazdik qawi nahin."
647,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''jab tum Azan kaho to thehar-thehar kar itminan ke sath kaho, aur jab iqaamat kaho to jaldi jaldi kaho, aur apni Azan aur iqaamat ke darmiyan itna waqfa rakho ke khana khaney wala shakhs apney khaney sey, peeney wala shakhs apney mashrub se jabkey qazaey-hajat ke liye janey wala shakhs apni hajat se farigh ho jaey, aur jab tak mujhey dekh na lo Namaz ke liye khadey na hua karo.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ham usey sirf Abdul-Mun-im ki hadees se pehchantey hain, aur uski asnaad majhool hai."
648,"Hazrat Ziyad bin Haris sudaai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey Azan deney ka hukm farmaya to maine Azan di, to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne iqaamat kehney ka irada kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sudaa qabiley ke shakhs ne Azan di hai, aur jo Azan dey wohi iqaamat kahiye.''"
649,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab musalman Madina tashrif laye to wo ikhattey jatey aur Namaz ke waqt ka andaza lagatey jabkey Namaz ke liye koi manadi nahin karta tha, eik roz unhoney us barey mein baat cheet ki, to un mein se kisi ne kaha : nasaara jaisa naaqoos bana lo aur kisi ne kaha ke yahood ke seeng jaisa koi seeng bana lo, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : tum kisi aadmi ko kyon nahin bhej detey ke wo Namaz ke liye manadi karey, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Bilal! utho aur Namaz ke liye aawaz do.'' muttafaq aleh."
650,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid bin Abde-Rabba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon ko Namaz ke liye jama karney ke liye naaqoos bajaney ka hukm farmaya to maine khuwab main eik shakhs ko haath mein naaqoos uthaey huey dekha, maine kaha : Allah ke bandey ! kya tum naaqoos bechtey ho? usney kaha tum iska kya karogey? maine kaha : ham iskey zariey Namaz ke liye bulaeyngey, usney kaha : kya main tumhen isse behtar chiz na bataaun? maine kaha : kyon nahin, zarur bataao , raawi bayan kartey hain, usney kaha : tum Allahu-akbar se aakhir Azan tak kaho , aur isi tarah iqaamat , pas jab subh hui to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unhen apna khuwab sunaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : inshaAllah ye sacha khuwab hai, aap Bilal ke sath khadey hon aur aapney jo dekha hai wo Bilal ko sikha do , wo un kalmaat ke sath Azan dey , kyonkey uski aawaz aap se ziyada buland hai.'' chunanche main Bilal ke sath khada ho kar unhen Azan ke kalmaat sikhata raha aur wo unke sath Azan detey rahey, raawi bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne apney ghar mein Azan ki aawaz suni to wo apni chadar ghaseet'tey huey tashrif laye aur kehney lagey : Allah ke Rasool ! us zaat ki qism ! jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja , jo kuch unhen dikhaya gaya hai bilkul wohi kuch maine dekha hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka shukr hai.'' . Abu-Dawud, Darmi , ibne-Maja , albatta unhoney iqaamat ka zikr nahin kya, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai, lekin unhoney waqia naaqoos ki sarahat nahin ki ."
651,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main namaze-Fajr ke liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana hua to aap jis aadmi ke paas se guzartey to usey Namaz ke liye aawaz detey ya apney paaon ke sath usey hila detey ."
652,Hazrat Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhen pata chala ke muazzan umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko namaze-Fajr ki ittilaa karney aaya to usney unhen soyaa hua dekh kar kaha : '' Namaz neend se behtar hai.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey hukm farmaya ke un kalmaat ko subh ki Azan mein shamil kar lo.
653,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Saad bin Ammar bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey merey walid ne apney walid se aur usney Saad bin Ammar ke dada Saad bin Aaid jo ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan they ke hawaley se hadees bayan ki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kanon mein ungliyan dakhil karney ka hukm detey huey farmaya : '' us se tumhari aawaz ziyada buland ho jaeygi .''
654,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' qiyamat ke din , Muazzan hazraat ki gardanen sab se lambi hongi .'' rawahu Muslim ."
655,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Namaz ke liye Azan kahi jati hai to shetan hawa khaarij karta hua peeth pher kar bhag jata hai yahan tak ke wo Azan ki aawaz nahin sunta , pas jab Azan mukammal ho jati hai to wo wapis aa jata hai, aur phir jab Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi jati hai to wo peeth pher kar bhag jata hai, aur phir jab iqaamat mukammal ho jati hai to wo wapis aa jata hai, aur wo aadmi ke dil mein waswasey daalta hai, aur kehta hai : falan chiz yad kar , falan chiz yad kar , aisi baaten yad karata hai jo usey yad nahin thin yahan tak ke aadmi ki ye keyfiyat ho jati hai ke usey pata nahin chalta ke usney kitni rakatein padhi hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
656,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Muazzan ki aawaz ko jin w ins aur jo dusri chizen sunti hain wo (sab) qiyamat ke din uskey haq mein gawahi dengi.'' Bukhari."
657,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum Muazzan ko suno to tum bhi wohi kaho jo Muazzan kehta hai, phir mujh par durood padho, kyonkey jo shakhs mujh par eik martaba durood padhta hai to Allah is par das rahmatein nazil farmata hai, phir tum Allah se merey liye wasila talab karo, kyonkey wo jannat main eik maqam hai, jo Allah ke sirf eik bandey ke shayaane-shaan hai, main ummid karta hun ke wo mein hunga, chunanche jis shakhs ne merey liye wasile ki dua ki uskey liye meri shafaat wajib ho gaee.'' rawahu Muslim ."
658,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Muazzan kehta hai, Allahu-akbar ''Allah sab se bada hai, '' aur tum mein se bhi koi khulus qalb se Allahu-akbar kehta hai, phir wo kehta hai : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur wo shakhs bhi yehi kalmaat kehta hai, phir wo kehta hai : main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, aur wo shakhs bhi yehi kalmaat kehta hai, phir wo kehta hai : Namaz ki taraf aao, to wo shakhs kehta hai : لا حول wla quwwata الا باللہ ''gunah se bachna aur neki karna mehaz Allah ki taufeeq se hai. phir wo kehta hai : kamiyabi ki taraf aao, to wo shakhs kehta hai : لا حول wla quwwata الا باللہ phir wo kehta hai, Allahu-akbar, to wo shakhs bhi Allahu-akbar kehta hai, phir wo kehta hai : (la Ilaah illa Allah), to wo shakhs bhi kehta hai : (la Ilaah illa Allah) Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar haq nahin '' . to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga .'' rawahu Muslim ."
659,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Azan sun kar ye dua padhey : aey Allah ! is dawate-kamil aur qaaim honey wali Namaz ke rab ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wasila w fazilat ata farma , aur unhen maqame-Mehmood par faaiz farmaya, jiska tune un se wada farmaya hai, to uskey liye roze-qiyamat meri shafaat wajib ho jaeygi.'' Bukhari ."
660,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Fajr tulu ho jati to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamla kya kartey they, aur aap badey ghor se Azan sunney ki koshish kartey, agar aap Azan sun letey to hamla na kartey warna hamla kar detey, eik martaba aapney kisi shakhs ko ''Allah sab se bada hai, Allah sab se bada hai"" kehtey huey suna, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo shakhs fitrat ( Deen ( par hai.'' phir us shakhs ne kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum jahannam se azad ho gaey.'' pas Sahaba ne usey dekha to wo bakriyon ka charwaahaa tha. rawahu Muslim ."
661,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Azan sun kar ye kehta hai : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain, main Allah ke rab honey, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Rasool aur Islam ke Deen honey par razi hun, to uskey gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain. rawahu Muslim ."
662,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her do azaanon (azaan w iqaamat) ke darmiyan (nafl) Namaz hai, her do azaanon ke beech Namaz hai, phir teesri martaba farmaya : ''us shakhs ke liye jo padhna chahey.'' muttafaq aleh."
663,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Imam (Namaz ka ( nigehban hai jabkey Muazzan (oqaate-namaz ka ( amanat daar hai, aey Allah! imamon ki raahnumai farma aur Azan deney walon ki maghfirat farma.'' Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Shafai, aur Imam Shafai ki dusri riwayat masaabeh ke alfaz se marwi (bayan) hai."
664,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs sawab ki niyat se saat baras Azan deta hai to uskey liye jahannam se khulasi likh di jati hai.''"
665,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tera rab pahad ki choti par bakriyan charaney waley us shakhs se khush hota hai jo Namaz ke liye Azan kehta hai aur Namaz padhta hai, chunanche Allah azz-w-jall farmata hai : merey us bandey ko dekho, wo Azan kehta hai aur Namaz padhta hai, wo mujh se darta hai, maine apney bandey ko bakhsh diya aur usey jannat mein dakhil farma diya.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
666,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen ashkhas roze-qiyamat kastoori ke tilon par hongey, wo ghulam jisney Allah aur apney Malik ka haq ada kya, wo Imam jis se uskey muqtadi khush hon aur wo shakhs jo rozana paanchon namazon ke liye Azan deta hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
667,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Muazzan ko uski aawaz ke mutabiq maghfirat se nawaza jata hai, her khushk w tar uskey haq mein gawahi deti hai, aur Namaz ke liye aaney waley shakhs ke liye pachchis namazon ka sawab likha jata hai, aur us se do namazon ke beech honey waley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja . Imam Nasai ne '' her khushk w tar '' ke alfaz tak riwayat kya hai, aur farmaya : '' Namaz padhney waley ki misl usey bhi ajr milta hai.''"
668,"Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! mujhey meri qom ka Imam muqarrar farma den , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum unke Imam ho, unke kamzor logon ka khayal rakhtey huey imamat karna , aur kisi aisey shakhs ko Muazzan banana jo Azan deney par ujrat wasul na karey.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
669,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey taalim di ke main maghrib ki Azan ke waqt ye dua padhun : ''aey Allah ! ye (yani Azan maghrib ( teri raat aaney , terey din ke janey aur Muazzan ki aawaz ka waqt hai, mujhey bakhsh dey .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
670,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke koi doosrey sahabi bayan kartey hain ke Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne iqaamat shuru ki, pas jab unhoney kaha : '' Namaz khadi ho chuki '' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah usey qaaim w daaim rakhey.'' aur baqi iqaamat mein Azan ke mutalliq umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ki tarah kalmaat kahey."
671,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''azaan w iqaamat ke beech dua radd nahin ki jati.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
672,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do duayen radd nahin ki jatin ya farmaya : kam hi radd ki jati hain, Azan ke waqt ki janey wali dua aur ghamasaan ki ladaai ke waqt ki janey wali dua, aur eik riwayat mein hai, barish ke waqt (ki janey wali dua).'' Abu-Dawud, Darmi, lekin Darmi ne ''barish ke waqt'' ka zikr nahin kya."
673,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! Muazzan to ham par fazilat ley gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jaisey wo kahin wesay hi tum kaho, pas jab tum (jawab deney sey) farigh ho jaao to (Allah sey) maango, tumhen ata kya jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
674,"Hazrat Jabir bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab shetan Namaz ke liye Azan sunta hai to wo maqam Rauha tak bhag jata hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, Rauha Madina se chhattis mail ki masafat par hai. rawahu Muslim ."
675,"Hazrat Alqama bin Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha, jab unke Muazzan ne Azan kahi to Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi apney Muazzan ke kalmaat kahey yahan tak ke jab usney kaha : aao Namaz ki taraf , to unhoney kaha : (لا حول wla quwwata الا باللہ ) '' gunah se bachna aur neki karna mehaz Allah ki tofiq se mumkin hai.'' pas jab usney kaha : ( حی Ali الفلاح ) to unhoney kaha : لا حول wla quwwata الا باللہ العلی العظیم aur uskey baad jaisey Muazzan ne kaha, wesay hi unhoney kaha, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey hi farmaya. rawahu Ahmed ."
676,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they. Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho kar Azan deney lagey , chunanche jab wo khamosh ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs khulus dil se ye kalmaat kahega wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' rawahu Nasai ."
677,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Muazzan ko Allah ke mabud honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Rasool honey ki gawahi detey huey suntey to farmatey : ''aur main bhi, aur main bhi (gawahi deta hun).'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
678,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs baara saal Azan dey to uskey liye jannat wajib ho jati hai, aur uski Azan ki wajeh se uskey haq mein har din 60 nekiyan aur her iqaamat ke badley tees nekiyan likhi jati hain.''"
679,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Azan maghrib ke waqt hamen dua karney ka hukm diya jata tha."
680,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Bilal (tulue-Fajr se pehley) raat ke waqt Azan detey hain, pas jab tak Umme-Maktum Azan na den tum (sehri) khatey raho.''raawi bayan kartey hain, ibne-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) na-bina shakhs they, aur jab tak unhen ye na kaha jata ke subh ho gaee , wo Azan nahin detey they. muttafaq aleh."
681,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Azan Bilal aur Fajr kazib tumhen sehri khaney-peeney se na rokey, lekin ufuq mein phel janey wali subh (subh saadiq honey par khaney peeney se ruk jaao).'' Muslim, aur ye alfaz Tirmizi ke hain. rawahu Muslim w Tirmizi ."
682,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main aur mera chachazaad, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum safar karo to tum Azan do (eik Azan dey doosra jawab dey) aur iqaamat kaho aur tum se jo bada hai wo tumhari imaamat karaaey.'' Bukhari ."
683,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen farmaya : ''tum wesay Namaz padho jaisey tum ne mujhey Namaz padhtey huey dekha hai, jab Namaz ka waqt ho jaey to tum mein se koi Azan dey , phir tum mein se jo bada ho wo imaamat kiraaey .'' muttafaq aleh."
684,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwa khaibar se wapis tashrif laye to aapney raat bhar safar jari rakha, yahan tak ke aap ko ungh aaney lagi to aapney raat ke aakhiri hissey mein neend ki gharz se padaaw dala aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''aap raat ke waqt pehra den.'' chunanche Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne is qadr nawafil padhey jis qadr unke muqaddar mein they jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba so gaey, jab Fajr ka waqt qarib aa pahuncha to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Fajr (mashriq) ki taraf rukh karkey apni sawari ke sath tek laga li to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) par neend ka ghalba ho gaya aur wo apni sawari ke sath tek lagaey huey so gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bedaar huey na Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aur na hi aap ka koi aur sahabi, yahan tak ke un par dhoop aa gaee, to un mein se sab se pehley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bedaar huey . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghabra kar farmaya : '' Bilal ! Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ( Allah ke Rasool!) jo chiz aap par ghalib aai wohi chiz mujh par ghalib aa gaee, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( yahan sey) apney janweron ko chalaao.'' unhoney thodi door tak apney janweron ko haanka, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu kya, aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm farmaya to unhoney Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi , aur aapney unhen Namaz padhai, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh chukey to farmaya : ''jo shakhs Namaz padhna bhool jaey to wo uskey yad aaney par usey padh ley, kyonkey Allah Taala ne farmaya : ''merey zikr ke liye Namaz qaaim karo.'' rawahu Muslim."
685,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi jaey to tum khadey na hua karo yahan tak ke tum mujhey dekh lo ke main ( hujra sey) bahar aa chuka hun.'' muttafaq aleh."
686,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Namaz ke liye iqaamat keh di jaey to phir Namaz ki taraf dodtey huey mat aao balke itminan w sukoon aur waqar ke sath aao, pas tum jo pa lo padh lo , aur jo tum se reh jaey usey pura kar lo .'' Bukhari , Muslim . aur Muslim ki eik riwayat mein hai : '' kyonkey jab tum mein se koi Namaz ka qasd (irada) karta hai to wo Namaz hi mein hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
687,"Hazrat Zaid bin Aslam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik andheri raat Makka mein raat ke aakhiri hissey mein padaaw dala, aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm farmaya ke wo unhen Namaz ke liye bedaar karey, pas Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aur wo sab so gaey yahan tak ke wo sab bedaar huey to Suraj tulu ho chuka tha, jab wo bedaar huey to ghabra gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen us wadi se nikal janey ka hukm farmaya , aur farmaya : is wadi mein shetan hai, pas Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) sawar huey yahan tak ke wo us wadi se nikal gaey, phir Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen hukm farmaya ke wo padaaw dalen aur wuzu karen, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Namaz ke liye Azan ya iqaamat kehney ka hukm farmaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sahaba kiram ko Namaz padhaai, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farigh huey to unki be chaini dekh kar farmaya : ''logo! be-shak Allah ne hamari roohen qabz kin, agar wo chahta to unhen us waqt ke ilawa kisi aur waqt (tulu aaftaab se pehley) hamari taraf lota deta, jab tum mein se koi Namaz ke waqt so jaey ya wo usey bhool jaey phir usey uskey mutalliq aagahi ho jaey to wo usey wesay hi padhey jaisey wo usey uskey waqt mein padha karta tha,'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : '' shetan , Bilal ke paas aaya jabkey wo Namaz padh rahey they, usney unhen lita diya, phir wo unhen thapki deta raha, jaisey bachey ko thapki di jati hai, yahan tak ke wo so gaey ''phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wesey hi bataya jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bataya tha, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main gawahi deta hun ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain. Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey mursal riwayat kya hai."
688,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalmanon ke do baton ki zimme daari w hifazat muazzanon ki gardanon mein muallaq hai, unke rozey aur unki namaazein.''"
689,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah ke andar tashrif ley gaey to aapney uskey tamam atraaf mein dua farmaai lekin aapney Namaz nahin padhi yahan tak ke aap wahan se bahar tashrif ley aaye , pas jab bahar tashrif laye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Kaba ke samney do rakatein padhein aur farmaya : ''ye ( Kaba ( qibla hai.'' Bukhari ."
690,Hazrat Imam Muslim ne usey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Muslim .
691,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Usama bin Zaid , Usman bin Talha Hajabi aur Bilal bin Ribah (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) Kaba ke andar tashrif ley gaey to Usman ne Baitullah ka darwaza band kar diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) thodi der ke liye wahan thehrey, aur jab bahar tashrif laye to maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( andar ( kya kya? unhoney farmaya : aapney eik sutoon apney baain , do sutoon apney daain aur teen sutoon apney peechey kar liye , un dino Baitullah chhe sutonon par tha, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padhi . muttafaq aleh."
692,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri is masjid ( masjide-nabawi ( main eik Namaz , Masjide-Haram ke ilawa , dusri masjidon ki hazar Namaz se behtar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
693,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen masjidein, masjide-Haram, masjide-Aqsa aur meri is masjid, ke siwa kisi aur masjid ke liye safar na kiya jaaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
694,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey ghar aur merey member ke darmiyan jo jagah hai wo jannat ka baghicha hai, aur mera member merey hoz ( kausar ( par hoga .'' muttafaq aleh."
695,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her haftey , kabhi pedal aur kabhi sawari par masjid Quba tashrif ley jaya kartey they, aur wahan do rakatein padha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
696,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke nazdik sab se ziyada pasandida maqamat masjidein hain aur sab se ziyada na-pasandida jaghen baazar hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
697,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ki raza ki khatir masjid banata hai to Allah uskey liye jannat mein ghar banata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
698,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh w Sham jitni martaba masjid mein jata hai, Allah uskey liye itni martaba hi jannat mein ziyafat ka ehtimam farmata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
699,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs jitni door se chal kar Namaz padhney aata hai to wo usi qadr ziyada ajr hasil karta hai, aur jo shakhs Namaz ka intizar karta rehta hai yahan tak ke wo Imam ke sath Namaz padhta hai to wo us shakhs se ziyada ajr hasil karta hai jo akela Namaz padh kar so jata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
700,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, masjid ( nabwi (ke Aas paas kuch zamin khaali hui to banu-Salma ne masjid ke qarib muntaqil honey ka irada kya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pata chala to aapney unhen farmaya : ''mujhey pata chala hai ke tum masjid ke qarib aana chahtey ho ?'' unhoney arz kya : ji haan , Allah ke Rasool ! hamara irada to yehi hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' banu-Salma ! apney gharon hi mein raho , tumharey qadam likhey jatey hain, apney gharon hi mein raho , tumharey ( masjid ki taraf uthney waley ( qadam likhey jatey hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
701,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' saat khush nasib aisey hain jinhen Allah apna saya nasib farmaeyga jis roz uskey saye ke siwa koi saya nahin hoga : aadil hukmran , wo nojawan jo Allah ki ibadat mein parwan chadha , wo aadmi jis ka dil masjid ke sath muallaq hai, jab masjid se nikalta hai) to wo masjid se la-talluq nahin rehta ( yahan tak ke wo wahan lot jata hai, wo do aadmi jo Allah ki raza ki khatir aapas mein mohabbat kartey hain, usi buniyad par ikhattey hotey hain, aur agar jude hotey hain to bhi us mohabbat par qaaim rehtey hain, wo aadmi jisney tanhai mein Allah ko yad kya to uski aankhen gili ho gaeen, wo aadmi jisey achche khandan wali khoobsurat ladki ne (burai ki) dawat di to usney kaha : main Allah se darta hun ! aur wo aadmi jisney jo sadqa kya, usney usey is qadr chhipa kar rakha yahan tak ke uska baayan haath nahin janta ke uskey daain haath ne kya kharch kya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
702,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aadmi jo Namaz ba-jamaat ada karta hai, uski wo Namaz uskey ghar ya baazar mein padhi janey wali Namaz sey, pachchis guna ziyada ajr w sawab rakhti hai, wo is liye ke jab wo wuzu karta hai aur achi tarah wuzu karta hai aur phir wo mehaz Namaz ada karney ke liye rawana hota hai to uskey her qadam par uska eik darja buland kar diya jata hai aur uski wajeh se uska eik gunah maaf kar diya jata hai, pas jab wo Namaz padh kar apni jaey Namaz par betha rehta hai to farishtey uskey liye duayen kartey rehtey hain : aey Allah ! is par rahmatein nazil farma , aey Allah ! is par rehem farma , aur jab koi shakhs Namaz ke intizar mein rehta hai to wo ( hukm w sawab ke lihaz sey) Namaz mein hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh. aur eik riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''jab wo masjid mein aaye aur Namaz usey ( masjid mein) rokey rakhey .'' Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne farishton ki dua mein ye izafa naql kya hai : ''aey Allah ! usey bakhsh dey, aey Allah! uski tauba qubul farma, aur jab tak wo kisi ko takleef pahunchaey na uska wuzu tootey to farishton ki dua ka silsila jari rehta hai.''"
703,"Hazrat abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi masjid mein dakhil ho to wo ye dua padhey : ''aey Allah! merey liye apni rehmat ke darwazey khol dey , aur jab wo masjid se bahar aaye to ye dua padhey : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se terey Fazal ka sawal karta hun.'' rawahu Muslim ."
704,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi masjid mein dakhil ho to wo bethney se pehley do rakatein padhey.'' muttafaq aleh."
705,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaasht ke waqt safar se (Madina) wapis aaya kartey they, jab aap wapis tashrif latey to sab se pehley masjid mein tashrif latey aur wahan do rakatein padhtey phir wahan beth jatey. '' muttafaq aleh."
706,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs, kisi aadmi ko gumshuda janwer (ya koi bhi chiz) ke mutalliq masjid mein aelan kartey suney, to wo shakhs kahey : Allah tumhari wo chiz tumhen wapis na lotaye, kyonkey masjiden is liye to nahin banai gaeen.'' rawahu Muslim."
707,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs us badbudar paudey (piyaz, lehsun waghera) se kuch kha ley to wo hamari masjid mein na aaye, kyonkey farishtey us chiz se takleef mehsus kartey hain, jis se insan takleef mehsus kartey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
708,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' masjid mein thookna gunah hai, aur uska kaffara usey dafn kar dena hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
709,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ke achey burey tamam aamaal mujh par pesh kiye gaey, maine, raastey se takleef deh chiz ko door kar dena, uski khoobiyan aamaal mein pana, aur wo thook jo masjid mein ho aur usey saaf na kya jaey to maine usey uskey burey aamaal mein paya.'' rawahu Muslim."
710,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs Namaz padh raha ho to wo apney samney na thookey, kyonkey wo jab tak Namaz mein hota hai apney rab se ham-kalam hota hai, aur wo apni daain taraf bhi na thookey kyonkey uskey daain janib farishta hai, aur) agar zarurat ho to ( apni baain janib ya apney paaon ke nichey thookey aur usey dafn kar dey .'' muttafaq aleh."
711,aur abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : '' apney baain paaon ke nichey .'' muttafaq aleh.
712,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney us marz ke doran , jis se aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sehatyaab na ho sakey, farmaya : ''Allah yahood-Nasara par lanat farmaey, unhoney apney Anbiya ki qabron ko sajda-gah bana liya.'' muttafaq aleh."
713,"Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' sun lo ! tum se pehley log apney Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) aur apney Saleh afrad ki qabron ko sajda-gah bana liya kartey they, khabrdar ! tum qabron ko sajdagah na banana, be-shak main tumhen us se mana karta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
714,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni (nafl) Namaz apney gharon mein padha karo, unhen qabristan na banaao.'' muttafaq aleh."
715,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qibla mashriq w maghrib ke beech hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
716,"Hazrat Talaq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham wafad ki surat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh huey to ham ne aap ki baiat ki, aap ke sath Namaz padhi aur aap ko bataya hamarey mulk mein hamara eik girja hai, aap hamen apney wuzu se bacha hua pani inayat farma den, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pani mangaya, wuzu kya aur kulli ki, phir usey hamarey liye eik bartan mein dal diya, aur hamen janey ki ijazat detey huey farmaya : ''jab tum apni sar zamin par pahuncho to apney girjey ko tod do, us jagah par ye pani chhidko aur wahan masjid banaao .'' ham ne arz kya : hamara mulk door hai jabkey garmi shadeed hai, isliye ye pani to khushk ho jaeyga, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' is mein aur pani mila lena kyonkey us se uski barkat mazeed badh jaeygi .'' rawahu Nasai ."
717,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mehlon mein masjid bananey aur unhen paak saaf rakhney ka hukm farmaya .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
718,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey masajid ko choona gach karney ka hukm nahin diya gaya.'' ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : tum unhen is tarah muzayyan karogey jaisey Yahud Nasara ne muzayyan kya."
719,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' alamaate-qiyamat mein se eik nishani ye hai ke log masaajid ke barey mein baham (aapas mein) fakhr karengey .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai w Darmi w ibne-Maja ."
720,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ke aamaal ka sawab mujh par pesh kya gaya, yahan tak ke wo tinka bhi jisey aadmi masjid se utha kar bahar phenk deta hai (us ka sawab bhi likha hua tha), aur meri ummat ke gunah bhi mujh par pesh kiye gaey to maine us se bada koi gunah nahin dekha ke kisi aadmi ko Quran ki koi sura ya koi aayat ata ki gaee aur usney ( yad karney ke baad) usey bhula diya .''"
721,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' andherey mein chal kar masjid ki taraf aaney walon ko roze-qiyamat mukammal Noor ki khushkhabri suna do.''"
722,Hazrat Imam ibne-Maja ne Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se usey riwayat kya hai.
723,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aadmi ko masjid ki abadi ke liye koshaan dekho to uskey eman ki gawahi do, kyonkey Allah Taala farmata hai : ''Allah ki masjidon ko sirf wohi log abad kar saktey hain jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhtey hon.'' (Hasan ( rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
724,"Hazrat Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! hamen khassi honey ki ijazat ata farmaeyn, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi ko khassi kya ya apney aap ko khassi kya to wo ham mein se nahin, kyonkey meri ummat ka khassi hona, roza rakhna hai.'' unhoney kaha : hamen sayahat ki ijazat marahmat farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ki sayahat, jihad fi sabililah hai.'' unhoney arz kya : hamen rehbaniyat ikhtiyar karney ki ijazat dey den, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Namaz ke intizar mein masaajid mein bethna meri ummat ki rehbaniyat hai.''"
725,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Aaish (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine ( khuwab mein) apney rab azz-w-jall ko behtareen surat mein dekha, usney farmaya : muqarrab farishtey kis chiz ke barey mein behes w mubaahisa kar rahey hain? maine arz kya : to behtar janta hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' usney merey kandhon ke darmiyan apna haath rakha to maine uski thandak apney qalb w siney mein mehsus ki, aur maine zamin w aasman ki her chiz jaan li .'' aur phir aapney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : '' aur isi tarah ham ne Ibrahim ko aasmano ki aur zamin ki badshahat dikhai taake wo yaqin rakhney walon mein se ho jaeyn .'' Darmi ne mursal riwayat kya, aur Tirmizi mein bhi unhen se usi ki misl hai. rawahu Darmi w Tirmizi ."
726,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai. aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne is mein ye izafa kya hai : ''Allah ne farmaya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! kya aap jantey hain ke muqarrab farishtey kis chiz ke barey mein behes w mubaahisa kar rahey hain? maine arz kya, ji haan gunah khatam karney waley aamaal ke barey mein) behes kar rahey hain (aur gunah khatam karney waley aamaal ye hain : namazon ke baad masjid mein bethey rehna , ba-jamaat Namaz padhney ke liye pedal chal kar jana , aur nagawari ke bawajud khub achi tarah wuzu karna , pas jo ye kerega wo behtar zindagi basar kerega aur uski maut bhi achi hogi , aur wo gunahon se aisey paak ho jaeyga jaisey uski maa ne usey aaj janm diya ho, aur farmaya : Muhammad ! jab aap Namaz se farigh ho jaeyn to ye dua kya karo : aey Allah ! main tujh se nek kaam baja laney , burey kaam chhod deney aur miskinon se mohabbat karney ki darkhaast karta hun aur jab to apney bandon ko kisi aazmaaish w fitney se do-char karney ka irada farmaai to mujhey us se do-chaar kiye baghair apni taraf utha lena.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' darjaat ki bulandi waley aamaal ye hain : salam aam karna , khana khilana aur jab log so rahey hon to Namaz tahajjud padhna .'' aur is hadees ke alfaz jaisa ke masaabeh mein hain, maine Abdur-Rehman ki sanad se Sharahus-sunnah mein paey hain. ."
727,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen aadmiyon ki mukammal hifazat karna Allah ke zimme hai, wo aadmi jo Allah ki raah mein jihad ke liye rawana ho to wo Allah ki hifazat mein hai yahan tak ke Allah usey faut karkey jannat mein dakhil farma dey, ya usey hasil honey waley ajr ya maale-ghanimat ke sath wapis lota dey. wo aadmi jo masjid ki taraf jaey to wo bhi Allah ki hifazat mein hai aur wo aadmi jo apney ghar mein dakhil hotey waqt salam karta hai wo bhi Allah ki hifazat mein hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
728,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ba-wuzu ho kar farz Namaz ke liye apney ghar se rawana hota hai to uska ajr ehram baandh kar Haj ke liye rawana honey waley ke ajr ki tarah hai, aur jo shakhs sirf Namaz chaasht ke liye rawana hota hai uskey liye Umra karney waley ke barabar ajr hai, aur eik Namaz ke baad dusri Namaz is tarah padhna ke unke darmiyan koi laghw baat na ho uska amal illiyeen mein likh diya jata hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood ."
729,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum jannat ke baaghon ke paas se guzro to kuch kha pi liya karo.'' arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! jannat ke baghaat kya hain? aapney farmaya : '' masaajid .'' puchha gaya Allah ke Rasool ! khaney-piney se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : (Subhan Allah, w Alhamdulillah, wala-ilaah-illallah, wallahu-akbar) ''Allah paak hai, her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur Allah sab se bada hai.''"
730,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs jis chiz ke liye masjid mein jata hai wohi uska nasib hogi , ( jo usey aakhirat mein milegi).''"
731,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) apni daadi Fatima kubra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat karti hain, unhoney farmaya : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein dakhil hotey to ye dua padhtey : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par salat w salam ho, aur farmatey : merey rab ! merey gunah bakhsh dey aur merey liye apni rehmat ke darwazey khol dey , aur jab aap masjid se bahar nikaltey to farmatey : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par salat w salam ho. aur farmatey : ''merey rab ! merey gunah bakhsh dey , aur merey liye Fazal ke darwazey khol dey . Tirmizi, Ahmed, ibne-Maja aur un dono ki riwayat mein hai, unhoney farmaya : jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein dakhil hotey aur isi tarah jab aap bahar tashrif latey to '' Muhammad par salat w salam ho'' ke bajaey : ''Allah ke naam sey, aur Rasulullah par salam ho.'' ke alfaz padhtey they. Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : iski sanad muttasil nahin, Fatima binte-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ki Fatima kubra (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat Sabit nahin."
732,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne masjid mein she'r goi, khareed-bikri aur Juma ke roz Namaz se pehley masjid mein halqey bana kar bethney se mana farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi."
733,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum kisi shakhs ko masjid mein khareed-bikri kartey huey dekho to tum kaho : Allah teri tijarat ko nafa mand na banaey , aur jab tum kisi shakhs ko is mein gum shuda janwer ka aelan kartey huey dekho to tum kaho : Allah karey wo chiz tumhen na miley .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi ."
734,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne masjid mein qisaas ka mutalba karney , ashaar padhney aur hudood qaaim karney se mana farmaya."
735,Hazrat masaabeh mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai.
736,Hazrat Muawiya bin Qurra (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un do paudon yani piyaz aur lehsun se mana kya aur farmaya : ''jo unhen khaye wo hamari masjid mein na aaye.'' aur farmaya : ''agar tum ne unhen zaroori khana hai to phir pakka kar unki bu khatm kar do.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood .
737,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qabristan aur Hammam ke ilawa sari zamin masjid hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Darmi ."
738,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne saat jagahon , kudey-karkat ke dher, zibeh khana, qabristaan, aam rastey, Hammam, oonton ke baadey aur Baitullah ki chhat par Namaz padhney se mana farmaya."
739,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bakriyon ke baadey mein Namaz padho lekin oonton ke baadey mein Namaz na padho .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
740,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qabron ki ziyaarat karney wali aurton par aur qabron ko sajda gaah bananey walon aur un par chiraaghan karney walon par laanat farmaai hai."
741,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi Yahudi aalim ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya : kon sa zamin ka hissa behtar hai? aap khamosh ho gaey aur farmaya : ''main Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ke aaney tak khamosh rahunga.'' aap khamosh rahey aur Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha to unhoney kaha is barey mein jawab denewala, sawal karney waley se ziyada nahin janta, lekin main apney rab tabarak w taala se poochhunga, phir Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! main Allah ke itna qarib hua ke main us se pehley kabhi itna qarib nahin hua , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : '' Jibrael ! wo ( qarib hona ( kaisey tha ?'' unhoney farmaya : merey aur uskey beech Noor ke sattar hazar pardey they, Allah Taala ne farmaya : bad-tareen maqamat baazar aur behtareen maqamat masaajid hain.'' (لا اصل لہ بھذا اللفظ ، لم اجدہ an ابی امامہ)"
742,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs meri is masjid mein mehaz koi khair w bhalai seekhney ya sikhaney ki gharz se aaye to wo Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ke maqam w martabey par hai, aur jo shakhs iskey ilawa kisi aur gharz se aaye to wo us aadmi ki tarah hai jo kisi ke maal par nazar rakhta ho.'' , ( rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
743,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) se mursal riwayat hai, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' logon par eik aisa daur aaeyga ke unki masaajid mein unki guftgu ka mauzu unke dunyawi umur (baton) hongey . pas tum unke sath na betho, Allah ko unki koi hajat nahin.''"
744,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main masjid mein soyaa hua tha to kisi aadmi ne mujhey kankari maari , maine dekha to wo umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) they. unhoney farmaya : jaao aur un dono aadmiyon ko merey paas laao , main unhen unke paas ley aaya, to unhoney farmaya : tum kis qabiley se ho aur kahan se ho? unhoney kaha : ehle-Taaif sey, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar tum ehle-Madina se hotey to main tumhen zarur saza deta , tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki masjid main apni aawazen buland kartey ho. Bukhari ."
745,"Hazrat Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne masjid ke koney mein Batiha naami eik sehan tayyar kya aur farmaya : jo shakhs fuzul baaten karna chahey, ya she'r padhna chahey ya apni aawaz buland karna chahey to wo us sehan ki taraf chala jaey."
746,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qible ( ki taraf deewar ( mein thook dekha to ye aap par is qadr shaaq guzra ke uskey asraat aap ke chehrey par numaya ho gaey . pas aap khadey huey aur apney haath se usey saaf kya, phir farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz padhta hai to wo apney rab se ham-kalam hota hai, kyonkey uska rab uskey aur qible ke beech hota hai, pas tum mein se koi apney qible ki taraf na thookey , balke apney baain taraf ya apney paaon ke nichey .'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni chadar ka kinara pakda phir is mein thooka aur us ( kapdey ( ko eik doosrey ke sath mil diya aur farmaya : '' ya phir wo is tarah kar ley.'' Bukhari ."
747,"Hazrat Saaib bin khallad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : kisi aadmi ne kuch logon ki imaamat karaai to usney qibla rukh thook diya, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey dekh rahey they, jab wo Namaz se farigh hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski qom se farmaya : ''ye tumhen Namaz na padhaaey .'' phir uskey baad usney Namaz padhaana chahi to unhoney usey rok diya aur usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman se aagah kya us shakhs ne aap se uska tazkira kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan (maine roka hai).'' raawi bayan kartey hain, mera khayal hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne Allah aur uskey Rasool ko aziyat pahunchaai hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
748,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen namaze-Fajr padhaaney ke liye tashrif na laye, qarib tha ke ham Suraj tulu honey ka mushaahida kar letey, phir aap bahut tezi se tashrif laye chunanche Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi gaee, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ikhtisaar ke sath Namaz padhaai, pas jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam phera to ba-aawaz buland farmaya : ''apni jagahon par aisey hi bethey raho.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamari taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : ''main abhi tumhen batata hun ke main tumhen Namaz padhaaney ke liye kyon nahin aaya, main raat ko bedaar hua, wuzu kya aur jis qadr muqaddar mein tha maine Namaz padhi, mujhey Namaz mein ungh aaney lagi yahan tak ke wo mujh par ghalib aa gaee , tab maine apney rab tabarak w taala ko behtareen surat mein dekha chunanche usney farmaya : Muhammad ! maine arz kya : merey rab ! hazir hun, farmaya : farishtey kis chiz ke barey mein behes w mubaahasa kar rahey hain? maine arz kya : main nahin janta .'' Allah Taala ne teen martaba aisey farmaya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine usey dekha ke usney apna haath merey kandhon ke darmiyan rakha yahan tak ke maine uski ungliyon ke poron ki thandak apney qalb aur siney mein mehsus ki, aur merey samney her chiz wazeh ho gaee aur maine pehchan li , phir rab taala ne farmaya : Muhammad ! maine arz kya, merey rab! main hazir hun, farmaya : muqarrab farishtey kis chiz ke barey mein behes w mubaahasa kar rahey hain? maine arz kya, gunah mita deney waley aamaal ke barey mein, farmaya : wo kya hain? maine arz kya : ba-jamaat Namaz padhney ley liye chal kar jana, Namaz ke baad masaajid mein bethey rehna, nagawari ke bawajud achi tarah wuzu karna, farmaya : phir wo kis chiz ke barey mein behes kar rahey hain? maine arz kya : darjaat ke barey mein, farmaya : wo kya hain? maine arz kya : khana khilana, narmi se baat karna aur jab log so rahey hon Namaz (tahajjud) padhna. farmaya : kuch mang lein.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine arz kya : aey Allah! tujh se nek aamaal baja laney, burey kaam chhod deney aur miskinon se mohabbat karney ki tofiq maangta hun, aur ye ke to mujhey bakhsh dey aur mujh par rehem farma , aur jab to kisi qom ko fitney se do-chaar karna chahey to mujhey is mein mubtala kiye baghair faut kar dena, main tujh sey, teri mohabbat, tujh se mohabbat karney walon ki mohabbat aur aisey amal ki mohabbat ka sawal karta hun jo mujhey teri mohabbat ke qarib kar dey .'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ( khuwab ( haq hai, pas usey yad karo aur phir usey dusron ko bataao .'' Ahmed, Tirmizi . Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, aur maine Muhammad bin Ismail (Imam Bukhari) se is hadees ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
749,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein dakhil hotey to ye dua kya kartey : ''main shetan mardud se Allah Azeem, uski zaat karim aur uski qadim badshahat w qudrat ke zariey panah chahta hun.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pas jab koi shakhs ye dua padhta hai to shetan kehta hai, ye ab sara din mujh se mehfooz rahega.'' Abu-Dawood ."
750,"Hazrat ata bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! meri qabr ko but na banana ke uski puja ki jaey, Allah un logon par sakht naraz ho jinhon ne Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) ki qabron ko sajda gaah bana liya.'' Imam Malik ne usey mursal riwayat kya. rawahu Malik."
751,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baghaat mein) nafl ( Namaz padhna pasand farmaya kartey they.'' Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, ham usey sirf Hasan bin abi Jaafar ke wastey se jantey hain, jabkey Yahya bin Saeed waghera ne isey zaeef . qarar diya hai."
752,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aadmi ki apney ghar mein padhi hui Namaz (sawab ke lihaz sey) eik Namaz hai, uski is masjid mein Namaz , jis mein mukhtalif qabiley Namaz padhtey hain, pachchis namazon ki tarah hai, aur jis masjid mein Juma hota ho, is mein uski Namaz paanch so namazon ki tarah hai, masjide-Aqsa mein uski Namaz pachas hazar namazon ki tarah hai, uski meri masjid mein padhi gaee Namaz pachas hazar namazon ki tarah hai aur Masjide-Haram mein uski Namaz eik lakh namazon ki tarah hai.''"
753,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ruey zamin par sab se pehley kon si masjid taamir ki gaee ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' masjide-Haram.'' raawi kehtey hain, maine arz kya, phir kon si masjid? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' masjide-Aqsa.'' maine arz kya : un dono ki taamir ke darmiyan kitna waqfa hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chaalis saal , phir sari zamin terey liye masjid hai, jahan Namaz ka waqt ho jaey Namaz padh lo .'' muttafaq aleh."
754,"Hazrat umr bin abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar eik kapdey mein liptey huey Namaz padhtey dekha, aapney us kapdey ke do kinarey apney kandhon par rakhey huey they. muttafaq aleh."
755,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs eik kapdey mein is tarah Namaz na padhey ke uskey kandhon par koi chiz na ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
756,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs eik kapdey mein Namaz padhey to wo uskey dono kinaron ko eik doosrey ke mukhalif samt kar ley ( daain kinarey ko baain kandhey par aur baain kinarey ko daain kandhey par) .'' Bukhari ."
757,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah ne eik munaqqash chadar mein Namaz padhi, aapney uskey naqsh w nigaar ko dekha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : ''meri ye chadar abu-Jahm ke paas ley jaao aur abu jaham ki naqsh w nigaar ke baghair chadar ley aao , isney to meri Namaz mein khalal dal diya tha.'' Bukhari , Muslim aur Bukhari ki eik riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main uskey naqsh w nigaar dekh raha tha jabkey main Namaz mein tha, mujhey andesha hua ke ye mujhey kisi fitney ka shikar na kar dey .'' muttafaq aleh."
758,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas eik parda tha jiskey sath unhoney apney ghar ki eik janib ko dhanp rakha tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : '' apney is pardey ko ham se door kar den , kyonkey uski taswirein meri Namaz mein musalsal merey samney aati rahen.'' Bukhari ."
759,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik reshmi coat tohfey mein diya gaya to aapney usey pehan kar Namaz padhi , phir Namaz se farigh ho kar sakht na pasandidgi ke aalim mein usey utaar diya aur farmaya : ''ye muttaqi logon ke shayane-shaan nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
760,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! main shikari aadmi hun, kya main eik qameez mein Namaz padh liya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, batan band karkey, chaahey kaanton ko hi bator batan istimal kar lo.'' Abu-Dawood. Imam Nasai ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
761,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi apna tehband latkaaey Namaz padh raha tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''jaao wuzu karo.'' wo gaya aur wuzu karkey phir hazir hua to kisi aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! aapney usey wuzu karney ka hukm kyon farmaya ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo apna tehband latkaaey huey Namaz padh raha tha, jabkey Allah tehband latka kar Namaz padhney waley shakhs ki Namaz qubul nahin farmata .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
762,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi baaligha aurat ki nangey sar Namaz qubul nahin hoti.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
763,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kya, kya aurat tehband ke baghair sirf qameez aur dupattey mein Namaz padh sakti hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, jab qameez is qadr kamil aur kushada ho ke wo uskey paaon dhaanpti ho.'' Abu-Dawud, aur unhoney raawiyon ki eik jamaat ka zikr kya jinhon ne is hadees ko Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) par moquf qarar diya hai.''"
764,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dorane-namaz galey mein kapda latkaaney aur munh dhaanpney se mana farmaya.
765,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : yahudiyon ki mukhalifat karo kyonkey wo apney juton aur mozon mein Namaz nahin padhtey.''"
766,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, us doran ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney Sahaba ko Namaz padha rahey they ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne achcha apney jootey utaar kar apney baain taraf rakh diye , jab Sahaba ne ye dekha to unhoney bhi apney jootey utaar diye , jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh chukey to farmaya : '' tumhen kis chiz ne jootey utaarney par aamada kya ?'' unhoney arz kya, ham ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jootey utaartey huey dekha to ham ne bhi utaar diye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Jibrael merey paas tashrif laye to unhoney mujhey bataya ke un mein gandagi hai, jab tum mein se koi masjid mein aaye to wo dekhey agar wo apney juton mein gandagi dekhey to wo usey saaf karey phir un mein Namaz padh ley.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Darmi ."
767,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz padhey to wo apney jutey apni daain taraf na rakhey na baain taraf kyonkey uski baain janib kisi doosrey shakhs ki daain janib hogi haan agar uskey baain taraf koi na ho to phir baain taraf rakh ley warna unhen apney paaon ke darmiyan rakhey .'' Abu-Dawood ibne-Maja ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
768,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine aap ko chatai par Namaz padhtey aur is par sajda kartey huey dekha, aur unhoney bayan kya ke maine aap ko eik kapdey mein is tarah Namaz padhtey huey dekha ke aapney apney jism ko eik kapdey mein dhanp rakha tha. rawahu Muslim ."
769,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi nangey paaon aur kabhi juton mein Namaz padhtey huey dekha . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
770,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Munkadir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik tehband mein is tarah Namaz padhi ke unhoney usey gardan ki taraf baandha hua tha, jabkey unke kapdey Mishjab (ghadonchi) par rakhey huey they, kisi ne un se kaha : aap eik kapdey mein Namaz padh rahey hain? unhoney farmaya : maine ye mehaz is liye kya hai taake aap jaisa ahmaq shakhs mujhey dekh ley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein ham mein se kon shakhs tha jiskey paas do kapdey hotey they? Bukhari."
771,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik kapdey mein Namaz padhna sunnat hai, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein aisa kya kartey they aur hamen mana nahin kya jata tha. ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye tab tha jab kapdon ki qillat thi, pas jab Allah farakhi ata farma dey to phir do kapdon mein Namaz padhna behtar w afzal hai. rawahu Ahmed ."
772,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subh ke waqt eidgaah ki taraf jatey eik chhota neza aapke aagey aagey utha kar ley jaya jata aur usey eidgaah mein aapke samney gaad diya jata, phir aap uski taraf rukh karkey Namaz padhtey. Bukhari."
773,"Hazrat abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Makka mein dekha, jabkey aap wadiye-Batha mein chamdey ke eik surkh khemey mein they, aur maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke wuzu ka pani liye khadey hain, aur maine logon ko dekha ke wo wuzu ke us pani ko hasil karney ke liye eik-doosrey par sabqat ley janey ki koshish kar rahey hain, chunanche jisey to is mein se kuch mil jata hai usey apney jism par mal leta hai, aur jisey is mein se kuch na milta to wo apney sathi ke haath ki nami hasil kar leta, phir maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney chhota neza lekar gaad diya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) surkh joda zeb tan kiye huey tezi se tashrif laye, aapney chhotey neze ki taraf rukh karkey logon ko do rakatein padhaein aur maine logon aur chaupaaon ko aap ke aagey se guzartey huey dekha. muttafaq aleh."
774,"Hazrat Naafe, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni sawari bitha diya kartey aur phir uski taraf rukh karkey Namaz padha kartey they. Bukhari, Muslim. muttafaq aleh. aur Imam Bukhari ne ye izafa naqal kya hai : raawi bayan kartey hain, maine kaha, jab oont charney ke liye jatey they ( to phir kya kartey they? ( unhoney kaha : wo paalaan w kajawa pakadtey aur usey samney rakh kar uskey aakhiri hissey ki taraf rukh karkey Namaz padh liya kartey they."
775,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs paalaan ki pichli lakdi ke barabar koi chiz apney aagey rakh ley to wo Namaz padhey aur jo us se padey guzrey uski koi parwah na karey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
776,"Hazrat abu-Jaheem bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar namazi ke aagey se guzarney waley shakhs ko pata chal jaey ke usey kitna gunah ya nuqsan hoga to uskey liye, uskey aagey se guzarney se chaalis tak khadey rehna, behtar hota.'' abu-Nazar ne farmaya : main nahin janta ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaalis din ya maah ya chaalis saal farmaai . muttafaq aleh."
777,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs kisi aisi chiz ki taraf rukh karkey Namaz padhey jo usey logon se chupa rahi ho (yani kisi chiz ko sutra bana kar Namaz padhey (aur phir bhi koi shakhs uskey aagey se guzarnaa chahey to wo usey rokey , lekin agar wo baaz na aaye to phir wo us se ladey kyonkey wo shetan hai.'' ye Bukhari ke alfaz hain. aur Muslim ke alfaz bhi usi maana mein hain. muttafaq aleh."
778,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat, gadha aur kutta (namazi ke aagey se guzar kar) Namaz tod detey hain, jabkey paalaan ki aakhiri lakdi ki misl koi chiz us se bachaati hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
779,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz tahajjud padha kartey they jabkey main, aap ke aur qible ke darmiyan is tarah leti hoti thi jis tarah (Imam ke aagey) janaza rakha hota hai. muttafaq aleh."
780,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main eik din gadhi par Sawar ho kar aaya, main un dino baligh honey key qarib tha, jabkey Rasulullah us waqt kisi deewar ki ot liye baghair Mina mein Namaz padha rahey they, pas main eik saf ke aagey se guzra, phir main gadhi se utra aur usey charney ke liye chhod diya, aur khud saf mein shamil ho gaya, aur kisi ne bhi mujh par aetraz na kya. muttafaq aleh."
781,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz padhey to wo apney samney koi chiz rakh ley, agar koi chiz na paey to phir apni lathi gaad ley , aur agar uskey paas lathi bhi na ho to phir eik lakeer khinch ley , phir uskey aagey se jo bhi guzar jaey wo uskey liye Muzir (nuqsandeh) nahin hoga.''"
782,"Hazrat Sehal bin abi Hashma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs sutra ki taraf rukh karkey Namaz padhey to wo uskey qarib ho jaey, taake shetan uski Namaz na kaat sakey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
783,"Hazrat Miqdad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab bhi kisi lakdi , sutoon aur darkht ki taraf rukh karkey Namaz padhtey huey dekha to aap usey apni daain ya baeyn abru ke samney kartey they, aur aap uskey bilkul samney khadey nahin hotey they."
784,"Hazrat Fazal-bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham jangal mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath mein hamarey paas tashrif laye aapney sutra ke baghair sehra mein Namaz ada ki, jabkey hamari gadhi aur kutiyaa aap ke aagey khel rahi thin, aapney usey koi ahmiyat na di. Abu-Dawud, Nasai ki riwayat bhi isi tarah hai."
785,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi chiz Namaz ko nahin todti, pas maqdoor bhar usey roko, kyonkey wo (guzarney wala) shetan hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
786,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aagey so jaya karti thi, jabkey merey paaon aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sajde ki jagah par hotey they, jab aap sajda kartey to aap mujhey haath se daba detey to main apney paaon samet leti aur jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho jatey to main unhen phela deti, unhoney bataya : un dino gharon mein chiragh nahin hua kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
787,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum mein kisi ko, Namaz mein mashghool apney bhai ke aagey se guzarney ka gunah malum ho to uskey liye so baras khadey rehna eik qadam uthaney se behtar hota.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
788,"Hazrat Kab Ahbar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, agar namazi ke aagey se guzarney waley ko pata chal jata ke usey is par kitna gunah milega to wo samajhta ke usey dhansa diya jaey to ye uskey liye, uskey aagey se guzarney se behtar hota. aur eik riwayat mein hai is par aasan hota. rawahu malik."
789,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs sutra ke baghair Namaz padhey to gadha, khinzir, yahudi, majusi aur aurat guzar kar uski Namaz tod detey hain, aur agar wo pathar phainkney ke fasley ke barabar uskey aagey se guzar jaeyn to phir uski Namaz ho jaeygi.''"
790,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi masjid mein aaya, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid ke eik janib tashrif farma they, pas usney Namaz padhi, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar salam arz kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey salam ka jawab de-kar farmaya : '' wapis ja kar Namaz padho , kyonkey tum ne Namaz nahin padhi , pas wo gaya aur Namaz dohraai, phir aa kar salam arz kya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam ka jawab de-kar farmaya : '' wapis ja kar Namaz padh kyonkey tum ne Namaz nahin padhi .'' pas teesri ya chauthi martaba usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! mujhey sikha den , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz padhney ka irada karo to khub achi tarah wuzu karo, phir qibla rukh khadey ho kar Allahu-akbar kaho , phir jis qadr Quran tumhen yad ho padho , phir itminan ke sath rukoo karo, phir sidhey khadey ho jaao , phir itminan ke sath sajda karo, phir utho yahan tak ke itminan ke sath beth jaao , phir itminan ke sath sajda karo, phir utho yahan tak ke itminan ke sath beth jaao .'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' phir utho yahan tak ke tum itminan ke sath khadey ho jaao , phir apni tamam ( farz w nafl ( namazon mein aisey hi kya karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
791,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz Allahu-akbar se aur qirat ( Alhamdulillahi rabbil aalameen) se shuru kya kartey they, jab aap rukoo kartey to apna sar Mubarak ooper uthatey they na nichey jhukaatey they, balke un dono Suraton ke darmiyan ( barabar ( rakhtey they, jab rukoo se sar uthatey to bilkul sidha khadey hotey aur phir sajda kartey , jab sajde se sar uthatey to phir itminan se beth jatey aur phir doosra sajda kartey , aap her do rakaaton ke baad at-tahiyaat padhtey they. aap baaeyn paaon ko bichha detey aur daain paaon ko khada rakhtey they, aap shetan ki tarah bethney (peeth ke bal beth kar taangein khadi kar lena aur haath zamin par laga dene) se aur darindon ki tarah bazu bichha kar sajda karney se mana kya kartey they, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) '' Assalaamualaikum warahmatullah'' par Namaz khatam kya kartey they."
792,"Hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ki eik jamaat mein farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke mutalliq main tum sab se ziyada janta hun, maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, jab aapney Allahu-akbar kaha to apney haath kandhon ke barabar kar liye , jab aapney rukoo kya to apney haath ghutnon par rakhey , phir apni kamar ko jhukaya , jab rukoo se sar uthaya to bilkul sidhey khadey ho gaey yahan tak ke her haddi apni jagah par aa gaee , jab sajda kya to aapney haath rakhey jo ke bichey huey they na simte huey they aur aapney paaon ki ungliyon ke kinaron ko qible ki taraf kya tha, jab aap do rakaaton mein bethey to aap apney baain paaon par bethey aur daain paaon ko khada kya, aur jab aakhiri rakaat mein bethey to baeyn paaon ko aagey badha kar peeth par beth gaey aur daain paaon ko khada kya. Bukhari ."
793,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz shuru kartey , rukoo ke liye Allahu-akbar kehtey, aur jab rukoo se sar uthatey to raful-yadain kya kartey they, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( rukoo se uthtey waqt ( farmatey : ''Allah ne sun li jisney uski hamd bayan ki, hamarey rab tamam hamd w sataaish terey hi liye hai.'' aur aap sajdon ke beech ye (raful-yadain) nahin kya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
794,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz shuru kartey to Allahu-akbar kehtey aur haath uthatey they, jab rukoo kartey to haath uthatey, jab (""Sami-Allahu-liman hamida) kehtey to haath uthatey aur jab do rakatein padh kar khadey hotey to haath uthatey they. jabkey ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne is hadees ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marfoo riwayat kya hai. Bukhari ."
795,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allahu-akbar kehtey to apney haath uthatey yahan tak ke wo unhen kanon ke barabar ley aatey, jab rukoo se sar uthatey aur ''Sami-Allahu liman hamida"" kehtey to bhi isi tarah kartey, aur eik-doosri riwayat mein : yahan tak ke wo unhen kanon ki lo ke barabar kar letey. muttafaq aleh."
796,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Namaz padhtey huey dekha, jab aap Namaz ki taaq rakaat mein hotey to itminan se beth jatey aur phir (dusri rakaat ke liye ( khadey hotey . Bukhari ."
797,"Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aapney Namaz shuru ki to haath utha kar Allahu-akbar kaha, phir apna kapda lapet liya , phir daayan haath baaeyn par rakha, jab rukoo karney ka irada kya to kapdey se haath nikaley, raful-yadain kya aur Allahu-akbar kaha, phir rukoo kya, jab (Sami-Allahu-liman hamida) kaha to rafaul-yadain kya, aur jab sajda kya to dono haathon ke darmiyan sajda kya. rawahu Muslim ."
798,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, logon ko hukm diya jata tha ke her aadmi dorane-namaz apna daayan haath baain bazu par rakhey . Bukhari ."
799,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ke liye khadey ho jatey to Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir jab rukoo kartey to Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir jab rukoo se sar uthatey to ''Sami-Allahu-liman hamida'' farmatey, phir aap haalate-qiyam mein '' ربنا لک الحمد '' padhtey , phir jab sajde ke liye jhuktey to Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir jab sajde se sar uthatey to Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir jab sajda kartey to Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir jab sajdey se sar uthatey to Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir Namaz mukammal honey tak isi tarah kartey aur jab do rakatein padh kar bethney ke baad khadey hotey to Allahu-akbar kehtey they. muttafaq aleh."
800,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' lambey qiyam wali Namaz sab se afzal hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
801,"Hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke das Sahaba ki mojudgi mein farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke mutalliq main tum sab se ziyada janta hun, unhoney farmaya : bayan karo ! unhoney farmaya : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ka irada farmatey to kandhon ke barabar haath uthatey, phir Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir qirat kartey, phir Allahu-akbar keh kar kandhon ke barabar haath uthatey , phir rukoo kartey aur apni hatheliyan ghutnon par rakh detey , phir barabar ho jatey , aap sar ko jhukaatey na buland kartey, phir sar uthatey to ''Sami-Allahu-liman hamida'' kehtey, phir kandhon ke barabar haath uthatey aur itminan ke sath barabar khadey ho jatey, phir Allahu-akbar kehtey aur sajde ke liye zamin ki taraf jhuk jatey, aap apney haath pehluon se door rakhtey, paaon ki ungliyan kholtey, phir sar uthatey, baeyn paaon ko modtey aur is par beth jatey, aur is qadr itminan se bethtey ke her haddi apni jagah par aa jati, aur itminan se bethey rehtey, phir sajda kartey, phir Allahu-akbar kehtey huey uthtey, baayan paaon modtey aur is par beth jatey, aur is qadr itminan se bethtey ke her haddi apni jagah par aa jati, phir khadey hotey, phir dusri rakaat mein isi tarah kartey, phir jab dusri rakaat ke baad khadey hotey to Allahu-akbar keh kar kandhon ke barabar raful-yadain kartey jaisa ke Namaz shuru kartey waqt kya tha, phir apni baqiya Namaz mein bhi aisey hi kya kartey they, yahan tak ke jab aakhiri sajda hota jiskey baad salam pherna hota to aap apna baayan paaon bahar nikal liya kartey aur baain karwat par beth jatey, aur phir salam phertey, unhon ( das Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : aapney durust kaha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi Namaz padha kartey they. Abu-Dawud, Darmi, jabkey Tirmizi, aur ibne-Maja ne bhi isi maana mein riwayat kya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. Abu-Dawud mein abu-Humaid se marwi (bayan) hadees mein hai : phir aapney rukoo kya to haath ghutnon par rakhey goya aapney unhen pakda hua hai, aapney haathon ko kamaan ke chilley ki tarah kar diya aur unhen pehluon se door rakha, aur unhoney bayan kya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phir sajda kya to naak aur peshani ko zamin par rakha, haathon ko pehluon se door rakha, aur hatheliyon ko kandhon ke barabar rakha, aur raanon ko kushada rakha aur pet ka koi hissey unke sath lagney na diya, yahan tak ke (sajde sey) farigh ho gaey, phir beth gaey to baaeyn paaon ko bichha diya aur daain paaon ke panjey ko qibla rukh kar liya, daain haath ko daain ghutney par aur baaein hath ko baain ghutney par rakh diya aur angushte-shahadat se ishara kya. Abu-Dawood ki dusri riwayat mein hai : jab aap do rakaton ke baad bethey to aap baain paaon par bethey aur daain paaon ko khada kya, aur jab chauthi rakaat ke baad bethey to aapney baain peeth ko zamin ke sath mila diya (yani baain peeth par bethey (aur dono paaon eik hi taraf nikal diye. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Darmi w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
802,Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap Namaz ke liye khadey huey to haathon ko kandhon ke barabar uthaya aur anguthon ko kanon ke barabar kya phir Allahu-akbar kaha. aur Abu-Dawood hi ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) anguthon ko kanon ki lo tak uthaya kartey they.
803,"Hazrat Qabisa bin Hulb (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid (Hulb (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen Namaz padhatey to aap daain haath se baaeyn ko pakad letey. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja."
804,"Hazrat Rifaa bin Raafe bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi aaya, usney masjid mein Namaz padhi, phir bani (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam kya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Namaz dobara padho , kyonkey tum ne Namaz nahin padhi .'' usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey sikha den ke main kaisey Namaz padhun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum qibla rukh ho jaao to Allahu-akbar kaho , phir Sura Fatiha aur jo chaho sura padho, jab (rukoo sey) utho to kamar sidhi karo aur sar uthaao yahan tak ke haddiyan apney jodon mein wapis aa jaeyn, jab sajda karo to khub achi tarah sajda karo, jab (sajdey sey) utho to baain raan par betho , phir her rukoo w sujood mein aisey hi karo yahan tak ke itminan ho jaey.'' ye masaabeh ke alfaz hain, Imam Abu-Dawud ne kuch tabdili ke sath usey riwayat kya hai, Imam Tirmizi aur Imam Nasai ne usi maana mein riwayat kya hai, aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai : farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz ka irada karo to Allah ki taalim w hukm ke mutabiq wuzu karo phir kalma shahadat padho, (baaz ne kaha : Azan do) phir iqaamat kaho, agar tumhen Quran yad ho to Quran padho, warna (alhamdulillah, Allahu-akbar, aur la Ilaah illallah) padho aur phir rukoo karo.'' , ( rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Nasai ( ."
805,"Hazrat Fazal-bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Namaz do rakaat hai, her do rakaat ke baad tashahud padh, khushu w khuzoo aur hamari aajizi w be-chaargi ka izhar kar, phir haath buland karkey apney rab se dua kar, aur jisney aisey na kya to wo is tarah, is tarah hai.'' aur eik-doosri riwayat mein hai : ''to wo naqis hai.''"
806,"Hazrat Saeed bin Haris bin-Mualla (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamen Namaz padhaai to unhoney jab sajdon se sar uthaya , jab sajda kya aur jab do rakaton ke baad khadey huey to buland aawaz se Allahu-akbar kaha, aur farmaya : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey dekha hai. Bukhari ."
807,"Hazrat Ikrima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Makka main eik buzurg ke peechey Namaz padhi to unhoney baais martaba Allahu-akbar kaha, to maine ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ye to ahmaq hai, unhoney kaha : teri maa tujhey gum paey , ye to abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat hai. Bukhari ."
808,"Hazrat Ali bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se mursal riwayat hai unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz mein jab jhuktey aur jab uthtey to Allahu-akbar kaha kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) puri zindagi isi tarah Namaz padhtey rahey . rawahu Malik."
809,"Hazrat Alqama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kya main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz na padhaaun, chunanche unhoney sirf Namaz ke aaghaz par Allahu-akbar kehtey huey haath uthaey . Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai , aur Abu-Dawood ne farmaya is maana mein ye hadees sahih nahin."
810,"Hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to qibla rukh ho kar haath uthatey aur ''Allah akbar '' kehtey . rawahu ibne-Maja ."
811,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen namaze-Zohar padhaai , pichli safon mein kisi aadmi ne Namaz mein kharabi ki, jab salam phera to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bulaya : '' falan shakhs ! kya tum Allah se nahin dartey, kya tum nahin dekhtey ke tum kaisi Namaz padhtey ho, kya tum samajhtey ho ke tum jo kartey ho wo mujh sey chhupa rehta hai, Allah ki qism ! main jis tarah apney aagey dekhta hun wesay hi apney peechey dekhta hun.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
812,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) takbire-tahrima aur qirat ke darmiyan kuch der sukoot farmaya kartey they, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! merey waliden aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par qurban hon, aap takbire-tehrima aur qirat ke darmiyan jo sukoot farmatey hain usmein kya padhtey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main ye dua padhta hun : aey Allah ! merey aur merey gunahon ke darmiyan aisey doori dal dey jaisey to ne mashriq w maghrib ke beech doori dali hai, aey Allah! mujhey gunahon se aisey paak saaf kar dey jis tarah safed kapda mail se saaf kar diya jata hai, aey Allah ! merey gunahon ko pani , barf aur olon se dho dey .''"
813,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ka irada farmatey, aur eik riwayat mein hai : jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz shuru kya kartey to takbir keh kar ye dua padha kartey : ''maine yaksoo ho kar apney chehrey ko us zaat ki taraf mutawajjeh kya jisney zamin w aasman ko adam se takhleeq farmaya , aur main mushrikon mein se nahin hun, be-shak meri Namaz , meri qurbani , mera jeena aur mera marna dono jahan ke rab , Allah ke liye hai, uska koi shareek nahin, mujhey usi ka hukm diya gaya hai aur main musalmanon ( itaat guzaaron ( mein se hun, aey Allah ! to Malik hai, to mera rab hai aur main tera banda hun, maine apni jaan par zulm kya, maine apney gunahon ka aetraaf kya, pas to merey sarey gunah maaf kar dey , kyonkey terey siwa koi gunah bakhsh nahin sakta , behtareen akhlaq ki taraf meri raahnumai farma, achey akhlaq ki taraf sirf tu hi raahnumai kar sakta hai, burey akhlaq mujh se door kar dey , kyonkey sirf tu hi burey akhlaq mujh se door kar sakta hai, main teri ibadat par qaaim hun aur ye merey liye baais sa'adat hai, tamam khair w bhalai terey haathon mein hai, jabkey burai teri taraf mansub nahin ki ja sakti , main terey hukm w tofiq se hun aur lot kar teri hi taraf aana hai, to barkat wala buland shaan wala hai, main tujh se maghfirat talab karta hun aur teri taraf ruju karta hun.'' aur jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rukoo kartey to ye dua padhtey : ''aey Allah ! maine terey liye rukoo kya, tujh par eman laya, teri itaat ikhtiyar ki, merey kaan, meri aankhen, mera dimagh, meri haddiyan aur merey aasaab ne terey liye hi tawazeh ikhtiyar ki .'' jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( rukoo sey) sar uthatey to ye dua padhtey : ''aey Allah ! hamarey rab ! her qism ki tareef terey hi liye hai jis se aasman w zamin aur jo uskey darmiyan hai bhar jaey, aur uskey baad us chiz ke bharaw ke barabar jo to chahey.'' aur jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sajda kartey to ye dua kartey : ''aey Allah ! maine terey liye sajda kya, tujh par eman laya , teri itaat ikhtiyar ki, merey chehrey ne us zaat ko sajda kya jisney usey paida farmaya , uski tasweer w surat banai , usko sama w basar se nawaza, barkat wala Allah behtareen takhleeq karney wala hai.'' phir aakhir par tashahud aur salam pherney ke darmiyan ye dua kartey : ''aey Allah! to merey agley pichley, poshida aur zahir gunah aur jo maine ziyadti ki aur wo gunah jinkey mutalliq to mujh se bhi ziyada janta hai, sab maaf farma, tu hi taraqqi deney wala aur tu hi tanazzul ki janib ley jaaney wala hai, terey siwa koi mabud nahin.'' aur Shafai (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : ''aur burai teri taraf mansub nahin ki ja sakti, hidayat wala wo hai jisey to hidayat ata farmaey, main teri tofiq se hun aur mera lotna bhi teri hi taraf hai, najat w panah sirf tujh se mil sakti hai, to barkat wala hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
814,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi aa kar saf mein shamil ho gaya uski saans phooli hui thi, usney kaha : Allah sab se bada hai, Allah ke liye hamd hai, hamd bahut ziyada, pakizah aur ba-barkat. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni Namaz mukammal kar li to farmaya : ''tum mein se ye kalmaat kis ne kahey they?'' tamam Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) khamosh rahey, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kalimat kis ne kahey they?'' wo phir khamosh rahey, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kalimat kis ne kahey they, usney koi qabil muwaakhiza baat nahin ki.'' eik aadmi ne arz kya : main aaya to meri saans phool chuki thi, chunanche wo kalmaat maine kahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine baara farishton ko un kalimaat ki taraf sabqat kartey huey dekha ke un mein se kon unhen ooper lekar jaey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
815,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz shuru kartey to ye dua kya kartey they : ''aey Allah! to paak hai, teri tareef ke sath (ham teri pakizgi bayan kartey hain) tera naam ba-barkat hai, teri shaan buland hai aur terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
816,"Hazrat ibne-Maja ne usey abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ham is hadees ko sirf Harisa ke wastey se jantey hain. jabkey uski kamzor yaaddaasht ki wajah se is par kalam kya gaya hai."
817,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Namaz padhtey huey dekha to (us waqt (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye padh rahey they farmaya : ''Allah bahut hi bada hai, Allah bahut hi bada hai, Allah bahut hi bada hai, Allah ke liye bahut ziyada tareef hai, Allah ke liye bahut ziyada tareef hai, Allah ke liye bahut ziyada tareef hai, teen martaba farmaya : Allah ke liye subh w Sham pakizgi hai, main shetan se uski phunk , uskey waswasey aur uskey khatrey se Allah ki panah chahta hun.'' Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja , albatta ibne-Maja ne (wal-hamdulillahi kaseera) ka zikr nahin kya, aur unhoney aakhir par : (minash-shaitaanir-rajeem) ka zikr kya, aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : uski phunk se murad kibr, uskey waswasey se murad sher aur uskey khatrey se junoon murad hai."
818,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se do saktey yad kiye , eik sakta jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) takbire-tehrima kehtey aur eik sakta jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (غیر المغضوب علیھم wla الضالین) ki qirat se farigh hotey , Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki tasdeeq ki . Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
819,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dusri rakaat ke liye khadey hotey to ( Alhamdulillahi rabbil-aalameen) se qirat shuru kartey they, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sakta nahin farmatey they. sahih Muslim mein isi tarah hai, Humaidi ne usey Imam Muslim ke mufridaat mein zikr kya, aur isi tarah sahabul-jaame ne usey sirf Muslim se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Muslim ."
820,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz shuru kartey to takbir keh kar ye dua padha kartey they : '' be-shak meri Namaz , meri qurbani , mera jeena aur mera marna Allah , dono jahano ke rab ke liye hai, mujhey isi ka hukm diya gaya hai aur main pehla itaat-guzar hun, aey Allah! behtareen aamaal w akhlaq ki taraf meri raahnumai farma, un behtareen aamaal w akhlaq ki taraf sirf tu hi rehnumai kar sakta hai, burey aamaal aur burey akhlaq se mujhey bacha, un burey aamaal w akhlaq se sirf tu hi bacha sakta hai.'' rawahu Nasai ."
821,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nafl Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to Allahu-akbar keh kar ye dua farmatey : ''maine yaksoo ho kar apney chehrey ko us zaat ki taraf mutawajjeh kar liya jisney zero se zamin w aasman ko paida farmaya, aur main mushrikon mein se nahin hun.'' aur unhon ( Muhammad bin Muslima ( ne Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ke jaisi hadees zikr ki, albatta unhoney (وانا من المسلمین)  ''main musalman hun, zikr kya hai, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! tu hi badshah hai, terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur ham teri hamd ke sath teri pakizgi bayan kartey hain.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qirat farmatey . rawahu Nasai ."
822,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne (Namaz mein) Sura Fatiha nahin padhi uski koi Namaz nahin.'' Bukhari, Muslim. muttafaq aleh. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : '' (us ki Namaz nahin hoti ( jo Sura Fatiha aur kuch zayed na padhey .''"
823,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Namaz padhi lekin is mein Sura Fatiha na padhi to wo ( Namaz ( naqis hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye teen martaba farmaya : '' mukammal nahin .'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya : ham Imam ke peechey hotey hain, unhoney farmaya : usey apney dil mein padho, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah taala ne farmaya : maine Namaz (yani Sura faatiha) ko apney aur apney bandey ke darmiyan aadha-aadha taqseem kar diya, aur merey bandey ne jo sawal kya wo usey mil gaya, chunanche jab banda kehta hai : '' her qism ki hamd Allah hi ke liye hai jo tamam jahano ka rab hai.'' Allah Taala farmata hai : merey bandey ne meri hamd bayan ki, aur jab banda kehta hai : ''jo bahut meharban , nihayat rehem wala hai.'' Allah Taala farmata hai : merey bandey ne meri sana bayan ki, jab kehta hai : '' yome-jaza ka Malik hai.'' Allah farmata hai : merey bandey ne meri shaan w shokat bayan ki, jab banda kehta hai : '' ham teri hi ibadat kartey hain aur tujh hi se madad chahtey hain.'' Allah farmata hai : ye merey aur merey bandey ke darmiyan hai, aur merey bandey ke liye wo kuch hai jo usney sawal kya, aur jab banda kehta hai : '' hamen sidhi raah dikha , un logon ki raah jin par tu ney inaam kya, unki nahin jin par tera ghazab hua aur na un logon ki raah jo gumrah huey .'' Allah Taala farmata hai : ''ye merey bandey ke liye hai aur merey bandey ke liye wo hai jis ka usney sawal kya. '' rawahu Muslim ."
824,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu) (Alhamdulillahi rabbil aalameen) se Namaz shuru kya kartey they.
825,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Imam Aameen kahey to tum Aameen kaho, kyonkey jiski Aameen farishton ki Aameen ke muwaafiq ( sath (ho gaee uskey sabiqa gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''jab Imam (غیر المغضوب علیھم wla الضالین) kahiye to tum Aameen kaho, kyonkey jis ka qol farishton ke qol ke muwaafiq ho gaya, uskey sabiqa gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' ye alfaz Bukhari ke hain aur Muslim ki riwayat bhi isi tarah hai. muttafaq aleh. aur Bukhari ki dusri riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab qaari (Imam) Aameen kahey to tum Aameen kaho , kyonkey farishtey bhi Aameen kehtey hain, jiski Aameen farishton ki Aameen ke muwaafiq ho gaee uskey sabiqa gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.''"
826,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz padhney ka irada karo to safein durust karo, phir tum mein se tumhen koi Namaz padhaaey , pas jab wo Allahu-akbar kahey to tum Allahu-akbar kaho , aur jab wo ( غیر المغضوب علیھم wla الضالین ( kahey to tum Aameen kaho , Allah tumhari dua qubul farmaeyga , jab wo Allahu-akbar kahey aur rukoo karey to tum Allahu-akbar kaho aur rukoo karo, kyonkey Imam tum se pehley rukoo karta hai aur tum se pehley ( rukoo sey) uthta hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ( pehley sar uthana ( uskey ( pehley rukoo janey (ka badla hai, aur jab wo kahey : ( Sami-Allahu-liman hamida ( ''Allah ne sun liya jisney uski tareef ki '' , to tum kaho : aey Allah ! her qism ki hamd terey hi liye hai, Allah tumhari dua sunta aur qubul farmata hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
827,aur Muslim ki Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees mein hai : '' aur jab wo qirat karey to tum khamosh raho .'' rawahu Muslim .
828,"Hazrat abu-Qatada bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki pehli do rakaaton mein Sura Fatiha aur do suraten jabkey dusri do rakaaton mein Sura Fatiha padha kartey they aur kabhi kabhar aap hamen koi aayat suna diya kartey they, aap jis qadr pehli rakaat mein qirat lambi kya kartey they is qadr dusri mein lambi nahin kya kartey they, aur aap isi tarah Asr mein aur isi tarah Fajr mein kya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
829,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham namaze-Zohar w Asr mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qiyam ka andaza lagaya kartey they, pas ham ne Zohar ki pehli do rakaaton mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qiyam ka andaza Sura sajda ki qirat ke barabar lagaya, aur eik-doosri riwayat mein hai her rakaat mein tees aayaat ke barabar tha, aur ham ne aakhiri do rakaaton mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qiyam ka andaza lagaya to wo us se nisf tha, ham ne Asr ki pehli do rakaaton ka andaza lagaya to wo Zohar ki aakhiri do rakaaton ke qiyam ke barabar tha jabkey Asr ki aakhiri do rakatein uski (pehli do rakaaton) se aadhi thin. rawahu Muslim."
830,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-Zohar mein) واللیل اذا یغشیٰ) aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai, ( سبح اسم ربک الاعلٰی) aur Asr mein usi tarah, jabkey namaze-Fajr mein us se ziyada lambi qirat kya kartey they. rawahu Muslim."
831,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaze-Maghrib mein Sura taur padhtey huey suna . muttafaq aleh."
832,"Hazrat Umme- Fazal bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaze-Maghrib mein) والمرسلات عرفاً ( padhtey huey suna . muttafaq aleh."
833,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz ( Isha ( padha kartey they, phir ja kar apni qom ki imaamat karatey they, eik raat unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz Isha padhi, phir apni qom ke paas gaey aur unhen Namaz padhaai to unhoney Sura Baqra shuru kar di, eik aadmi ne alag ho kar salam pher diya, phir akeley hi Namaz padh kar chala gaya to Sahaba ne usey kaha : aey falan! kya to munafiq ho gaya hai? usney kaha : nahin, Allah ki qasam! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar aap se shikayat karunga, chunanche wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham oonton par pani la kar kheton aur baghaat ko sairab karney waley log hain, din bhar kaam kaaj kartey hain, aur ye Muaz hain ke unhoney aap ke sath Namaze-Isha ada ki, phir apni qom ke paas aaye to unhoney Sura Baqra shuru kar di, pas (ye sun kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Muaz ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''Muaz! kya tum logon ko fitney mein mubtala karna chahtey ho? tum (والشمس وضحھا) , ( واللیل اذا یغشیٰ) aur ( سبح اسم ربک الاعلٰی) padha karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
834,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Namaz Isha mein) والتین والزیتون ( padhtey huey suna, aur maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ziyada achchi aawaz wala koi aur nahin suna . muttafaq aleh."
835,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-Fajr mein Sura Qaaf aur is tarah ki suraten padha kartey they, aur us (yani namaze-Fajr) ke baad aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baqi namazein mukhtasar hoti thin. rawahu Muslim."
836,Hazrat Amr bin Hurais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaze-Fajr mein (واللیل اذا عسعس) padhtey huey suna . rawahu Muslim .
837,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen Makka mein namaze-Fajr padhaai to aapney Sura mominoon shuru ki yahan tak ke Musa w Harun (Alaihimussalam) ka zikr aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko roney ki wajeh se khaansi aaney lagi jis par aapney rukoo kar diya. rawahu Muslim ."
838,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Juma ke roz namaze-Fajr ki pehli rakaat mein Sura sajda aur dusri rakaat mein Sura dahar padha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
839,"Hazrat Ubaidullah bin abi Raafe bayan kartey hain, Marwan Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko Madina ka khalifa muqarrar karkey khud Makka tashrif ley gaey, chunanche unhoney hamen Namaz Juma padhaai to unhoney pehli rakaat mein Sura Juma aur dusri rakaat mein Sura munafiqoon padhi to phir unhoney farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Juma ke roz ye suraten padhtey huey suna . rawahu Muslim ."
840,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz eidain aur Namaz Juma mein Sura Aala aur Sura Ghashiya padha kartey they, aur unhoney farmaya : agar eid Juma ke roz aa jati to phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dono namazon mein yehi dono suraten tilawat farmatey . rawahu Muslim ."
841,Hazrat Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Waqid Leshi (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-azha aur eidul-fitr mein kon si suraten tilawat kya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un dono mein Sura Qaaf aur Sura Qamar tilawat kya kartey they. rawahu Muslim .
842,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fajr ki do rakaaton ( sunnaton) mein Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas tilawat farmaai. rawahu Muslim .
843,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki rakaaton mein Sura Baqra ki aayaat (قولو امنا باللہ وما انزل الینا)  aur Sura Aale-Imran se ( قل  یا اھل الکتاب تعالوا الیٰ کلمۃ سواء بیننا وبینکم ( padha kartey they. rawahu Muslim ."
844,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni Namaz Bismillah se shuru kya kartey they. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : is hadees ki sanad qawi nahin. rawahu Tirmizi ."
845,"Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna ke aapney ( غیر المغضوب علیھم wla الضالین ( padha to buland aawaz sey, Aameen ''kaha . rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Darmi w ibne-Maja ."
846,"Hazrat abu-Zuhair Numairi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nikley to ham eik aadmi ke paas se guzrey jo badi aajizi ke sath Allah se dua kar raha tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar usney dua khatam ki to ( jannat w maghfirat ( wajib kar li.'' logon mein se kisi aadmi ne arz kya : wo kis chiz ke sath khatam karey? farmaya : ''aameen ke sath.''"
847,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Maghrib ki do rakaaton mein Sura Aaraf tilawat farmaai. rawahu Nasai .
848,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main dorane-safar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki oontni ki muhar thaam kar aagey aagey chala karta tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Aqba ! kya main tumhen padhi janey wali do behtareen suraten na sikhaaun? '' aapney Sura Falaq aur Sura Naas mujhey sikhaain, raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un Suraton ki wajeh se mujhey ziyada khush na dekha, pas jab aap Namaz subh ke liye tashrif laye to aapney namaze-Fajr padhatey huey yehi do suraten tilawat farmaain, jab Namaz se farigh huey to meri taraf tawajjoh kartey huey farmaya : '' Aqba ! tum ne ( un Suraton ki azmat ko) kaisey dekha ?'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
849,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Juma ki raat namaze-Maghrib mein Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas tilawat kya kartey they."
850,"Hazrat ibne-Maja ne usey ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai, lekin unhoney Juma ki raat ka zikr nahin kya."
851,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko , maghrib ke baad do rakaaton mein aur Fajr se pehley do rakaaton mein, Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas itni martaba padhtey huey suna ke main shumar nahin kar sakta."
852,"Hazrat ibne-Maja ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai, lekin unhoney ''maghrib ke baad'' ka zikr nahin kya."
853,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : maine falan shakhs ke siwa kisi ke peechey aisi Namaz nahin padhi jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke bahut mushabeh ho, Suleman (Alaihissalam) (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain maine us ( falan shakhs (ke peechey Namaz padhi to wo Zohar ki pehli do rakatein lambi aur aakhiri do rakatein halki padha kartey they, aur namaze-Asr halki padha kartey they jabkey namaze-Maghrib mein qasaar mufassal ( Sura Bayena se aakhir tak) Isha mein ausaat mufassal (Buruj se Bayena tak) aur Fajr mein tawaal mufassal ( Sura Hujurat se Buruj tak) padha kartey they. Nasai, aur ibne-Maja ne ''namaze-Asr halki padha kartey they"", tak riwayat kya hai."
854,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham namaze-Fajr mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey they. aapney qirat ki to aap par qirat giraan ho gaee, chunanche jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Namaz sey) farigh ho gaey to farmaya : ''shayad ke tum apney Imam ke peechey qirat kartey ho?'' ham ne arz kya, ji haan, Allah ke Rasool! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Sura Fatiha ke ilawa qirat na kya karo, kyonkey jo usey nahin padhta uski Namaz nahin hoti .'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai bil-maana. aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main bhi) apney dil mein) kehta tha ke Quran padhna mujh par dushwaar kyon hai, jab main buland aawaz se qirat karun to tum Sura Fatiha ke siwa kuch na padha karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Nasai."
855,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni kisi Jehri qirat wali Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : ''kya tum mein se kisi shakhs ne abhi-abhi merey sath qirat ki hai?'' to eik aadmi ne arz kya, ji haan, Allah ke Rasool! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main bhi) dil mein) kehta tha, mujhey kya hua hai ke mujh se Quran china ja raha hai, munasib bayan kartey hain : Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye baat suni to wo jehri qirat wali namazon mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath qirat karney se ruk gaey . Malik , Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai , aur ibne-Maja ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
856,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur bayazi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' namazi apney rab se kalam karta hai, pas usey ghor karna chahiye ke wo uskey sath kya kalam kar raha hai? eik doosrey ke paas buland aawaz se Quran na padha karo.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
857,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Imam to isliye banaya jata hai ke uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey, pas jab wo Allahu-akbar keh chukey to phir tum Allahu-akbar kaho, aur jab wo qirat karey to tum khamosh raho .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
858,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya : main Quran se kuch bhi yad nahin kar sakta , lihaza mujhey aap kuch sikha den jo merey liye kafi ho, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kaho سبحان اللہ والحمدللہ wala الہ الا اللہ و اللہ اکبر wala حول wala قوۃ الا باللہ''Allah paak hai, her qism ki hamd w sataaish usi ke liye hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, Allah sab se bada hai, aur gunah se bachna aur neki karna mehaz Allah ki tofiq se hai.'' us shakhs ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! ye to Allah ke liye mukhtas hai, to merey liye kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kaho : اللھم ارحمنی و عافنی و اھدنی و ارزقنی''aey Allah ! mujh par rehem farma , mujhey aafiyat ata farma , mujhey hidayat nasib farma aur mujhey rizq ata farma .'' pas us shakhs ne apney haathon se ishara kya aur unhen band kya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jahan tak us aadmi ka talluq hai to usney apney haath khair se bhar liye .'' Abu-Dawood . aur Imam Nasai (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat : ( illa billah ( tak hai."
859,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Sura Aala padhtey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : سبحان ربی الاعلیٰ
860,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jo shakhs Sura Teen ki tilawat karey aur jab wo sura ki aakhiri aayaat par pahunchey to wo kahey : بلیٰ : وانا علیٰ ذلک من الشاھدین ""kyon nahin, aisey hi hai, aur main is par gawah hun.'' aur jo shakhs Sura Qiyama ki tilawat karey aur aakhiri aayat ""kya wo is par qadir nahin ke wo mardon ko zinda karey.'' par pahunchey to wo kahey : ( بلیٰ ( ''kyon nahin, wo zarur qadir hai.'' aur jo shakhs Mursalaat ki tilawat karey, aur wo aakhiri aayat ''uskey baad wo kis hadees par eman laeyngey''. par pahunchey to wo kahey : (aamanna billah) ''ham Allah par eman laye.'' Abu-Dawud, aur Imam Tirmizi ne : وانا علیٰ ذلک من الشاھدین tak riwayat kya hai."
861,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney Sahaba ke paas tashrif laye aur unhen puri Sura Rehman sunai to wo khamosh rahey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis raat jin aaye, maine jab ( فبای الاء ربکما تکذبن ( ''tum apney rab ki kon kon se nematon ko jhutlaaogey.'' padha, to unhoney bahut achcha jawab diya tha, kaha : hamarey rab ! ham teri nematon mein se kisi chiz ko bhi nahin jhutlatey , aur her qism ki hamd terey liye hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
862,Hazrat Muaz bin Johni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke juhaina qabiley ke eik aadmi ne unhen bataya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna ke aapney Fajr ki do rakaaton mein Sura Zilzal tilawat farmaai. mein nahin janta ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bhool kar aisey kya ya janbujhkar. rawahu Abu-Dawood .
863,Hazrat Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ne namaze-Fajr padhi to unhoney dono rakaaton mein Sura Baqra tilawat farmaai .
864,"Hazrat Farafisa bin Umer Hanfi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Sura Yusuf , Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ki qirat se yad ki ke wo namaze-Fajr mein kasrat ke sath uski tilawat kya kartey they. rawahu Malik."
865,"Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechey namaze-Fajr padhi to unhoney dono rakaaton mein tajweed ke sath Sura Yusuf aur Sura Haj tilawat farmaai , un se puchha gaya ke tab to wo tulu Fajr ke sath hi Namaz shuru kartey hongey, unhoney kaha : haan! rawahu Malik."
866,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine mufassal Suraton (yani Hujurat se aakhir tak) mein se her chhoti badi sura ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaban Mubarak se suna ke aap farz namazon ki imaamat karatey huey unki tilawat farmaya kartey they."
867,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Utba bin Masood bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Maghrib mein Sura Dukhan tilawat farmaai. Imam Nasai ne usey mursal riwayat kya hai. rawahu Nasai."
868,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''rukoo w sujood mukammal kya karo, Allah ki qasam! main tumhen apney peechey bhi dekhta hun.'' muttafaq aleh."
869,"Hazrat Bara bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka rukoo, aapke sujood, sajdon ke darmiyan bethna (jalsa istiraahat) aur jab aap rukoo se khadey hotey (qauma) to qiyam w tashahud ke ilawa ye sab taqriban barabar they. muttafaq aleh."
870,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ( Sami-Allahu-liman hamida ( kehtey to aap khadey rehtey yahan tak ke ham ( dil mein) kehtey ke aap ko weham dal diya gaya hai, phir aap sajda kartey aur aap do sajdon ke darmiyan bethtey yahan tak ke ham ( dil mein) kehtey ke aap ko weham dal diya gaya hai. rawahu Muslim ."
871,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney rukoo w sujood mein kasrat ke sath ye dua kya kartey they : ''aey hamarey parwardigar ! to paak hai, ham teri tareef bayan kartey hain, aey Allah! mujhey bakhsh dey'', aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Quran par amal kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
872,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney rukoo w sujood mein ye dua kya kartey they : '' (mera rukoo w sujood us zaat ke liye hai jo) farishton aur Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ka rab nihayat paak w muqaddas hai.'' rawahu Muslim .
873,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey rukoo w sujood mein Quran padhney se mana kya gaya hai, raha rukoo to is mein rab ki azmat bayan karo, aur rahey sujood to un mein khub dua karo, pas tumhari dua qubuliyat ke laaiq hogi.'' rawahu Muslim ."
874,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Imam ''Sami-Allahu-liman hamida'' kahey to tum kaho : ''(اللھم ربنا لک الحمد) kyonkey jis ka ye qol farishton ke qol ke muwaafiq ho gaya to uskey sabiqa gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey .'' muttafaq aleh."
875,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi Bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rukoo se apni kamar uthatey to aap ye dua padhtey : ''Allah ne sun liya jisney uski tareef ki, aey Allah ! hamarey rab ! sari tareef terey hi liye hai aasmano , zamin aur her us chiz ke bharaaw ke barabar jo to chahey .'' rawahu Muslim ."
876,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rukoo se sar uthatey to aap ye dua padha kartey they : ''aey Allah ! hamarey rab ! her qism ki tareef terey liye hai, aasmano aur zamin aur her us chiz ke bharaaw ke barabar jo to chahey aur bandey ne jo teri tareef aur shaan bayan ki wo terey hi laaiq hai, ham sab terey hi bandey hain, aey Allah ! jo chiz to ata kar dey usey koi rokney wala nahin, jis chiz ko to rok ley usey koi ata karney wala nahin, aur dolat mand ki dolat , terey yahaan koi faeyda nahin dey sakti.'' rawahu Muslim ."
877,"Hazrat Rifa bin Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey Namaz padh rahey they, pas jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rukoo se sar uthaya to farmaya : ''Sami-Allahu-liman hamida.'' aap ke peechey eik aadmi ne kaha : hamarey rab! terey hi wastey tareef hai, bahut ziyada pakizah aur ba-barkat tareef. jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : '' abhi bolney wala kon tha ?'' us aadmi ne kaha : main ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tees se zayed farishton ko dekha ke wo jaldi kar rahey they ke unka sawab sab se pehley kon likhta hai.'' Bukhari ."
878,"Hazrat abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak aadmi rukoo w sujood main apni kamar mukammal taur par barabar nahin karta uski Namaz durust nahin hoti.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai , ibne-Maja, Darmi, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
879,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab (فسبح باسم ربک العظیم) nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey apney rukoo mein padha karo.'' aur jab (سبح اسم ربک الاعلیٰ) nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey apney sajdon mein padha karo.'' Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja w Darmi."
880,"Hazrat Aun bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi eik rukoo karta hai aur apney rukoo mein teen martaba ( subhan rabil azeem) padhta hai to apna rukoo mukammal kar leta hey, aur ye uska kam se kam darja hai, aur jab wo sajda karta hai aur apney sajdon mein teen martaba ( subhan rabil aala) padh leta hai to wo apna sajda mukammal kar leta hai, aur ye ( tadaad ( uska kam se kam darja hai. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja . Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : iski sanad muttasil nahin, kyonkey Aun ki ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat nahin hui ."
881,"Hazrat Huzefa se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi , aap apney rukoo mein) subhan rabil-azeem) aur sujood mein) subhan rabiyal-aala) padha kartey they, jab aap kisi aayat rehmat par pahunchey to waqf farma kar rehmat talab kartey aur jab kisi aayat azab par pahunchtey to waqf farma kar Allah ki panah talab kartey. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Darmi , aur Nasai w ibne-Maja ne ( الاعلیٰ ( tak riwayat kya, aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
882,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ( haalate-Namaz mein) qiyam kya, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rukoo kya to Sura Baqra ki qirat ke barabar rukoo mein rahey aur ye dua kartey rahey : ''qahar aur ghalbey, badshahat w kibriyaai aur azmat wala rab paak hai.'' rawahu Nasai."
883,"Hazrat ibne-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad kisi aisey shakhs ke peechey Namaz nahin padhi jiski Namaz, is nojawan yani umr bin Abdul-Azeez ke siwa , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke mushabeh ho, raawi ne kaha, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ham ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke rukoo w sujood ki tasbeehaat ka andaza das das martaba ka lagaya . rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
884,"Hazrat Shaqiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik aadmi ko na mukammal rukoo w sujood kartey huey dekha, jab wo Namaz padh chuka to unhoney usey bulaya , Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey farmaya : tum ne Namaz nahin padhi , raawi bayan kartey hain, mera khayal hai ke unhoney kaha : agar tum ( isi tarah ( faut ho jatey to tum us fitrat w millat par faut na hotey jis par Allah ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko paida farmaya. Bukhari ."
885,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se bura chor wo hai jo apni Namaz ki chori karta hai.'' Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! wo apni Namaz ki chori kaisey karta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo uska rukoo w sujood mukammal nahin karta .'' rawahu Ahmed ."
886,"Hazrat Noman bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum sharab nosh, zaani aur chor ke barey mein kya guman kartey ho?'' raawi kehtey hain, ye unke barey mein hudood (sharai sazaaeyn) nazil honey se pehley ki baat hai, Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo kabeera gunah hain aur un par saza hai, aur sab se badi chori wo hai jo apni Namaz ki chori karta hai.'' Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! wo apni Namaz ki kaisey chori karta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo uska rukoo w sujood mukammal nahin karta.'' malik, Ahmed, jabkey Darmi ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
887,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey, saat aaza : peshani, dono haathon, dono ghutnon aur paaon ki ungliyon ke kinaron par sajda karney aur (dorane-namaz) kapdon aur baalon ko na sametney ka hukm diya gaya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
888,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sujood mein aetidaal rakho , tum mein se koi shakhs apney bazu kuttey ki tarah na bichhaaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
889,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum sajda karo to apni hatheliyan (jaey Namaz par) aur apni kohniyan (zameen sey) buland rakho.'' rawahu Muslim."
890,"Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sajda kartey to apney haathon ko pehluon se door rakhtey they yahan tak ke agar bakri ka bachcha aap ke haathon ke nichey se guzarnaa chahta to wo guzar jata . ye Abu-Dawood ki riwayat ke alfaz hain, jaisa ke Baghwi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Sharahus-sunnah main apni sanad se bayan kya hai, aur Muslim mein usi maana ki riwayat hai : Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sajda kartey to agar bakri ka bacha aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke nichey se guzarna chahta to wo guzar sakta tha."
891,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Malik bin Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda kartey to apney haathon ke beech fasla rakhtey yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aa jati . muttafaq aleh."
892,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney sajdon mein ye dua kya kartey they : ''aey Allah! merey chhotey, badey, pehley, pichley, zahir aur poshida tamam gunah maaf farma dey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
893,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bistar par na paya to maine (apney haath sey) aapko tatola to mera haath aapke paaon ke talwey par laga, aap Namaz mein haalate-sajda mein they jabkey aap ke paaon khadey they, aur aap dua kar rahey they : ''aey Allah! main teri razamandi ke zariey terey ghussey sey, teri aafiyat ke zariey teri saza se aur teri rehmat ke zariey terey azab se panah chahta hun, main teri tareef ko shumar nahin kar sakta, to wesa hi hai jis tarah to ne apni tareef khud farmaai hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
894,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''banda sajdey ki haalat mein apney rab ke intehai qarib hota hai, pas (sajdey ki haalat mein) ziyada duayen karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
895,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab ibne-Adam aayate-sajda tilawat karkey sajda karta hai to shetan alag ho kar roney lagta hai, aur kehta hai : haaye afsos! ibne-Adam ko sajdey ka hukm diya gaya to usney sajda kar liya to wo jannat ka mustahiq qarar paya, jabkey mujhey sajdey ka hukm diya gaya to maine inkar kar diya aur jahannam mera muqaddar thehri.'' rawahu Muslim ."
896,"Hazrat Rabeea bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan raat basar kya karta tha, mein aap ke liye wuzu ka pani aur aap ki deegar zarooriyaat ka intizam kya karta tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : '' mujh se koi chiz maango .'' maine arz kya, main aap sey, jannat mein aap ke sath honey ka sawal karta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya iskey ilawa kuch aur ?'' maine arz kya : bas yehi hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pas apni zaat ke liye kasrate-sujood se meri madad kar .'' rawahu Muslim ."
897,"Hazrat Maadaan bin Talha bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke azad karda ghulam Soban se mila to maine kaha : mujhey koi aisa amal bataeyn jisey karkey main jannat mein dakhil ho jaaun, wo khamosh rahey, phir maine un se sawal kya, to wo khamosh rahey, phir maine teesri martaba un se sawal kya to unhoney farmaya : maine uskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha tha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya tha : ''tum Allah ki raza ki khatir kasrat se sajdey karo, kyonkey tum Allah ke liye jo bhi sajda karogey to Allah uskey zariey tumhara eik darja badha dega aur uskey zariey tumhara eik gunah mita dega .'' Maadaan bayan kartey hain, phir main abu-Darda se mila to maine un se bhi puchha to unhoney mujhey wesay hi bataya jaisey Soban ne mujhey bataya tha. rawahu Muslim ."
898,"Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap sajda kartey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney haathon se pehley apney ghutney nichey lagatey aur jab ( qiyam ke liye ( khadey hotey to ghutnon se pehley haath uthatey they."
899,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi sajda karey to wo (haathon se pehley ghutney laga kar) oont ki tarah na bethey, wo ghutnon se pehley apney haath nichey lagaey .'' Abu-Dawud, Nasai , Darmi . abu-Suleman Khattabi ne farmaya : Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees , is hadees se ziyada durust hai, aur ye bhi kaha gaya hai ke ye mansookh hai."
900,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do sajdon ke darmiyan ye dua kya kartey they : ''aey Allah! mujhey bakhsh dey, mujh par rehem farma, meri raahnumai farma, mujhey aafiyat mein rakh aur mujhey rizq ata farma .''"
901,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do sajdon ke darmiyan ye dua padha kartey they : ''merey rab ! mujhey bakhsh dey .'' rawahu Nasai w Darmi .
902,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin shabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kawwey ki tarah thongein maarney, darindey ki tarah bazu bichaney aur oont ki tarah masjid mein apney liye koi jagah makhsus karney se mana farmaya."
903,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Ali ! main jo apney liye pasand karta hun wohi tumharey liye pasand karta hun aur jo apney liye napasand karta hun wohi tumharey liye napasand karta hun, sajdon ke darmiyan peeth nichey laga kar , taangein khadi karkey aur haath zamin par laga kar na betho .''"
904,"Hazrat Talaq bin Ali Hanfi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah azz-w-jall us bandey ki Namaz ki taraf dekhta bhi nahin jo dorane-namaz rukoo w sujood main apni kamar sidhi nahin karta .''"
905,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : jo shakhs apni peshani zamin par rakhey to wo apney haath bhi usi jagah rakhey jahan usney apni peshani rakhi thi, phir jab wo ( peshani ( uthaey to dono haathon ko bhi utha ley, kyonkey haath bhi sajda kartey hain jis tarah chehra sajda karta hai. rawahu Malik."
906,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashahud ke liye bethtey to apna daayan haath apney daain ghutney par aur baayan haath apney baaeyn ghutney par rakhtey aur tirpan ki gireh bana kar shahadat ki ungli se ishara farmatey they. rawahu Muslim ."
907,aur eik riwayat mein hai : jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz mein (tashahud ke liye) bethtey to aap apney dono haath apney dono ghutnon par rakhtey aur daain haath ki shahadat ki ungli buland kartey aur uskey sath ishara farmatey jabkey baaeyn haath ko baain raan par khula rakhtey they. rawahu Muslim .
908,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashahud ke liye bethtey to daayan haath apni daain raan par aur baayan haath apni baain raan par rakhtey aur angusht shahadat se ishara farmatey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna angoothaa apni darmiyani ungli par rakhtey aur apney baaein hath se apney ghutney ko luqmey ki tarah pakad letey. rawahu Muslim ."
909,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey to ham kehtey : Allah par uskey bandon ki taraf se salam ho, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aur mikael (Alaihissalam) par salam ho, falan par salam ho, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to aapney apna rukhe-anwar hamari taraf karkey farmaya : ''tum aisey na kaho : Allah par salam ho, kyonkey Allah to khud salam hai, jab tum mein se koi (tashahud ke liye) Namaz mein baithey to wo yun kahey: '' (meri sari) qouli, badani, aur maali ibadaat sirf Allah ke liye khas hain, aey Nabi aap par Allah ki rehmat, salamti aur barkaten hon aur ham par aur Allah ke doosrey nek bandon par bhi salamti ho, kyonkey jab wo aisey kahega to ye dua zamin w aasman ke her nek bandey ko pahunch jaeygi, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain, phir wo apni pasandida dua karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
910,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen tashahud (us ehtimam ke sath) sikhatey they jaisey hamen Quran ki koi sura sikhatey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : '' (meri sari) qouli, badani aur maali ibadaat Allah ke liye khas hain, aey nabi! aap par Allah ki rehmat, salamti aur barkaten hon, aur ham par aur Allah ke doosrey nek bandon par bhi salamti ho, mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain.'' rawahu Muslim. aur maine sahihain mein aur Humaidi mein Alif Lam ke baghair (salam alaik) aur (salam aliana) nahin paya, lekin sahabul jaame (ibne-aseer) ne Imam Tirmizi se usey riwayat kya hai."
911,"Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney bayan kya : phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (tashahud ke liye) bethey aapney apna baayan paaon bichaya, baayan haath apni baain raan par rakha, daain kohni ko daain raan se utha kar rakha, do ungliyon ko band kya aur darmiyani ungli aur anguthey ko mila kar halqa banaya, phir apni angusht shahadat ko uthaya, maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap usko harkat detey aur uskey sath ishara kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Darmi."
912,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kartey to apni ungli se ishara kartey aur aap usko harkat nahin detey they. Abu-Dawud, Nasai, Imam Abu-Dawood ne ye izafa naqal kya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nazar aap ke isharay se aagey nahin jati thi."
913,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi apni dono ungliyon ke sath ishara karta tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik ke sath, eik ke sath.''"
914,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz mein haath ka sahara lekar bethney se mana kya kartey they. Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, aur unhi ki eik riwayat mein hai : jab aadmi Namaz mein khada ho to usey haathon ka sahara lekar khada honey se mana farmaya. sahih bil-lafz al-awwal rawahu Ahmed ."
915,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pehli do rakaaton mein is tarah bethtey they jaisey garm pattharon par bethey hon yahan tak ke aap khadey ho jatey.
916,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (us ehtimam sey) hamen tashahud sikhaya kartey they jaisey hamen Quran ki sura sikhaya kartey they : Allah ke naam aur Allah ki tofiq ke sath, (meri sari) qoli, badni aur maali ibadatein sirf Allah ke liye khas hain, aey nabi! aap par Allah ki rehmat, salamti aur barkaten hon, aur ham par aur Allah ke doosrey nek bandon par bhi salamti ho, mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain, main Allah se jannat talab karta hun aur aag ( jahannam ( se Allah ki panah chahta hun.''"
917,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) (tashahud ke liye) Namaz mein bethtey to wo apney haath apney ghutnon par rakh letey, ungli se ishara kartey aur apni nazar us (isharay ya ungli) par rakhtey, phir unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye yani angusht shahadat shetan par lohey se bhi ziyada sakht hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
918,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, tashahud aahista aawaz se padhna masnun hai. Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
919,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila bayan kartey hain, Kab bin Ajra mujhey miley to unhoney farmaya : kya main tumhen eik hadiya pesh na karun jisey maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha, maine kaha : kyon nahin, zarur pesh farmaeyn. unhoney farmaya : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kartey huey arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham aap ke ehle-bait par kaisey durood bhejein? kyonkey Allah ne hamen ye to sikha diya hai ke ham aap par kaisey salam bhejein, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' yun kaho, Ilaahi, rehmat farma Muhammad par aur aale-Muhammad par jis tarah to ne rehmat farmaai Ibrahim aur aale-Ibrahim par, be-shak to tareef wala aur buzurgi wala hai, aey Allah! barkat farma Muhammad par aur aale-Muhammad par jis tarah to ne barkat farmaai Ibrahim aur aale-Ibrahim par, be-shak to tareef wala buzurgi wala hai.'' Bukhari, Muslim. albatta Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne do jagahon par (Aale-Ibrahim) zikr nahin kya. muttafaq aleh."
920,"Hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi bayan kartey hain, Sahaba ne arz kya Allah ke Rasool! ham aap par kaisey durood bhejein? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kaho, aey Allah! Muhammad par, unki azwaj (jodey) par aur unki aulad par rehmat farma, jis tarah to ne aale-Ibrahim par rehmat farmaai, aur Muhammad par, aapki azwaj (jodey) aur aapki aulad par barkat farma jis tarah to ne aale-Ibrahim par barkat farmaai, be-shak to tareef wala buzurgi wala hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
921,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs mujh par eik martaba durood bhejna hai to Allah is par das rahmatein nazil farmata hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
922,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs mujh par eik martaba durood padhta hai to Allah is par das rahmatein nazil farmata hai, uskey das gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain, aur uskey das darjaat buland kar diye jatey hain.'' rawahu Nasai ."
923,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mujh par sab se ziyada durood bhejney wala shakhs roze-qiyamat merey sab se ziyada qarib hoga .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
924,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah ke kuch farishtey zamin par chaltey rehtey hain, wo meri ummat ki taraf se mujh par salam pahunchatey hain.'' rawahu Nasai w Darmi."
925,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi shakhs mujh par salam bhejta hai to Allah meri rooh mujh par lota deta hai yahan tak ke main uskey salam ka jawab deta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
926,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' na apney gharon ko qabristaan banaao na meri qabr ko eid (ziyaarat gaah) banana, aur mujh par durood bhejo , kyonkey tum jahan bhi ho tumhara durood mujh tak pahuncha diya jata hai.'' rawahu Nasai ."
927,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us shakhs ki naak khaak aalud ho jiskey samney mera zikr kya jaey lekin wo mujh par durood na padhey , us shakhs ki naak khaak aalud ho jiskey paas Ramazan aa kar chala gaya lekin uski maghfirat na ho sakey , aur us shakhs ki naak bhi khaak aalud ho jiski zindagi mein uskey waliden ya un mein se koi eik budhapey ko pahunch jaey lekin) unki khidmat ( phir bhi usey jannat mein dakhil na karwa sakey .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
928,Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) badey khush tashrif laye to farmaya : ''Jibrael (Alaihissalam) merey paas tashrif laye to unhoney farmaya : aap ka rab farmata hai : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! kya ye baat aap ke liye khushi ki nahin ke jab aap ki ummat mein se koi shakhs eik martaba aap par durood bhejey to main is par das rahmatein bhejun aur aap ki ummat mein se jo shakhs eik martaba aap par salam bhejey to main is par das martaba salamti bhejun .'' rawahu Nasai w Darmi .
929,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! main aap par bahut ziyada durood bhejta hun, main apni dua ka kitna hissey aap par durood w salam ke liye waqf kar dun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jitna tum chaho.'' maine arz kya : chothai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jitna tum chaho , agar tum ziyada kar lo to wo tumharey liye behtar hai.'' maine arz kya, aadhi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jitna tum chaho, agar tum ziyada kar lo to wo tumharey liye behtar hai.'' maine arz kya : do tihai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jitna tum chaho, agar ziyada kar lo to wo tumharey liye behtar hai.'' maine arz kya : main apni puri dua aap ( par durood w salam (ke liye waqf kar deta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' phir to tumhari sari muraadein puri ho jaeyngi aur tumharey gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey.''"
930,"Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma they to eik aadmi aaya, usney Namaz padhi aur dua ki : aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey aur mujh par rehem farma, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' namazi shakhs ! tum ne jald bazi ki, jab tum Namaz padh kar) tashahud ke liye ( betho to Allah ki, uski shaan ke laaiq , hamd bayan karo, mujh par durood bhejo, phir Allah Taala se dua karo.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, phir uskey baad eik aur aadmi ne Namaz padhi to usney Allah ki hamd bayan ki, Nabi par durood bheja to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : '' namazi shakhs ! dua karo, tumhari dua qubul hogi.'' Tirmizi. Abu-Dawood aur Nasai ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
931,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Namaz padh raha tha, jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tashrif farma they, jab main betha to maine sab se pehley Allah Taala ki sanaa bayan ki, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par durood bheja , phir apney liye dua ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maango! diya jaeyga, maango ! diya jaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
932,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko pasand ho ke usey pura pura ajr w sawab diya jaey to phir jab wo ham ehle bait par durood padhey to wo yun kahey : aey Allah ! Muhammad, ummi Nabi par, aapki paak biviyon, mominon ki maaon par, aap ki aulad aur aap ke ehle-khana par rahmatein nazil farma jaisey to ne aale-Ibrahim par rehmatein nazil farmaain, be-shak to tareef wala, buzurgi wala hai.''"
933,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke paas mera zikr kya jaey aur wo mujh par durood na bhejey to wo bakheel hai.'' Tirmizi, Imam Ahmed ne Husain bin Ali ki sanad se riwayat kya hai aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
934,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs meri qabr ke paas mujh par durood padhta hai to main usey khud sunta hun, aur jo shakhs door se mujh par durood bhejta hai to wo mujhey pahuncha diya jata hai.''"
935,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jo shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par eik martaba durood bhejna hai to Allah aur uskey farishtey is par sattar rahmatein nazil farmatey hain.
936,"Hazrat Ruwefe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par durood bheja aur dua ki : aey Allah ! roze-qiyamat unhen apney paas maqame-Mehmood ata farma, uskey liye meri shafaat wajib ho gaee.''"
937,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye yahan tak ke khajuron ke baagh mein tashrif ley gaey, aapney bahut taweel sajda kya yahan tak ke mujhey andesha hua ke kahin Allah Taala ne aap ki rooh qabz na kar li ho, wo bayan kartey hain, main aap ko dekhney ke liye aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna sar uthaya to farmaya : '' aapko kya hua?'' pas maine aap se wo khadsha bayan kar diya, raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Jibrael ne mujhey farmaya : kya main aap ko basharat na dun ke Allah azz-w-jall aap se farmata hai : jo shakhs aap par durood bhejta hai to main is par rahmatein nazil karta hun, aur jo aap par salam bhejta hai to main is par salamti bhejta hun.''"
938,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab tak tum apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par durood na bhejo to tumhari dua aasman aur zamin ke darmiyan thehri rehti hai aur is mein se koi chiz bhi ooper nahin chadhti ."
939,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz mein ye dua kya kartey they : ''aey Allah! main azabe-qabr aur Masihe-dajjaal ke fitney se teri panah chahta hun, main maut w hayaat ke fitney se teri panah chahta hun, aey Allah! main gunah aur qarz se teri panah chahta hun.'' kisi ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : aap qarz se is qadr kyon panah talab kartey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kyonkey jab aadmi maqrooz hota hai to wo baat kartey huey jhoot bolta hai, aur jab wada karta hai to khilaf warzi karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
940,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi tashahud se farigh ho to wo chaar chizein, azabe-jahannam, azabe-qabr, maut w hayaat ke fitney aur Masih dajjaal ke fitney se Allah ki panah talab karey.'' rawahu Muslim."
941,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen ye dua us ehtimam ke sath sikhaya kartey they jaisey aap unhen Quran ki sura sikhaya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : '' kaho, aey Allah ! main azabe-jahannam, azabe-qabr, Masih dajjaal ke fitney aur maut w hayaat ke fitney se teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
942,"Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey koi dua sikhaein jo main apni Namaz mein kya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kaho, aey Allah! be-shak maine apni jaan par bahut zulm kya hai, terey siwa gunahon ko koi nahin bakhsh sakta , so apni Janab se mujhey bakhsh dey, aur mujh par rehem farma, be-shak tu hi bakhshney wala meharban hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
943,"Hazrat Aamir bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko daain baeyn salam phertey huey dekhta tha yahan tak ke main aap ke rukhsaar ki safedi bhi dekhta tha. rawahu Muslim."
944,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se farigh hotey to aap apna chehra Mubarak hamari taraf kar letey they. Bukhari."
945,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (salam pherney ke baad) apni daain taraf se rukh badaltey they. rawahu Muslim."
946,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs apni Namaz se shetan ke liye hissey na banaey aur is tarah ke wo samjhey ke) salam pherney ke baad) sirf daain taraf hi se rukh badlega, halanke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap aksar apni baain janib se phirtey they. muttafaq aleh."
947,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey Namaz padhtey to ham aap ke daain janib khada hona pasand kartey they, ( kyonkey (aap hamari taraf chehra Mubarak kya kartey they. neez farmaya : maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''merey rab! mujhey us roz, jab to apney bandon ko uthaeyga, apney azab se bachaanaa.'' rawahu Muslim."
948,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein jab khawatin farz Namaz se salam phertin to wo khadi ho (kar fauran chali) jatin, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke sath Namaz padhney waley Sahaba , jab tak Allah chahta , bethey rehtey , pas jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey hotey to phir Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) bhi khadey hotey . Bukhari . ham Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees insha Allah ( baab الضحک )mein zikr karengey ."
949,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mera haath pakad kar farmaya : ''Muaz! main tum se mohabbat karta hun.'' maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main bhi aap se mohabbat karta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her Namaz ke baad ye dua padhna tarak na karna : merey rab! apney zikr w shukr aur apni behtareen khalis ibadat karney par meri madad farma .'' Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, Nasai"
950,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Assalamualaikum warahmatullah) kehtey huey daain taraf salam phertey yahan tak ke aap ke daain rukhsaar ki safedi nazar aa jati , aur (Assalamualaikum warahmatullah) kehtey huey baain taraf salam phertey yahan tak ke aap ke baeyn rukhsaar ki safedi nazar aa jati.'' Abu-Dawud, Nasai , Tirmizi, albatta Imam Tirmizi"
951,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) se usey riwayat kya hai.
952,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zyada tar apni Namaz se apni baain taraf, apney hujrey ki taraf phira kartey they."
953,"Hazrat Ata khurasaani (Raziallahu anhu) Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Imam us jagah jahan usney (farz) Namaz padhi hai, (nafl) Namaz na padhey yahan tak ke jagah badal ley.'' Abu-Dawud, aur unhoney farmaya : ata khurasaani ki Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat Sabit nahin."
954,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Namaz par targheeb dilai aur aapney unhen aap ke (unki taraf phirney) se pehley uth kar janey se mana farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood .
955,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni Namaz mein ye dua kya kartey they : ''aey Allah! main Deen ke mamley mein Sabit qadmi, rushdo-hidayat par azeemat, teri nemat par shukr aur teri behtareen aur khalis ibadat karney ka tujh se sawal karta hun, main tujh se qalbe-saleem aur zabane-sadiq ka sawal karta hun, main us khair w bhalai ka tujh se sawal karta hun jisey to jaanta hai, aur her us shar se teri panah chahta hun jisey to janta hai, aur un gunahon se jisey to janta hai tujh se maghfirat talab karta hun.'' Nasai , Imam Ahmed ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai. rawahu Nasai ."
956,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni Namaz mein tashahud ke baad ye kaha kartey they : '' behtareen kalamullah ka kalam hai aur sab se behtareen tariqa Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka tariqa hai.'' rawahu Nasai ."
957,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz mein apney chehrey ke samney se eik salam phertey phir thoda sa apni daain janib jhuk jatey they."
958,"Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen hukm diya ke ham Imam ke salam ka jawab den, baham (aapas mein) mohabbat karen aur eik doosrey ko salam karen."
959,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ka pura hona Allahu-akbar ki aawaz se pahchanta tha. muttafaq aleh."
960,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) salam pherney ke baad ye dua : ''aey Allah ! to salamti wala hai, teri hi taraf se salamti hai, aey shaan w ikram waley ! to bada hi ba barkat hai.'' padhney tak ( qibla rukh ( bethey rehtey . rawahu Muslim ."
961,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se farigh hotey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) teen martaba ''Astaghfirullah'' kehtey aur phir ye kalmaat padhtey, ''aey Allah! to salamti wala hai aur teri hi taraf se salamti hai, aey shaan w ikram waley! to bada hi ba-barkat hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
962,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her farz Namaz ke baad ye padha kartey they : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ke liye badshahat aur usi ke liye hamd hai, aur wo her chiz par qadir hai, aey Allah ! jo to ata karna chahey usey koi rok nahin sakta aur jo to rok ley usey koi ata nahin kar sakta , aur dolat mand ko (us ki) dolat terey azab se nahin bacha sakti .'' muttafaq aleh."
963,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se salam phertey to buland aawaz se ye dua padhtey : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ke liye badshahat aur usi ke liye tareef hai, aur wo her chiz par qadir hai, gunah se bachna aur neki karna mehaz Allah ki tofiq se hi mumkin hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, ham sirf usi ki ibadat kartey hain, usi ke liye nemat w Fazal aur usi ke liye behtareen tareef hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, ham usi ke liye itaat ko khalis kartey hain, chahey kafir usey na pasand karen .'' rawahu Muslim ."
964,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo apni aulad ko ye kalmaat sikhaya kartey they, aur wo kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ke baad unke zariey taawuz (panah) hasil kya kartey they : ''aey Allah! main buzdili aur kanjusi se teri panah chahta hun, aur is baat se bhi teri panah chahta hun ke mujhey nikammi (yani budhapey ki) umr ki taraf pher diya jaey, aur isi tarah mein duniyawi fitnon aur azabe-qabr se bhi teri panah chahta hun.'' Bukhari ."
965,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke kuch Muhajir fuqraa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney arz kya : maaldaar daaimi nematein aur buland darjaat pa gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo kaisey?'' unhoney arz kya : jaisey ham Namaz padhtey hain wesay wo Namaz padhtey hain, jaisey ham rozey rakhtey hain, wesay wo rozey rakhtey hain, lekin wo sadqa kartey hain aur ham sadqa nahin kartey, wo ghulam azad kartey hain, ham ghulam azad nahin kartey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen koi aisi chiz na sikhaaun jiskey zariey tum apney se sabqat ley janey walon ko pa logey aur apney baad walon se sabqat pa jaaogey, aur tum se sirf wohi ( maaldaar ( shakhs behtar hoga jo tumharey jaisa amal kerega ? unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kyon nahin, zarur bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum her Namaz ke baad tentis tentees baar ( Subhanallah ( , ( Allahu-akbar (aur ( Alhamdulillah ( padh liya karo.'' abu-Saaleh bayan kartey hain, Muhajir fuqraa dobara Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur arz kya : hamarey maal daar bhaiyon ko hamarey amal ka pata chal gaya hai aur unhoney bhi wohi amal shuru kar diya hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye Allah ka Fazal hai, wo jisey chahta hai ata karta hai. Bukhari, Muslim, lekin abu-Saaleh ka qol sirf sahih Muslim mein hai. sahih Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai : ''tum her farz Namaz ke baad das martaba ( Subhanallah ( , das martaba ( Alhamdulillah (aur das martaba ( Allahu-akbar ( padha karo ye alfaz : ''tentees ke mutabadil farmaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
966,"Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her farz Namaz ke baad chand kalmaat kahey jatey hain, unka kehney wala nakam aur na-murad nahin hoga, tentis martaba ( Subhanallah ( tentis martaba ( Alhamdulillah (aur chauntees martaba ( Allahu-akbar ( kehna : '' rawahu Muslim ."
967,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne her Namaz ke baad tentis martaba ( Subhanallah ( tentis martaba ( Alhamdulillah (aur tentis martaba ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha, pas ye ninnanwey huye, aur : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ke liye badshahat hai, usi ke liye hamd hai aur wo her chiz par qadir hai, se so pura kar liya to uskey gunah chahey samandar ki jhaag ke barabar hon to bhi maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
968,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool! kon si dua ziyada qubul hoti hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aakhiri aadhi raat mein aur farz namazon ke baad ki gaee dua.''"
969,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya ke main her ( farz ( Namaz ke baad muawwizaat ( Sura ikhlas , Falaq aur Naas ( ki tilawat kya karun. rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w al-Behaqi ."
970,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey namaze-Fajr se tulu aaftaab tak Allah ka zikr karney wali jamaat ke sath bethna , aulade-Ismail (Alaihissalam) se talluq rakhney waley chaar ghulam azad karney se ziyada pasand hai, jabkey mujhey, namaze-Asr se ghurub aaftaab tak Allah ka zikr karney wali jamaat ke sath bethna, chaar ghulam azad karney se ziyada pasand hai.''"
971,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs namaze-Fajr ba-jamaat ada karta hai, phir usi jagah beth kar tulu aaftaab tak Allah ka zikr karta rehta hai, phir do rakatein padhta hai to uskey liye mukammal Haj w Umre ka sawab hai.'' aapney ye teen martaba farmaya."
972,"Hazrat azraq bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, hamarey Imam abu-Ramsa ne hamen Namaz padhaai to unhoney kaha : maine ye Namaz ya uski misl Namaz , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath padhi thi, unhoney kaha : abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) w umr (Raziallahu anhu) pehli saf mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki daain janib khadey hua kartey they, eik aadmi jo takbire-ola mein aa kar shamil hua, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padhi , phir apney daain baain salam phera yahan tak ke ham ne aap ke rukhsaaron ki safedi dekhi, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mudey jaisey abu-Ramsa yani wo khud mudey , pas wo aadmi jo takbire-ola mein aapke sath shareek hua tha, wo khada hua aur phir Namaz shuru kar di, to umr (Raziallahu anhu) jaldi se khadey huey aur usey uskey kandhon se pakad kar khub hilaya, phir farmaya : beth jaao, kyonkey ehle-kitab usi liye halak huey they ke unki (farz w nafl) namazon mein koi waqfa nahin hota tha, pas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni nazar uthai to farmaya : '' ibn khattab! Allah ne teri wajeh se haq qaaim kar diya .''"
973,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, hamen hukm diya gaya ke ham her Namaz ke baad tentis dafa ( Subhanallah ( tentis dafa ( Alhamdulillah (aur chauntees martaba ( Allahu-akbar ( kahin , ansaar ke eik aadmi ne khuwab mein kisi aadmi ko dekha to usney us ( Ansari aadmi ( se kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tumhen hukm diya hai ke tum her Namaz ke baad is qadr tasbih karo, Ansari shakhs ne apney khuwab mein kaha : haan ! us shakhs ne kaha : usey pachchis , pachchis martaba kar lo aur us mein) la Ilaah illallah ( shamil kar lo , jab subh hui to wo Ansari Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney aap ko khuwab ka waqia bayan kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisey hi kar liya karo.'' rawahu Ahmed w Nasai w Darmi ."
974,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member ki sidhiyon par farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs her Namaz ke baad aayatal-kursi padhta hai to usko jannat mein dakhiley se sirf maut rokey huey hai aur jo shakhs soney ke liye apney bistar par let'tey waqt usey padhta hai to Allah uskey ghar ko , uskey padosi ke ghar aur uskey Aas paas ke ghar walon ko aman ata kar deta hai.'' ( Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan), aur unhoney kaha : iski sanad zaeef hai."
975,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin ghanam Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs namaze-Maghrib aur namaze-Fajr padhney ke baad apni usi jagah aur usi keyfiyat ( tashahud ( mein bethey huey ye dua : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ke liye badshahat aur usi ke liye her qism ki hamd hai aur her qism ki khair w bhalai usi ke haath mein hai, wohi zinda karta hai aur maarta hai, aur wohi her chiz par qadir hai.'' das martaba padhta hai to uskey her martaba padhney par uskey liye das nekiyan likhi jati hain, uskey das gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain aur uskey das darjaat buland kar diye jatey hain, aur her nagawar chiz se uska bachaaw ho jata hai, aur mardud shetan se uska bachaaw ho jata hai, shirk ke ilawa koi gunah usey halak nahin kar sakta aur wo sab se behtareen amal karney wala hota hai siwaey iske ke koi shakhs us se behtar kalam se dua karey.'' rawahu Ahmed."
976,"Hazrat Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne (illa shirk) tak Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah riwayat kya hai aur unhoney namaze-Maghrib aur (baida al-khair) ka zikr nahin kya, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
977,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Najad ki taraf eik lashkar rawana kya, unhoney bahut sa maale-ghanimat hasil kya aur bahut jald (Madina) wapis aagey to ham mein se eik aadmi ne kaha : ham ne us lashkar se ziyada maale-ghanimat lekar aur itni jaldi wapis aatey huey koi lashkar nahin dekha, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen ziyada maale-ghanimat ke sath ziyada jaldi wapis aaney waley lashkar ke barey mein na bataaun ? wo aisey log hain jo ba-jamaat Fajr padhney ke baad beth kar tulu aaftaab tak Allah ka zikr kartey rehtey hain, pas ye wo log hain jo behtareen maale-ghanimat lekar bahut jald wapis aaney waley hain.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees gharib hai, Hammad bin abi Humaid raawi hadees ke barey mein zaeef hai."
978,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Hakam bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padh raha tha ke is doran logon mein se kisi aadmi ne chheenk maar di, to maine (dorane-namaz) keh diya : Allah tum par rehem karey, log mujhey aakhon ke isharay se rokney lagey , maine kaha : meri maa mujhey gum paey , tumhen kya hua ke tum mujhey is tarah dekh rahey ho? unhoney apni raanon par apney haath maarna shuru kar diye , chunanche jab maine unhen dekha ke wo mujhey chup kara rahey hain to main khamosh ho gaya, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padh li , merey waliden aap par qurban hon, maine aap jaisa behtareen muallim aap se pehley koi dekha hai na aap ke baad, Allah ki qasam! aapney mujhey daanta na maara aur na hi gaali di, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye jo Namaz hai ismein logon ka baaten karna durust nahin, ye to sirf tasbih w takbir aur qirate-Quran hai.'' ya us se miltey jultey alfaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaai . maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! main naya naya musalman hua hun, Allah ne hamen Islam ki dolat se nawaza hai be-shak ham mein kuch aisey log hain jo kaahinon ke paas jatey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum unke paas na jana.'' maine arz kya, ham mein se kuch log faal letey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye wo chiz hai jo wo apney seenon mein paatey hain, (us ki koi daleel nahin) pas ye chiz unhen rokney na paey .'' maine arz kya, ham mein se kuch log lakeerein khinchtey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik Nabi bhi khat khincha kartey they, pas jis ka khat unke muwaafiq hoga to wo durust hai.'' rawahu Muslim"
979,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham dorane-namaz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam kya kartey they aur aap hamen jawab dey diya kartey they pas jab ham Najashi ke paas se wapis aaye to ham ne aap ko salam arz kya, lekin aapney hamen jawab na diya, to ham ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! ham aap ko dorane-namaz salam arz kya kartey they aur aap hamen jawab diya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Namaz eik tarah ki mashghooliyat (la talluqi) hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
980,"Hazrat Mueqeeb (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us shakhs ke barey mein riwayat kartey hain, jo sajde ki jagah par mitti durust karta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum ne zarur hi karna hai to phir eik martaba kar ley.'' muttafaq aleh."
981,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dorane-namaz pehlu par haath rakhney se mana farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
982,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Namaz mein idhar-udhar dekhney ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo to uchak lena hai, shetan bandey ki Namaz se uchak leta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
983,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' logon ko dorane-namaz , dua ke waqt apni aankhen aasman ki taraf uthaney se baaz aa jana chahiye, ya unki aankhen uchak li jaeyngi.'' rawahu Muslim ."
984,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko logon ki imaamat karatey huey dekha jabkey (aap ki nawaasi ( Amama binte-abi al-Aas aap ke kandhey par thin, jab aap rukoo kartey to unhen (kandhey sey) utaar detey aur jab sajdon se sar uthatey to phir unhen utha letey they. muttafaq aleh."
985,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ko dorane-namaz jamaai aaye to jis qadr ho sakey usey rokey kyonkey (munh khula ho to) shetan dakhil ho jata hai.'' usey Muslim ne riwayat kya hai. rawahu Muslim ."
986,"aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) sahih Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai : ''jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ko dorane-namaz jamaai aaye, to jis qadr ho sakey usey rokey, ha ha na karey, ye to mehaz shetan ki taraf se hai, wo is par hansta hai.'' Bukhari ."
987,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' guzishta raat achcha eik sarkash jin aaya taake meri Namaz kharab kar dey , lekin Allah ne mujhey is par ikhtiyar ata farmaya to maine usey masjid ke sutoon ke sath baandhney ka irada kya yahan tak ke tum sab usey dekh letey, to phir mujhey merey bhai Suleman (Alaihissalam) (Alaihissalam) ki dua yad aa gaee : merey rab ! mujhey aisi badshahat ata farma jo merey baad kisi aur ke laaiq na ho, pas maine usey zaleel karkey bhaga diya .'' muttafaq aleh."
988,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko Namaz mein koi aariza pesh aa jaey to wo '' Subhanallah '' kahey, haath par haath maarna to khawatin ke liye hai.'' muttafaq aleh. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Subhanallah kehna mardon ke liye hai jabkey haath par haath maarna khawatin ke liye hai.''"
989,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain hijrate-Habsha se pehley ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko haalate-Namaz mein salam kya kartey they, aur aap hamen salam ka jawab diya kartey they, jab ham sar zameene-Habsha se wapis ( Makka ( aaye to main aapki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap us waqt Namaz padh rahey they, maine aap ko salam kya lekin aapney mujhey salam ka jawab na diya, yahan tak ke jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz mukammal kar chukey to farmaya : ''Allah jis tarah chahta hai apna hukm zahir karta hai, aur ab jo naya hukm aaya hai wo ye hai ke tum Namaz mein baat na karo.'' phir aapney mujhey salam ka jawab diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
990,"aur farmaya : ''Namaz to qirat Quran aur Allah ke zikr ke liye hai, pas jab tum us ( Namaz ( mein ho to tumharey pesh nazar bhi yehi kuch hona chahiye.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
991,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : jab Sahaba kiram Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko haalate-Namaz mein salam kya kartey they to aap unhen kaisey jawab diya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : aap apney haath se ishara kya kartey they. Tirmizi, Nasai ki riwayat mein bhi isi tarah hai aur Bilal ki jagah Suheb ka zikr kya. rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai ."
992,"Hazrat Rifa bin Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey Namaz padhi to mujhey chheenk aa gaee to maine kaha : her qism ki hamd Allah ke liye hai, hamd bahut ziyada , khalis aur ba barkat , jaisey hamarey rab ko pasand aur mehbub hai, chunanche jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padh kar hamari taraf rukh kya to farmaya : '' Namaz mein bolney wala kon tha ?'' kisi ne jawab na diya, phir aapney dusri martaba puchha : to phir kisi ne jawab na diya phir aapney teesri martaba puchha to Rifaa ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! maine baat ki thi, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! tees se kuch ziyada farishtey sabqat ley janey ki koshish kar rahey they ke un mein se kon unhen ooper lekar chadhta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
993,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dorane-namaz jamaai aana shetan ki taraf se hai, pas jab tum mein se kisi ko jamaai aaye to wo maqdoor bhar usey rokney ki koshish karey.'' Tirmizi aur usi ki dusri riwayat aur ibne-Maja mein hai : '' wo apney munh par haath rakh ley.'' ."
994,"Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs achi tarah wuzu karkey masjid ke qasd (irada) se rawana ho to wo ( raastey mein) apney eik haath ki ungliyan doosrey haath mein dakhil na karey, kyonkey wo ( hukman ( Namaz hi mein hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w Darmi ."
995,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab banda Namaz mein hota hai to jab tak wo idhar-udhar na dekhey to Allah azz-w-jall is par apni tawajjoh markooz rakhta hai, jab wo idhar-udhar dekhta hai to phir wo us se rukh mod leta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w Darmi ."
996,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Anas ! apney sajde ki jagah par nazar rakho.'' Behaqi ne Hasan an-Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki sanad se apni sunan al-Kabir mein marfoo riwayat kya hai.
997,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' beta ! Namaz mein idhar-udhar dekhney se ehtiyat karo, kyonkey Namaz mein idhar-udhar dekhna baais halakat hai, pas agar zarur hi dekhna ho to phir nafl mein hai lekin farz mein nahin .''"
998,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dorane-namaz gardan modey baghair daain baeyn dekh liya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai .
999,"Hazrat Adi bin Sabit apney baap se aur wo apney dada se marfoo riwayat kartey hain, farmaya : '' dorane-namaz chhinkein, ungh, jamaai, haiz, qai ka aana neez nakseer ka phootnaa shetan ki taraf se hai.''"
1000,"Hazrat Mutrif bin Abdullah bin shikhkhir apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap Namaz padh rahey they to roney ki wajeh se aap ke pet se handiyon ke ubalney ki si aawaz aa rahi thi. eik dusri riwayat mein hai : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Namaz padhtey huey dekha to roney ki wajeh se aap ke seeney mein chuki chalney ki si aawaz aa rahi thi. Ahmed, aur Imam Nasai ne pehli riwayat ki hai aur Imam Abu-Dawood ne dusri . sahih ."
1001,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz ke liye khada ho to wo kankariyon ko haath na lagaey kyonkey us waqt usey rehmat ka samna hota hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja."
1002,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamarey Aflah naami ghulam ko dekha ke jab wo sajda karta to phunk maarta , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aflah ! apney chehrey ko mitti lagney do.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
1003,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dorane-namaz kamar (kokh) par haath rakhna, jahannamiyon ka andaz rahat hai.''"
1004,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do siyah chizon, sanp aur bichhu ko qatl kar do chahey ( tum ( Namaz mein ho.'' Ahmed, Abu-Dawood Tirmizi aur Nasai ki riwayat usi maana mein hai."
1005,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) darwaza band karkey nafl ada kar rahey they, mein aai to maine darwaza kholney ki darkhast ki, aap chal kar aaye aur merey liye darwaza khol kar phir apni jaey Namaz par wapis chaley gaey, aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne zikr kya ke darwaza qible ki samt tha. Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, aur Nasai ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
1006,"Hazrat Talaq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ki dorane-namaz hawa khaarij ho jaey to wo ja kar wuzu karey aur aa kar Namaz dohraaey.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi ne alfaz ki kami beshi ke sath riwayat kya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
1007,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ka dorane-namaz wuzu toot jaey to wo apni naak pakad kar wahan se bahar nikal jaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1008,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ka wuzu toot jaey jabkey wo salam pherney se pehley , Namaz ke aakhir mein betha ho, to uski Namaz puri ho gaee .'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : is hadees ki asnaad qawi nahin, unhon (yani muhaddeseen ( ne uski asnaad ko muztarib qarar diya hai."
1009,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ke liye tashrif laye, chunanche aapney jab Allahu-akbar kaha to phir wapis chaley gaey aur unhen ishara kya ke wo usi haalat mein rahen , phir aap gaey, ghusl kya, phir tashrif laye to aap ke sar se pani ke qatrey gir rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Namaz padhaai , jab Namaz padh chukey to farmaya : ''main junbi tha, aur main ghusl karna bhool gaya tha.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
1010,aur Imam Malik ne Ata bin Yasar se mursal riwayat kya hai.
1011,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath namaze-Zohar ada kar raha tha, maine kankariyon ki mutthi bhari taake wo meri mutthi mein thandi ho jaeyn, main garmi ki shiddat ki wajeh se un par sajda kya karta tha. Abu-Dawud, aur Imam Nasai ne bhi usi ke misl riwayat kya hai."
1012,"Hazrat Abu-Darda bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein Namaz padha rahey they, to ham ne aap ko teen martaba ye kehtey huey suna : ''main tujh se Allah ki panah chahta hun.'' phir farmaya : ''main tujhey Allah ki lanat ke zariey lanat bhejta hun.'' aur aapney apna haath aagey badhaya jaisey aap koi chiz pakad rahey hon, isliye jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to ham ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham ne aap ko Namaz mein kuchh kehtey huey suna jo ham ne is se pehley aap ko kehtey huey nahin suna aur ham ne aap ko haath badhaatey huey bhi dekha . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka dushman iblees aag ka eik shola lekar aaya taake wo usey merey chehrey par dal dey , to maine teen martaba kaha : main tujh se Allah ki panah chahta hun, phir maine kaha : main Allah ki lanat kamil ke zariey tujh par lanat bhejta hun, lekin wo teeno martaba peechhey na hata to phir maine usey pakadney ka irada kiya, Allah ki qism ! agar hamarey bhai Suleman(Alahissalaam) ki dua na hoti to wo subah ke waqt yahan bandhaa hua hota aur ehle Madina ke bachchey uskey sath khel rahey hotey.'' rawahu Muslim."
1013,"Hazrat Naafe bayan kartey hain ke Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) eik aadmi ke paas se guzrey jo Namaz padh raha tha, unhoney usey salam kiya to usney bol kar jawab diya, Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) uskey paas wapis aaye aur usey bataya : jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ko haalate Namaz mein salam kiya jaey to wo bol kar jawab na dey balke apney haath se ishara kar dey. rawahu Malik."
1014,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz padh raha hota hai to shetan uskey paas aa kar usey moghaltey mein mubtala kar deta hai yahan tak ke wo nahin janta ke usney kitni Namaz padhi hai, jab tum mein se koi aisi surat (tardeed) paey to wo bethney ki haalat hi mein do sajdey kar ley.'' Muttafaq Aleh."
1015,"Hazrat Ata bin Yasar , Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko apni Namaz ke barey mein shak ho aur usey pata na chaley ke usney kitni rakatein padhi hain, teen ya chaar , to wo shak door karey aur yaqin par buniyad rakhey , phir salam pherney se pehley do sajdey karey, agar usney paanch rakaat padh li hain to ye do sajdey uski Namaz ko juft (jaude ke shakl mein) bana dengey , aur agar usney ye rakaat chaar mukammal karney ke liye padhi hai to phir wo do sajdey shetan ko zaleel karne ke liye hongey. ''Muslim , Imam Maalik ne Ata se mursal riwayat kiya hai, aur unki riwayat mein hai : ''usney un do sajdon se usko juft (jaude ke shakl mein) bana diya.'' rawahu Muslim aur Malik."
1016,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Zohar paanch rakatein padhein , aap se arz kiya gaya, kya Namaz mein izafa kar diya gaya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo kya ?'' Sahaba ne arz kiya : aapney paanch rakatein padhi hain, to aapney salam pherney ke baad do sajdey kiye , aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main bhi tum jaisa insan hun, jaisey tum bhool jatey ho wesay hi main bhool jata hun, isliye jab kabhi main bhool jaaun to mujhey yad kara diya karo, aur jab tum mein se kisi ko apni Namaz mein shak guzrey to wo durust baat talash karney ki puri koshish karey aur us buniyad par Namaz mukammal karey. phir salam pherey aur phir do sajdey karey.'' Muttafaq Aleh."
1017,"Hazrat ibne Sireen (Raziallahu anhu) Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein namaze-Zohar ya Asr ki Namaz padhaai ,ibne Sireen (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne uska naam bhi bataya tha lekin main usey bhool gaya hun, unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein do rakatein padhaein , phir masjid mein rakhi hui lakdi ke sath tek laga kar khadey ho gaey goya aap ghusse ki haalat mein they, aapney daayan haath baeyn par rakha , ungliyon mein ungliyan dalen aur apna daayan rukhsaar baain hatheli ki pusht par rakh diya, aur jald baaz log masjid ke darwazon se bahar chaley gaey, baqi Sahaba ne kaha : (kya) Namaz kam kar di gaee hai? Sahaba kiram mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi mojud they, lekin wo bhi aap se baat karney se ghabraatey they, Sahaba main eik aadmi tha jiskey haath lambey they aur usey Zul-Yadain kaha jata tha, usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap bhool gaey hain ya Namaz kam kar di gaee hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main bhoolaa hun na Namaz kam ki gaee hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya aisey hi hai jaisey Zul-Yadain keh raha hai?'' Sahaba ne arz kiya : ji haan ! aap aagey badhey , aur jo Namaz chhodi thi wo padhaai , phir salam phera , phir Allahu-Akbar kaha aur apney sajdon ki tarah ya un se bhi ziyada lamba sajda kiya, phir sar uthaya aur Allahu-Akbar kaha, phir Allahu-Akbar kaha aur apney sajdon ki tarah ya un se ziyada lamba sajda kiya, phir apna sar uthaya, aur Allahu-Akbar kaha . chunanche unhon (shagirdon) ne ibne Sireen (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : phir aapney salam phera? wo bayan kartey hain, mujhey bataya gaya ke Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : phir aapney salam phera . Bukhari , Muslim aur alfaze hadees Bukhari ke hain. Sahih Bukhari aur Sahih Muslim ki eik dusri riwayat mein hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (لم انس ولم تقصر) ke badley (کل ذالک لم یکن) kaha : ''ye sab kuchh nahin hua.'' to unhon (Zul-Yadain) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! un mein (yani na main bhoolaa hun na Namaz qasr ki gaee hai) se kuchh to hua hai. Muttafaq Aleh."
1018,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen namaze-Zohar padhaai to aap pehli do rakatein padh kar khadey ho gaey aur tashahud na bethey , to Sahaba bhi aap ke sath hi khadey ho gaey yahan tak ke jab aapney Namaz padhli to Sahaba ne salam pherney ka intizar kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam pherney se pehley bethey huey do sajdey kiye aur phir salam phera . Muttafaq Aleh."
1019,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Namaz padhaai to aap bhool gaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do sajdey kiye , phir tashahud padhi phir salam phera . Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan Ghareeb hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1020,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Imam do rakatein padh kar (tashahud padhey baghair) khada ho jaey, agar mukammal taur par sidha khada honey se pehley usey yad aa jaey to wo beth jaey, aur agar wo mukammal taur par sidha khada ho jaey to phir na bethey, aur saho (galti) ke do sajdey kar ley.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja\."
1021,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Asr padhaai aur teen rakaaton ke baad salam pher diya, phir aap apney ghar tashrif ley gaey to Khirbaaq naami shakhs jiskey haath lambey they, aap ke ghar ke raastey mein khada ho kar arz karney laga , Allah ke Rasool ! phir usney aap se teen rakaaton ke baad salam pher deney ke mutalliq zikr kiya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusse ki haalat main apni chadar ghaseet'tey huey bahar tashrif laye yahan tak ke logon ke paas aa kar farmaya : ''kya ye sahih keh raha hai?'' unhoney arz kiya : ji haan ! chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik rakat aur padhi , phir salam phera , phir do sajdey kiye aur phir salam phera. rawahu Muslim."
1022,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs Namaz padhey aur usey Namaz mein kami ka shak ho to wo Namaz padhey yahan tak ke usey ziyadti ka shak ho jaey.''"
1023,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sura najam ki tilawat kartey huey sajda kya to musalmanon, mushrikon aur jinnon aur insanon ne aap ke sath sajda kya. Bukhari ."
1024,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Sura Inshiqaq aur Sura Alaq ki tilawat par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath sajda kya. rawahu Muslim ."
1025,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aayat sajda tilawat farmatey, jabkey ham aap ki khidmat mein hazir hotey, aap sajda farmatey to ham bhi aap ke sath sajda kartey, pas ham ikhattey ho jatey yahan tak ke ham mein se kisi ko sajda karney ke liye peshani rakhney ki jagah na milti . muttafaq aleh."
1026,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Sura najam sunai to aapney is mein sajda na kya. muttafaq aleh."
1027,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya : Sura Suad ka sajda, taakeedi sajdon mein se nahin, lekin maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is mein sajda kartey huey dekha hai. Bukhari ."
1028,"aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : Mujahid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, maine ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se daryaft kya, kya main Sura suad ki tilawat par sajda karun? unhoney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : '' aur unki aulad mein se Dawud aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) (Alaihissalam) '' , '' pas aap unki raah ki iqtida (pairvi) karen .'' unhoney farmaya : tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi unhi mein se hain jinhen unki iqtida (pairvi) karney ka hukm diya gaya hai. Bukhari ."
1029,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey Quran ke pandarah sajdey padhaaey, un mein se teen mufassal Suraton mein hain, jabkey Sura Haj mein do sajdey hain."
1030,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! Sura Haj ko fazilat ata farmaai gaee ke is mein do sajdey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan , aur jo shakhs ye do sajdey nahin karta usey un do aayaton ki tilawat nahin kerni chahiye.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : is hadees ki asnaad qawi nahin, aur masaabeh mein hai : '' wo shakhs is sura ki tilawat na karey.'' jaisa ke Sharahus-sunnah mein hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
1031,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Zohar mein sajda kya, phir khadey huye, to rukoo kya, Sahaba kiram ne jaan liya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sura Sajda tilawat farmaai ."
1032,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein Quran sunaya kartey they, isliye jab aap aayat sajda padhtey to takbir keh kar sajda kartey aur ham bhi aap ke sath sajda kartey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1033,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke saal aayate-Sajda tilawat farmaai to tamam logon ne sajda kiya, un mein se baaz sawari par they, aur un mein se baaz ne zamin par sajda kiya yahan tak ke sawar apney haath par sajda kar rahey they."
1034,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab se Madina tashrif laye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mufassal (tafseeli) Suraton mein sajda nahin farmaya."
1035,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ke waqt sajda tilawat mein ye dua padha kartey they : ''merey chehrey ne us zaat ke liye sajda kiya, jisney usey paida farmaya , aur apni qudrat qaur taqat se kaan aur aankhen banaeyn.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1036,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! maine raat khuwab mein dekha ke main eik darkht ke peechhey Namaz padh raha hun, isliye maine sajda kiya to darkht ne bhi merey sajda karney ki wajeh se sajda kiya, maine usey ye padhtey huey suna : aey Allah merey liye uska sawab apney yahan likh ley , iskey zariey merey gunah maaf farma , usey apney yahan zakhira bana , aur usey mujh se qubul farma jaisey tu ney apney bandey Dawud (Alaihissalam) se qubul farmaya. ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayate-Sajda tilawat farmaai to aapney sajda kiya, maine aap ko wohi dua kartey huey suna jo aadmi ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko darkht ke mutalliq batai thi. Tirmizi, ibne-Maja : lekin unhoney (وتقبلھا منی کما تقبتھا من عبدک داود) ke alfaz zikr nahin kiye , aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja."
1037,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sura Najm ki tilawat farmaai to aapney aur jo aap ke sath they sab ne sajda kiya, lekin eik boodhey Quraishi ne kankariyon ya mitti ki mutthi bhari aur usey apni peshani tak laya aur kehney laga : merey liye bas yehi kafi hai, Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : uskey baad maine usey dekha ke wo haalate kufr mein maara gaya. Bukhari , Muslim . Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik riwayat mein ye izafa naqal kiya hai ke wo Umayya bin Khalaf tha. Muttafaq Aleh."
1038,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sura Suaad ki tilawat par sajda kiya aur farmaya : ''Dawud (Alaihissalam) ne tauba ke liye sajda kiya jabkey ham bator shukr sajda kartey hain.'' rawahu Nasai .
1039,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs tulu aaftaab aur ghurub aaftaab ke waqt Namaz padhney ka qasd (irada) (iraada) na karey.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Suraj ka kinara zahir ho jaey to Namaz na padho yahan tak ke wo mukammal taur par zahir ho jaey, aur jab Suraj ka kinara ghurub ho jaey to Namaz na padho yahan tak ke wo mukammal taur par ghurub ho jaey, aur Suraj ke tulu aur ghurub ke oqaat ko apni Namaz ke liye mutayyan na karo, kyonkey wo shetan ke do seengon (kinaron) ke darmiyan se tulu hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1040,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) teen oqaat : jab Suraj tulu ho raha ho yahan tak ke wo buland ho jaey, nisfun-nahar (eain beech)  ke waqt yahan tak ke wo zawal ki taraf jhuk jaey aur jab wo ghurub ke liye jhuk jaey yahan tak ke wo mukammal taur par ghurub ho jaey 'mein'  hamen Namaz padhney aur mardon ko dafn karney se mana farmaya kartey they. rawahu Muslim."
1041,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''namaze-Fajr ke baad Suraj ke buland honey tak aur namaze-Asr ke baad Suraj ke ghurub ho janey tak koi Namaz (padhna durust) nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
1042,"Hazrat Amr bin Usba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to main bhi Madina aaya aur aap ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aap mujhey Namaz ke oqaat ke mutalliq bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Namaze-Fajr padh aur phir Suraj ke achchhi tarah tulu honey tak koi Namaz na padh , kyonkey jab wo tulu hota hai to wo shetan ke sar ke dono kinaron ke darmiyan se tulu hota hai, aur us waqt kuffar usey sajda kartey hain. phir (nafl) Namaz padh kyonkey Namaz padhtey waqt farishtey hazir hotey hain, yahan tak ke neze ka saya uskey sar par aa jaey to phir Namaz na padh kyonkey us waqt jahannam bhadkai jati hai, isliye jab saya zahir honey lagey to Namaz padh kyonkey Namaz ke waqt farishtey hazir hotey hain, yahan tak ke to Namaze-Asr padh ley , phir Namaz na padh yahan tak ke Suraj ghurub ho jaey. kyonkey wo shetan ke sar ke dono kinaron ke darmiyan ghurub hota hai, aur us waqt kuffar usey sajda kartey hain.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Nabi ! wuzu ke mutalliq mujhey bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs apney wuzu ka pani qarib karkey kulli karta hai, naak mein pani dal kar usey jhadta hai to uskey chehrey , uskey munh aur uskey naak ke baanson se gunah jhad jatey hain, phir jab Allah ke hukm ke mutabiq apna chehra dhota hai to phir pani ke sath hi uskey chehrey aur dadhi ke atraaf (aas-paas) se gunah jhad jatey hain, phir kohniyon tak haath dhota hai to phir pani ke sath uskey haath ki ungliyon ke poron tak ke gunah jhad jatey hain, phir wo sar ka masah karta hai to phir pani ke sath uskey baalon ke atraaf tak ke gunah jhad jatey hain. phir takhnon samet paaon dhota hai to phir pani ke sath paaon ki ungliyon samet tak ke gunah jhad jatey hain, phir agar wo khada ho kar Namaz padhta hai aur Allah ki hamd aur sanaa aur uski shaan bayan karta hai jis ka wo ehal hai aur apney dil ko khalis Allah ki taraf mutawajjeh kar leta hai to phir wo Namaz ke baad us roz ki tarah gunahon se paak ho jata hai jis roz uski walida ne usey janm diya tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
1043,"Hazrat Kureb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abdur-Rehman bin Azhar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas bheja to unhoney kaha : unhen salam arz karna aur phir un se Asr ke baad do rakaaton ke barey mein daryaft karna . raawi bayan kartey hain, main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya aur unhoney jo pegham de-kar mujhey bheja tha wo maine un tak pahuncha diya to unhoney farmaya : Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se daryaft karo, isliye main unke paas wapis chala aaya to unhoney mujhey Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke paas bhej diya, to Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko un se mana farmatey huey suna, phir maine aap ko unhen padhtey huey dekha, phir aap tashrif laye to maine londi ko aap ke paas bheja aur kaha, aap se arz karna , Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain, Allah ke Rasool ! maine aap ko un do rakaaton se mana kartey huey suna hai. jabkey maine aap ko unhen padhtey huey dekha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Umaiya ki beti ! tum ne Asr ke baad do rakatein padhney ke mutalliq puchha hai, (wo aisey hua) ke Abdul-Qais ke kuchh log merey paas aaye aur unhoney Zohar ke baad wali do rakaaton se mujhey mashghool rakha , isliye ye wo do rakatein hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
1044,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) , Qais bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko Namaze-Fajr ke baad do rakatein padhtey huey dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Namaze-Fajr do rakaat hai, do rakaat.'' us aadmi ne arz kiya : maine un se pehley ki do rakatein nahin padhi thin, maine unhen ab padha hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey. Abu-Dawud, aur Imam Tirmizi ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kiya hai, aur unhoney farmaya : is hadees ki sanad muttasil nahin, kyonkey Muhammad bin Ibrahim ne Qais bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se nahin suna. Sharahus-sunnah aur masaabeh ke baaz nuskhon mein Qais bin Qahad se isi tarah marwi (bayan) hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
1045,Hazrat Juber bin Mua'tim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bano Abd Munaaf ! din ya raat ke kisi bhi waqt Baitullah ka tawaf karney aur is mein Namaz padhney se kisi ko mana na karna.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood aur Nasai.
1046,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jume ke siwa nisfun-nahar (eain beech) ke waqt Namaz padhney se mana farmaya yahan tak ke Suraj dhal jaey.
1047,"Hazrat Abu-Khaleel (Raziallahu anhu) , Abu-Qatada se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume ke din ke siwa nisfun-nahar (eain beech) ke waqt Namaz padhna na pasand farmaya kartey they yahan tak ke Suraj dhal jata, aur farmaya : Jume ke din ke siwa jahannam ko bhadkaya jata hai. Abu-Dawood aur unhoney farmaya : Abu-Khaleel ki Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat Sabit nahin."
1048,"Hazrat Abdullah Sunabihi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Suraj us haal mein tulu hota hai ke shetan ke seeng uskey sath hotey hain, isliye jab wo buland ho jata hai to wo us se alag ho jatey hain. phir jab wo barabar (nisfun-nahar (eain beech) par (ho jata hai to wo us se aa miltey hain, isliye jab wo dhal jata hai to wo phir alag ho jatey hain, aur jab wo ghurub ke qarib hota hai to wo phir uskey sath aa miltey hain, aur jab ghurub ho jata hai to wo alag ho jatey hain.'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne in oqaat mein Namaz padhney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Malik aur Ahmed aur Nasai."
1049,"Hazrat Abu-Basra Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maqame-makhmas par hamein Namaze-Asr padhaai to farmaya : ''ye Namaz tum se pehley logon par pesh ki gaee to unhoney isey zaya kar diya. isliye jo shakhs iski hifazat karega to usey iska das guna ajr miley , aur uskey baad tulu ''shaahid'' tak koi Namaz nahin.''  aur ''shaahid'' se sitarey murad hain. rawahu Muslim."
1050,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : be-shak tum (asr ke baad do rakaat) Namaz padhtey ho, halanke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rahey, ham ne aap ko unhen padhtey huey nahin dekha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne to un yani Asr ke baad do rakaaton se mana farmaya tha. Bukhari."
1051,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Kaba ki seedhi par chadh kar farmaya : jo mujhey pehchanta hai to isliye wo mujhey pehchanta hai, aur jo mujhey nahin pehchanta to main Jundub hun, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : Makka ke siwa (teen martaba farmaya) Namaze-Fajr ke baad tulu aaftaab tak aur Asr ke baad ghurub aaftaab tak koi Namaz (padhna durust) nahin.''"
1052,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ba-jamaat Namaz , akeley shakhs ki Namaz se sattaais darjey ziyada fazilat rakhti hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1053,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! maine irada kar liya tha ke lakdiyan ikhatti karney ka hukm dun, wo ikhatti ho jaeyn to phir main Namaz ke mutalliq hukm dun, uskey liye Azan di jaey, phir main kisi aadmi ko hukm dun ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaey , phir main un logon ke peechhey jaaun , aur eik riwayat mein hai, jo jamaat ke sath Namaz padhney nahin aatey to main unke gharon samet unhen jala dun, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar un mein se kisi ko pata chal jaey ke wo ( masjid mein) gosht wali haddi ya do behtareen paey paeyga to wo Namaze-Isha mein zarur hazir ho.'' Bukhari . Muslim mein bhi isi tarah riwayat hai, muttafaq aleh."
1054,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik na-bina shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey masjid tak pahunchaney ke liye merey paas koi aadmi nahin, us shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se darkhast ki ke aap usey rukhsat (chhoot) inayat farma den ke wo ghar mein Namaz padh liya karey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey rukhsat inayat farma di, jab wo wapis muda to aapney usey bula kar puchha : ''kya tum Namaz ke liye Azan suntey ho?'' usney arz kiya, ji haan ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to phir usey qubul karo (masjid mein aao).'' rawahu Muslim."
1055,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney eik raat jab sardi thi aur thandi hawa chal rahi thi, Azan kahi , phir farmaya sun lo ! apney gharon mein Namaz padho , phir farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sard aur barsat wali raat Muazzan ko hukm farmaya kartey they ke wo kahey : ''apney gharon mein Namaz padho.'' muttafaq aleh."
1056,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Sham ka khana laga diya jaey aur Namaz ke liye iqaamat keh di jaey to pehley Sham ka khana kha lo, aur koi shakhs jaldi na karey yahan tak ke us se farigh ho jaey.'' ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye khana laga diya jata aur Namaz khadi kar di jati to aap us se farigh ho kar hi Namaz ke liye aaya kartey they, halanke wo Imam ki qirat sun rahey hotey they. muttafaq aleh."
1057,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''khaaney ke (samney) hotey huey Namaz hoti hai na us waqt ke jab do khabees chizen (peshab-pakhaney) usey rok rahi hon.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1058,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Namaz ke liye iqaamat keh di jaey to phir farz Namaz ke ilawa koi aur Namaz nahin hoti.'' rawahu Muslim."
1059,Hazrat Ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ki ehliya masjid janey ki ijazat talab karey to wo usey mana na karey.'' muttafaq aleh.
1060,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi masjid mein jaey to wo khushbu na lagaey.'' rawahu Muslim.
1061,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo aurat khushbu lagaey (khushbu ki dhooni ley) to wo hamarey sath Namaze-Isha padhney ke liye na aaye.'' rawahu Muslim."
1062,"Hazrat Ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni khawatin ko masaajid mein aaney se mana na karo, jabke unke ghar unke liye behtar hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1063,"Hazrat Ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat ka apney ghar ke andar Namaz padhna , ghar ke sehan mein Namaz padhney se afzal hai, aur uska ghar ke andar kisi kothri mein Namaz padhna , uskey khuley makaan mein Namaz padhney se afzal hai.''"
1064,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine apney mehbub Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''us aurat ki Namaz qubul nahin hoti jo masjid mein aaney ke liye khushbu lagaey yahan tak ke wo is tarah (khoob achhi tarah) ghusl karey jaisey ghusle-janabat kiya jata hai.'' Abu-Dawud, Ahmed aur Nasai ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kiya hai."
1065,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(kisi ajnabi ko shehwat ke sath dekhney wali) har aankh zaaniya hai, aur be-shak aurat jab itr laga kar kisi majlis ke paas se guzarti hai to wo aisi wesi yani zaaniya hai.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai ki riwayat bhi isi tarah hai."
1066,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaze-Fajr padhaai , jab salam phera to farmaya : ''kya falan shakhs mojud hai?'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, nahin, phir puchha : ''kya falan shakhs mojud hai?'' Sahaba ne arz kiya : nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye dono namazein munafiqon par bahut bhari hain, agar tum jaan lo ke un mein kitna ajr aur sawab hai to phir chahey (chaahe) tumhen ghutnon ke bal aana padta tum zarur aatey aur be-shak pehli saf (ajr aur fazilat ke lihaz sey) farishton ki saf ki tarah hai, aur agar tumhen uski fazilat ka ilm ho jaey to tum uski taraf zarur sabqat karo, be-shak aadmi ka doosrey aadmi ke sath Namaz padhna , uskey akeley Namaz padhney se behtar hai, aur uska do aadmiyon ke sath Namaz padhna , uskey eik aadmi ke sath Namaz padhney se behtar hai, aur jis qadr ziyada ho to wo Allah ko ziyada mehbub hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai ."
1067,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis basti aur jangal mein teen aadmi hon aur wahan ba-jamaat Namaz ka ehtimam na ho to phir (samjho ke) un par shetan ghalib aa chuka hai, tum jamaat ke sath lagey raho , bhediya alag aur door rehney wali bakri ko kha jata hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
1068,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Azan sun kar bila-uzr ba-jamaat Namaz padhney na aaye to wo jo akeley Namaz padhta hai wo qubul nahin hoti .'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, uzr kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khof ya marz.''"
1069,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi jaey aur tum mein se koi qazaey-hajat mehsus karey to pehley wo qazaey-hajat se farigh ho.'' isey Tirmizi ne riwayat kiya hai jabkey Maalik , Abu-Dawood aur Nasai ne isi ki misl (jaise) riwayat kiya hai."
1070,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen kaam aisey hain jin ka karna kisi ke liye halal nahin, koi shakhs jo muqtadiyon ko chhod kar sirf apni zaat ke liye dua karta ho wo unki imaamat na karaaey, agar wo aisey kerega to wo un se khayanat kerega, koi shakhs ijazat talab karney se pehley kisi ghar mein na jhaankey , agar usney aisey kiya, to usney un se khayanat ki, aur koi shakhs peshab-pakhaney rok kar Namaz na padhey yahan tak ke wo (us se farigh ho kar) halka ho jaey.'' Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi ki riwayat bhi isi tarah hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
1071,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khaaney aur kisi aur kaam ki khatir Namaz ko muakhkhar (taala) na karo.''"
1072,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham jantey they ke ba-jamaat Namaz se sirf wohi munafiq shakhs peechhey rehta tha jis ka munafiq hona malum tha, ya phir koi mareez reh jata tha, agar mareez do aadmiyon ke saharey chal sakta to wo ba-jamaat Namaz ke liye hazir hota, aur unhoney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen hidayat ki raahen sikhaeen, aur jis masjid mein Azan di jati ho is mein Namaz padhna hidayat ki raahon mein se hai. aur eik riwayat mein hai, farmaya : jis shakhs ko pasand ho ke wo kal musalman ki haisiyat se Allah se mulaqat karey to phir usey paanchon namazon ki ba-jamaat pabandi karni chahiye, be-shak Allah ne tumharey Nabi ke liye hidayat ki raahen muqarrar farma di hain, aur be-shak wo (paanchon namaazein) hidayat ki sunan mein se hain, agar tum ne Namaz se peechhey reh janey waley us shakhs ki tarah apney gharon mein Namaz padhi to tum apney Nabi ki sunnat chhod dogey , aur agar tum ne apney Nabi ki sunnat chhod di to tum gumrah ho jaaogey . aur jo shakhs achchhi tarah wuzu karkey kisi masjid ka qasd (irada) (iraada) karta hai to Allah uskey her qadam uthaney par uskey liye eik neki likh deta hai, uskey zariey eik darja buland farma deta hai aur uski wajeh se eik gunah maaf farma deta hai, aur ham jantey they ke Namaz se sirf wohi munafiq shakhs peechhey rehta tha jiskey nifaq ke barey mein malum hota tha, aur aisey bhi hota tha ke kisi aadmi ko do aadmiyon ke saharey la kar saf mein khada kar diya jata tha. rawahu Muslim."
1073,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar gharon mein khawatin aur bachchey na hotey to main Namaze-Isha qaaim karney ka hukm deta aur apney nojawanon ko hukm deta aur wo ghar mein mojud (Namaz se peechhey reh janey waley) logon ko aag se jala detey.''"
1074,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hukm farmaya : ''jab tum masjid mein ho aur Azan ho jaey to phir tum mein se koi shakhs Namaz padhey baghair wahan se bahar na jaey.''"
1075,"Hazrat Abu-Sha'shaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Azan ke baad masjid se bahar nikal gaya to usey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya is shakhs ne Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nafarmani ki . rawahu Muslim."
1076,"Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Azan ke waqt masjid mein mojud ho aur phir wo bila-zarurat masjid se nikal jaey aur uska wapis aaney ka bhi koi irada na ho to aisa shakhs munafiq hai.''"
1077,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Azan sun kar bila-uzr masjid mein na aaye to uski (masjid ke ilawa padhi hui) Namaz durust nahin.'' rawahu Daar Qutni."
1078,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Umme-Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Madina mein bahut ziyada moozi janwer aur darindey hain, jabkey main eik na-bina shakhs hun, kya aap merey liye koi gunjaaish paatey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum , aao Namaz ki taraf , aao kamiyabi ki taraf (yani Azan) suntey ho?'' unhoney arz kiya, ji haan. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya, ''isliye phir jaldi aao.'' aur aapney rukhsat na di."
1079,"Hazrat Umme-Dardaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ghusse ki haalat mein merey paas tashrif laye to maine puchha : aap kis wajeh se ghusse mein hain? unhoney farmaya Allah ki qism ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ummat ka eik hi kaam baqi reh gaya hai ke wo ba-jamaat Namaz ada kartey hain. Bukhari."
1080,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Abu Hashma bayan kartey hain ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Abu Hashma ko namaze-Fajr mein na paya , aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) baazar tashrif ley gaey, Suleman (Alaihissalam) ka ghar masjid aur baazar ke darmiyan waqey tha, to aap Suleman (Alaihissalam) ki walida Shifaa ke paas se guzrey to aapney un se puchha : maine Namaze-Fajr mein Suleman (Alaihissalam) nahin dekha . to unhoney arz kiya, wo raat bhar Namaz padhta raha aur phir usey neend aa gaee. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar main Namaze-Fajr ba-jamaat ada kar lun to ye mujhey raat bhar qiyam karney se ziyada mehbub hai."
1081,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do aur do se zayed eik jamaat hai.''"
1082,"Hazrat Bilal bin Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab khawatin tum se (masjid janey ki) ijazat talab karen to tum unhen masjid ke sawab se mehroom na rakho (ye sun kar) Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham unhen zarur roken gey , to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen farmaya : main kehta hun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya , aur tum kehtey ho, ham unhen rokengey. rawahu Muslim."
1083,"Hazrat Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ki apney walid (Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) se marwi (bayan) eik riwayat mein hai, unhoney kaha, Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar usey bahut ziyada bura bhala kaha, is tarah bura bhala kehtey huey maine unhen kabhi nahin suna, aur unhoney farmaya : main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hawaley se bayan kar raha hun jabkey tum kehtey ho ke Allah ki qism ! ham unhen zarur rokengey. rawahu Muslim."
1084,"Hazrat Mujahid (Raziallahu anhu) Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi shakhs apney ehle-khana ko masjid janey se na rokey.'' (ye sun kar) Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke eik bete ne kaha : ham unhen zarur rokengey. is par Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees bayan karta hun, aur tum ye keh rahey ho, raawi bayan kartey hain : Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne zindagi bhar us-se kalam nahin kiya."
1085,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamari safon ko aise barabar kiya kartey they goya unke sath teeron ko barabar kartey hon, yahan tak ke aapney samajh liya ke ham aap se seekh chukey hain. phir eik roz aap tashrif laye to khadey ho gaey, qarib tha ke aap takbir kehtey ke aapney eik aadmi ko dekha, uska Sina saf se bahar nikla hua hai, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke bando ! safein barabar kiya karo, warna Allah tumharey andar ikhtilaf paida farma dega.'' rawahu Muslim."
1086,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Namaz ke liye iqaamat keh di gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna chehra Mubarak hamari taraf kartey huey farmaya : ''safein durust rakho aur baham (aapas mein) mil kar khadey hua karo, kyonkey main tumhen apni pusht ke peechey se bhi dekhta hun.'' Bukhari. Sahih Bukhari aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safein mukammal karo kyonkey main tumhen apni pusht ke peechhey se bhi dekhta hun.'' Bukhari aur Muslim."
1087,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni safein barabar karo, be-shak safon ka barabar karna Namaz qaaim karney se hai.'' Bukhari , Muslim . albatta Sahih Muslim mein : ''Namaz mukammal karney se hai.'' ke alfaz hain. muttafaq aleh."
1088,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz mein apney haath hamarey kandhon par rakhtey aur farmatey : ''barabar ho jaao, ikhtilaf na karo warna tumharey dil mukhtalif ho jaeyngey, aur tum mein se sahibe-aql aur danish hazraat merey qarib khadey hua karen, phir jo unke qarib hain phir jo unke qarib hain.'' aur Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aur tum aaj sakht ikhtilaf ka shikar ho. rawahu Muslim."
1089,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se sahibe aql aur danish hazraat merey qarib khadey hua karen, phir jo un se qarib hon, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen martaba aisey farmaya aur bazaron ke shor (masayel) se bacho.'' rawahu Muslim."
1090,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Sahaba ka (pehli saf sey) peechhey hatna dekha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''aagey badho, meri iqtida (pairvi) karo aur tumharey baad waley tumhari iqtida (pairvi) karen, log peechhey hatey rahengey yahan tak ke Allah unhen (apni rehmat mein) peechhey kar dega.'' rawahu Muslim."
1091,"Hazrat Jabir bin Sumra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye to aapney hamein mukhtalif halqon mein dekh kar farmaya : ''kya wajeh hai main tumhen mutafarriq (alag-alag) dekh raha hun?'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye to farmaya : ''tum wesay safein kyon nahin banatey jis tarah farishtey apney Rab ke yahan safein banatey hain?'' ham ne arz kiya, farishtey apney Rab ke yahan kaisey safein banatey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo pehli safein mukammal kartey hain aur saf mein baham (aapas mein) mil kar khadey hotey hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
1092,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mardon ki safon mein se pehli saff, behtareen saf hai aur unki aakhiri saf kamtar hai, jabkey aurton ki aakhiri saf unki behtareen saf hai, aur unki pehli saf badtar hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
1093,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni safon ko khub milaoo aur inhen baham (aapas mein) qarib banaao, gardanon ko barabar aur muqabil rakho, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai? mein shetan ko dekhta hun ke wo bakri ke bachchey ki tarah safon ke shigaaf (darar) mein dakhil ho jata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
1094,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agli saf ko pura karo, phir usko jo uskey baad hai, isliye jo kami ho wo aakhiri saf mein honi chahiye.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1095,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''be-shak Allah aur uskey farishtey un logon par rehmat nazil farmatey hain jo pehli safon ko milaate hain, Allah ko wo qadam intehai mehbub hai jo saf mein milney ke liye uthaya jata hai.''"
1096,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah aur uskey farishtey safon ki daain janib walon par rehmat nazil farmatey hain.''"
1097,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ham Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamari safein barabar farmatey, jab ham barabar ho jatey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allahu-Akbar kehtey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1098,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni daain janib farmatey : ''barabar ho jaao, safein durust karo.'' aur apni baain janib bhi farmatey : ''barabar ho jaao , safein durust karo.''"
1099,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Namaz mein kandhey naram rakhney wala shakhs tum mein sab se behtar hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1100,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''barabar ho jaao , barabar ho jaao , barabar ho jaao , us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! main apni pusht se tumhen isi tarah dekhta hun jaisey main tumhen apney samney dekhta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1101,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah aur uskey farishtey pehli saf par rahmatein nazil farmatey hain.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! dusri par? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah aur uskey farishtey pehli saf par rahmatein nazil farmatey hain.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! dusri par? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah aur uskey farishtey pehli saf par rahmatein nazil farmatey hain.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! dusri par? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''doosri par.'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni safein barabar karo, kandhey barabar rakho , apney bhaiyon ke haathon mein naram ho jaao aur shigaaf (darar) band karo kyonkey shetan bakri ke bachchey ki tarah tumharey darmiyani shigaaf mein dakhil ho jata hai.''"
1102,"Hazrat Ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni safein qaaim karo, kandhey barabar rakho , shigaaf (darar) band karo, apney bhaiyon ke haathon ke liye naram ho jaao , shetan ke liye shigaaf ( khaali jagah ( na chhodo aur jo shakhs saf milaaeyga Allah (apni rehmat ke sath) usey milaaeyga aur jo usey qata' (todega) kerega, Allah usey (apni rehmat sey) qata' kar dega. ''Abu-Dawood. aur Imam Nasai (Raziallahu anhu) ne (من وصل صفا) se aakhir tak un se riwayat kiya hai."
1103,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Imam ko wast (beech) mein jagah do aur shigaaf (khali jagah/darar) band karo.''"
1104,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''log pehli saf se peechhey hattey rahengey yahan tak ke Allah unhen jahannam mein sab se aakhiri tabqey mein dal dega.''"
1105,"Hazrat Wabisa bin Maabad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne saf ke peechhey eik aadmi ko akeley Namaz padhtey huey dekha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey Namaz lautane ka hukm farmaya. Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1106,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine apni khaala Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar raat basar ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar Namaz padhney lagey to main bhi unke baain janib khada ho gaya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni pusht ke peechhey se mujhey bazu se pakad kar isi tarah apni pusht ke peechhey se mujhey apni daain janib khada kar liya. muttafaq aleh."
1107,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey Namaz padh rahey they, main aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baain taraf khada ho gaya, aapney mera haath pakad kar mujhey pher kar apni daain janib khada kar liya , phir Jabbaar bin Sakhr aaye to wo bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baain janib khadey ho gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen hamarey haathon se pakad kar peechhey hataayaa yahan tak ke aapney hamein apney peechhey khada kar diya. rawahu Muslim."
1108,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main aur eik yateem ne hamarey ghar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhi aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) (Umme- Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne hamarey peechhey. rawahu Muslim."
1109,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey aur meri walida ya meri khaala ko Namaz padhaai, wo bayan kartey hain, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey apni daain janib aur aurat ko apney peechhey khada kiya. rawahu Muslim."
1110,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunchey to aap rukoo farma rahey they, unhoney saf tak pahunchney se pehley hi rukoo kar liya , phir chal kar saf tak pahunch gaey, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kiya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tumhari hirs mein izafa farmaai , aainda aisey na karna.'' Bukhari."
1111,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hukm farmaya ke jab ham teen hon to ham mein se eik hamari imaamat karaaey."
1112,"Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney madaain mein logon ko imaamat karaai to wo chabootrey par khadey huey jabkey log un se nichey khadey they, Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne aagey badh kar unhen haathon se pakad liya to Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) unke peechhey peechhey chaltey gaey yahan tak ke Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen nichey utaar diya, jab Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz se farigh huey to Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen farmaya : kya aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey nahin suna? ''jab aadmi logon ki imaamat kiraaey to wo un se buland jagah par khada na ho.'' ya aapney is tarah ki baat farmaai , to Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : isi liye to main aap ke pakadney par aap ke peechhey chal diya tha."
1113,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke un se puchha gaya ke member kis chiz se banaya gaya tha? to unhoney farmaya : Gaba ke jhaaoo se bana hua tha aur falan aurat (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu)) ke azad karda ghulam ne usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye banaya tha. jab usey bana kar rakh diya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is par qibla rukh khadey ho kar Allahu-Akbar kaha, aur log aap ke peechhey khadey ho gaey, aapney qirat ki, rukoo kiya aur logon ne bhi aap ke peechey rukoo kiya, phir aapney sar uthaya , phir ultey paaon wapis aaye aur zamin par sajda kiya, phir member par tashrif laye, phir qirat ki, phir rukoo kiya phir sar uthaya, phir ultey paaon wapis aaye yahan tak ke zamin par sajda kiya. ye sahih Bukhari ke alfaz hain, jabkey Sahih Bukhari aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat bhi isi tarah hai, aur is riwayat ke aakhir mein hai : jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farigh huey to logon ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : ''logo ! maine ye isliye kiya hai taake tum meri iqtida (pairvi) karo aur tum meri Namaz seekh lo.'' muttafaq aleh."
1114,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hujre mein Namaz padhi jabkey log hujrey ke bahar se aap ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1115,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kya main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke mutalliq na bataaun? aapney Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi , aur mardon ne saf banai , aur unke peechhey bachchon ne saf banai phir aapney unhen Namaz padhaai , aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ka tazkira kartey huey farmaya : is tarah Namaz hai, Abdul-A'alaa ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke aapney farmaya : ''meri ummat ki Namaz is tarah hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1116,"Hazrat Qais bin Ibaad bayan kartey hain, isi beech mein ke main masjid mein pehli saf mein tha ke kisi aadmi ne mujhey zor se peechhey khincha , wo mujhey wahan se hata kar khud wahan khada ho gaya, Allah ki qism ! mujhey apni Namaz ke barey mein kuchh yad na raha , jab Namaz se farigh huey to wo Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) they, unhoney farmaya : nojawan ! Allah tumhen kisi takleef se dochaar na karey, be-shak ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se hamarey liye hukm hai ke ham Imam ke paas khadey hon, phir unhoney qibla rukh khadey ho kar farmaya : ''ehle-aqd'' halak ho gaey, Rabe-Kaaba ki qism ! mujhey un par koi afsos nahin, lekin mujhey afsos to un par hai jinhon ne gumrah kiya, maine kaha : Abu-Yaqub ! ''ehle-aqd'' se kon murad hain? unhoney farmaya : hukmran. rawahu Nasai."
1117,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon ki imaamat wo shakhs kiraaey jo un mein se Kitabullah ko ziyada padhney (janney , samajhney) wala ho, isliye agar wo qirat mein sab barabar hon to phir un mein se jo sunnat ko ziyada janney wala ho, agar wo sunnat mein barabar hon to phir un mein se jisney hijrat pehley ki ho, aur agar wo hijrat karney mein barabar hon to phir un mein se jo umr mein bada ho, aur koi shakhs kisi ki jagah (bila ijazat) imaamat kiraaey na bila ijazat uskey ghar mein uski izzat ki jagah bethey.'' Muslim. aur Muslim hi ki riwayat mein hai : ''koi aadmi kisi aadmi ki uskey ghar mein imaamat na karaaey.'' rawahu Muslim."
1118,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab teen afrad hon to un mein se eik unki imaamat kiraaey aur un mein se jo ziyada Quran padhney wala hai wo imaamat ka ziyada haq daar hai.'' Muslim, aur Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees (baab fazale-azaan) ke baad waley baab (silsile) mein bayan ho chuki hai. rawahu Muslim."
1119,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se behtar shakhs Azan kahe aur tum mein se behtar qaari tumhen Namaz padhaaey.''"
1120,"Hazrat Abu Atiya Uqeeli bayan kartey hain, Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) hamari Namaz ki jagah par hamarey paas tashrif laya kartey aur baaten kiya kartey they, eik roz Namaz ka waqt ho gaya, Abu Atiya ne kaha, ham ne unse darkhast ki ke wo aagey badhen aur Namaz padhaein , unhoney hamen farmaya : apney kisi aadmi ko aagey karo wo tumhen Namaz padhaaey ga : ''main an-qareeb tumhen bataaun ga ke main tumhen Namaz kyon nahin padhata , maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs kisi qom ke paas jaey to wo unki imaamat na kiraaey balke unhi mein se koi shakhs unki imaamat karaaey.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai , albatta unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke alfaz tak iktifa kiya (kafi samjha) hai."
1121,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ibne-Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) ko khalifa muqarrar farmaya , wo logon ki imaamat karatey they halanke wo na-bina they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1122,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen qism ke logon ki Namaz unke kanon se aagey nahin jati , bhaga hua ghulam yahan tak ke wo wapis aa jaey, wo aurat jo us haal mein raat basar karey ke uska khawind is par naraz ho, aur logon ka Imam jabkey wo usey na pasand kartey hon.'' Tirmizi aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
1123,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen qism ke logon ki Namaz qubul nahin hoti : wo Imam jisey muqtadi na pasand kartey hon, eik wo shakhs jo Namaz ka waqt guzar janey ke baad Namaz padhta hai, aur eik wo aadmi jo kisi azad shakhs ko ghulam banaley.''"
1124,"Hazrat Sulama binte Hur (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat ki eik nishani ye bhi hai ke masjid waley Namaz padhaaney se jaan chhudaen gey wo Namaz padhaaney ke liye koi Imam nahin paeyn gey.''"
1125,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Har ameer ke sath mein jihad karna tum par farz hai, chahey (chaahe) wo nek ho ya faajir, agar-che wo kabeera gunahon ka murtakib ho, aur har musalman ke peechhey Namaz padhna tum par wajib hai chahey wo nek ho ya faajir, agar-che wo kabeera gunahon ka murtakib ho aur har musalman par Namaz padhna wajib hai chahey wo nek ho ya faajir , agar-che wo kabeera gunahon ka murtakib ho.''"
1126,"Hazrat Amr bin Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham eik chashme par rihaaish pazeer they jo logon ke liye aam guzar gaah tha, qafiley hamarey paas se guzartey to ham un se poochhtey rehtey ke ab logon ka kya haal hai? aur us shakhs ki kya keyfiyat hai? to wo kehtey is shakhs ka khayal hai ke Allah ne usey Rasool bana kar bheja hai, uski taraf ye ye wahi ki gaee hai, main unse ye baaten yad kar leta , goya wo merey dil mein ghar kar gaee hain, aur Arab Islam qubul karney ke barey mein Fateh Makka ke muntazir they, wo kehtey they : usey aur uski qom ko (uskey haal par) chhod do , agar wo un par ghalib aa gaya to wo sachcha Nabi hai, jab Makka Fateh hua to har qom ne Islam qubul karney mein jaldi ki, aur merey walid ne bhi Islam qubul karney main apni qom se jaldi ki, jab wo wapis pahunchey to unhoney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main sachchay Nabi ke paas se tumharey paas aaya hun, unhoney farmaya : ''ye Namaz us waqt padho aur ye Namaz us waqt padho, tum mein se koi eik shakhs Azan keh dey aur tum mein se ziyada Quran padhney wala tumhari imaamat karaaey.'' unhoney jayeza liya to mujh se ziyada Quran janney wala koi nahin tha, kyonkey mein qafilon se sun kar Quran ka ilm hasil kar chuka tha, unhoney mujhey apna Imam bana liya , main us waqt chhe ya saat baras ka tha, merey ooper eik chadar hi thi, jab main sajda karta to wo sikud jati , (aur mera sattar khul jata, ye dekh kar) qabiley ki eik aurat ne kaha : tum apney Imam ki peeth ham se kyon nahin chhupatey ho? unhoney (kapda) kharid aur merey liye qameez banai , main jitna us qameez se khush hua itna kisi aur chiz se khush nahin hua. Bukhari."
1127,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab awwal muhajrin Madina tashrif laye to Abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam Salim unki imaamat karaya kartey they jabkey umr (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Salma bin Abdul Asad (Raziallahu anhu) unmein mojud they. Bukhari."
1128,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen qism ke log hain, jin ki namazein unke sar se eik baalisht bhi ooper nahin jatin : wo Imam jiskey muqtadi us-se naraz hon, wo aurat jo us haal mein raat basar karey ke uska khawind us se naraz ho aur baham (aapas mein) qata' talluq kar leney waley do bhai.''"
1129,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki si bahut halki aur bahut kamil Namaz kisi Imam ke peechhey nahin padhi , jab aap kisi bachchey ke roney ki aawaz suntey to us andeshe ke pesh-nazar ke uski walida kisi aazmaaish se dochaar ho jaeygi, Namaz halki kar diya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
1130,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main lambi Namaz padhney ke iraday se Namaz shuru karta hun, lekin phir main bachchey ke roney ki aawaz sunta hun to apni Namaz mein kami kar deta hun, isliye ke main janta hun ke uskey roney ki wajeh se uski walida ghamgin hoti hai.'' Bukhari."
1131,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi logon ko Namaz padhaaey to wo chhoti karey, kyonkey un mein bimar , zaeef aur boodhey hotey hain, aur jab tum mein se koi shakhs akela Namaz padhey to phir jis qadr chahey lambi padhey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1132,"Hazrat Qais bin Abi Hazim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya ke eik aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! Allah ki qism ! main falan shakhs ki wajeh se Namaze-Fajr der se padhta hun, kyonkey wo hamen bahut lambi Namaz padhata hai, chunanche maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko waaz nasihat kartey waqt us din se ziyada naraz kabhi nahin dekha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak tum mein kuchh nafrat dilaney waley bhi hain, isliye tum mein se jo shakhs logon ko Namaz padhaaey to wo ikhtisaar se kaam ley kyonkey un mein zaeef , boodhey aur hajat mand bhi hotey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
1133,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo (Imam) tumhen Namaz padhaein gey , chunanche agar unhoney durust padhaai to tumharey liye ajr hai, aur agar unhoney ghalati ki to tumharey liye ajr hai aur un par gunah hai.'' Bukhari."
1134,"Hazrat Usman bin Abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mujhey aakhiri wasiyat ye thi : ''jab tum logon ki imaamat karaao to unhen halki Namaz padhaao.'' Muslim . unhi se marwi (bayan) eik riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''apni qom ki imaamat karaao.'' wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main apney dil mein kuchh waswasa paata hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qarib ho jaao.'' Aapney mujhey apney samney bitha liya , phir aapney apna haath meri chhaati par rakh diya, phir farmaya : ''pehlu badlo.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna haath merey kandhon ke darmiyan meri pusht par rakha , phir farmaya : ''apni qom ki imaamat karaao, jo shakhs kisi qom ki imaamat kiraaey to wo halki Namaz padhaaey, kyonkey un mein boodhey hotey hain, un mein mareez hotey hain, un mein zaeef hotey hain, aur un mein koi hajat mand hotey hain, jab tum mein se koi akela Namaz padhey to phir jaisey chahey padhey.'' rawahu Muslim."
1135,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein halki Namaz padhaaney ka hukm diya kartey they, jabkey Aap Sura Saffaat se hamari imaamat karaya kartey they. rawahu Nasai."
1136,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padha kartey they, jab Aap ''Sami-Allahu-liman-hamida'' farmatey to ham mein se koi shakhs apni kamar na jhukaataa yahan tak ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni peshani zamin par rakh detey. muttafaq aleh."
1137,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhaai , jab aap Namaz padh chukey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna chehra Mubarak hamari taraf kartey huey farmaya : ''logo ! main tumhara Imam hun, tum rukoo aur sujood , qiyam aur Namaz se farigh honey mein mujh se sabqat na kiya karo, kyonkey main apney aagey aur peechhey se tumhen dekhta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
1138,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Imam se sabqat na karo, jab wo Allahu-Akbar kahe to tum Allahu-Akbar kaho , jab wo (ولاالضالین) kahe to tum Aameen kaho, jab rukoo karey to rukoo karo, jab ''Sami-Allahu-liman hamida'' kahe to tum ''ربنا لک الحمد'' kaho.'' Bukhari, Muslim. lekin Imam Bukhari ne : ''aur jab (ولاالضالین) kahe.'' ka zikr nahin kiya. muttafaq aleh."
1139,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghodey par Sawar huey to aap us-se gir gaey, jis se Aap ki daain janib kharaashein aa gaeen, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne koi eik Namaz beth kar padhaai , to ham ne bhi aap ke peechhey beth kar Namaz padhi , jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farigh huey to farmaya : ''Imam isi liye banaya jata hai ke uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey jab wo khadey ho kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi khadey ho kar Namaz padho , jab rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo, jab wo sar uthaey to tum bhi sar uthaao, jab wo (Sami-Allahu-liman hamida) kahe to tum (ربنا لک الحمد) kaho , aur jab wo beth kar Namaz padhey to tum sab beth kar Namaz padho.'' Humaidi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye farman , Aap ke marz qadim ke waqt ka hai, phir uskey baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne beth kar Namaz padhaai to Sahaba ne aap ke peechhey khadey ho kar Namaz padhi, aapney unhen bethney ka hukm nahin farmaya , aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka aakhiri kaam bator hujjat liya jata hai, ye Sahih Bukhari ke alfaz hain, aur Imam Muslim ne (اجمعون) tak ittifaq kiya hai, aur eik riwayat mein izafa naqal kiya hai : ''us se ikhtilaf na karo, aur jab wo sajda karey to tum sajda karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
1140,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar huey to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ko Namaz ki ittilaa karney aaye , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm do ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaein, chunanche Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne un dinon mein Namaz padhaai , phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuchh ifaaqa faayda mehsus kiya to Aap ko do aadmiyon ke saharey laya gaya us haal mein aap ke paaon zamin par lag rahey they, yahan tak ke aap masjid mein dakhil huye, jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap ki aamad mehsus ki to wo peechhey hatney lagey , lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen ishara farmaya ke peechhey na hatein , Aap tashrif laye aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baain janib beth gaey, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho kar Namaz padha rahey they jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baith kar , Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they jabkey log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki Namaz ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they. Bukhari , Muslim , un dono ki eik riwayat mein hai, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko takbir sunatey they. muttafaq aleh."
1141,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Imam se pehley apna sar utha leta hai wo is baat se nahin darta ke Allah kahin uskey sar ko gadhey ka sar na bana dey. muttafaq aleh."
1142,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz ke liye aaye to wo jis haal mein Imam ko paey to wo bhi usi haalat mein unke sath shamil ho jaey.'' Tirmizi. aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1143,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz ke liye aao aur ham sajde ki haalat mein hun to tum bhi sajda karo, aur usey kuchh bhi shumar na karo, jisney eik rakat pa-li usney Namaz pa-li.''"
1144,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ki raza ki khatir chaalis roz takbire-aula ke sath ba-jamaat Namaz padhta hai, uskey liye do chizon : jahannam aur nifaq se bara-at (chhoot) likh di jati hai.''"
1145,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs achhi tarah wuzu karkey Namaz ke liye jaey lekin wo logon ko paey ke wo Namaz padh chukey hon to Allah usey ba-jamaat Namaz padhney walon ki misl (jaisa) ajr ata farma deta hai, aur us se unke ajr mein bhi koi kami waqey nahin hogi.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
1146,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi aaya jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh chukey they, aapney farmaya : ''kya koi shakhs is par sadqa kerega ke wo uskey sath Namaz padhey?'' eik aadmi khada hua to usney uskey sath (ba-jamaat) Namaz padhi. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
1147,"Hazrat Ubaidullah bin Abdullah bayan kartey hain, main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya aur arz kiya : kya Aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke marz ke mutalliq mujhey kuchh bataeyngi? unhoney farmaya : kyon nahin, farmaya : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar huey to aapney puchha : ''kya log Namaz padh chukey hain?'' ham ne arz kiya, nahin, Allah ke Rasool ! wo to Aap ka intizar kar rahey hain, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey tab mein pani dalo.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ham ne pani dal diya to aapney ghusl farmaya , aapney uthney ka qasd (irada) (iraada) kiya to aap par ghashi taari ho gaee , phir ifaaqa (faayda) hua to farmaya : ''kya log Namaz padh chukey hain?'' ham ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! nahin, wo Aap ka intizar kar rahey hain Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey liye tab mein pani dalo .'' aapney beth kar ghusl farmaya , phir uthney ka qasd (irada) kiya to aap par ghashi taari ho gaee , phir ifaaqa hua to farmaya : ''kya log Namaz padh chukey hain.'' ham ne arz kiya, nahin Allah ke Rasool ! aur log masjid mein khadey Namaze-Isha ke liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke muntazir they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf pegham bheja ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaein, qaasid unke paas aaya aur usney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aap ko hukm farma rahey hain ke aap logon ko Namaz padhaein, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne , jo ke narm-dil they, farmaya : umr ! aap Namaz padhaein , to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen farmaya : aap iskey ziyada haq-daar hain, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne un dinon mein Namaz padhaai , phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni tabiat mein behtari mehsus ki to Aap do aadmiyon , un mein se eik Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) they, ke saharey namaze-Zohar ke liye tashrif laye jabkey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padha rahey they, jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap ko dekha to wo peechhey hatney lagey, lekin Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen peechhey na hatney ka ishara farmaya , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey unke pehlu mein bitha do.'' unhoney Aap ko Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke pehlu mein bitha diya, aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne beth kar Namaz ada ki . Ubaidullah bayan kartey hain, main Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya, to maine unhen kaha : kya main tumhen wo hadees bayan karun jo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke marz ke mutalliq mujhey bayan ki hai, unhoney farmaya : bayan karo, maine un se marwi (bayan) hadees unhen bayan ki to unhoney is hadees mein se kisi chiz ka inkar na kiya, albatta unhoney ye puchha : kya unhoney Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath doosrey aadmi ke naam ke barey main tumhen bataya tha? maine kaha : nahin, unhoney farmaya : wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they. muttafaq aleh."
1148,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jisney rukoo pa liya to usney rakaat pa li , aur jisey Sura Fatiha na mili to wo khair Kasir se mehroom ho gaya."
1149,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jo shakhs Imam se pehley sar utha leta hai aur us se pehley jhuka deta hai to uski peshani shetan ke haath mein hai.''"
1150,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padha kartey they, phir wo apni qom ke paas jatey aur unhen Namaz padhatey they. muttafaq aleh."
1151,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Muaz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaze-Isha ada kartey phir apni qom ke paas jatey aur unhen Namaze-Isha padhatey, aur ye (baad wali Namaz) unke liye nafl hoti thi. rawahu Dar-Qutni."
1152,"Hazrat Yazid bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Haj kiya, maine Namaze-Fajr aap ke sath masjid khaif mein ada ki, jab Aap Namaz padh chukey aur peechhey mudey to wahan aakhir par do aadmi bethey huey they jinhonne aap ke sath Namaz nahin padhi thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen merey paas laao.'' unhen laya gaya to wo ghabrahat se kaanp rahey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum dono ne hamarey sath Namaz kyon nahin padhi?'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham apney gharon mein Namaz padh chukey they? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisey na kiya karo, jab tum apney gharon mein Namaz padh chuko aur phir tumhen masjid mein jamaat mil jaey to unke sath bhi Namaz padh liya karo, kyonkey wo tumharey liye nafl hogi.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
1153,"Hazrat basar bin Mohjin apney walid se riwayat kartey hain unhoney kaha ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath kisi majlis mein mojud they, itney mein Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey aur Namaz padh kar wapis tashrif ley aaye jabkey Mohjin apni jagah par hi they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unse puchha : ''tum ne logon ke sath Namaz kyon nahin padhi , kya tum musalman nahin ho?'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kyon nahin, zarur musalman hain, lekin main apney ghar Namaz padh chuka tha, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz padhney ke baad masjid mein aao , aur Namaz ho rahi ho to tum jamaat ke sath Namaz padho chahey (chaahe) tum Namaz padh hi chukey ho.'' rawahu Malik aur Nasai."
1154,"Hazrat Asad bin Khuzaima ke qabiley ke eik shakhs se riwayat hai ke unhoney Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se masla daryaft kiya, ham mein se koi shakhs apney ghar mein Namaz padh kar masjid mein aata hai aur Namaz ho rahi ho to kya main unke sath Namaz padhun? is par mera dil mutmain nahin hota, Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne is barey mein puchha tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : uskey liye jamaat ka sawab hai.''"
1155,"Hazrat Yazid bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap Namaz padh rahey they, main beth gaya aur unke sath Namaz mein shareek na hua , jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farigh huey to aapney mujhey bethey huey dekh kar farmaya : '' Yazid ! kya tum musalman nahin?'' maine arz kiya, kyon nahin, Allah ke Rasool ! main to musalman hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne jamaat ke sath Namaz kyon nahin padhi?'' unhoney arz kiya, main samjha ke Aap Namaz padh chukey hongey lihaza maine ghar mein padh li thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz ke liye aao aur logon ko paao to phir tum unke sath Namaz padho aur agar tum padh chukey ho to phir wo tumharey liye nafl hogi aur ye farz.''"
1156,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne un se puchha usney kaha : main ghar mein Namaz padh lun aur phir masjid mein ba-jamaat Namaz pa lun to phir kya main jamaat ke sath shareek ho jaaun? unhoney usey bataya , haan , us aadmi ne kaha : main un mein se kis ko apni (farz) Namaz qarar dun? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kya tujhey uska ikhtiyar hai? uska ikhtiyar to Shan Wale Allah ko hasil hai ke wo unmein se jisey chahey (farz) banaey. rawahu Malik."
1157,"Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam Suleman (Alaihissalam) bayan kartey hain, ham maqam balaat par ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye to wo log Namaz padh rahey they, maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya aap unke sath Namaz nahin padhtey? unhoney farmaya : main padh chuka hun, aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''eik Namaz ko eik hi din mein do martaba na padho.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
1158,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : jo shakhs Namaze-Maghrib ya Namaze-Fajr padh ley , phir wo unhen Imam ke sath pa ley to wo unhen dobara na padhey. rawahu Malik."
1159,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs din aur raat mein (farz Namaz ke ilawa) baara rakatein padhta hai to uskey liye jannat main eik ghar bana diya jata hai : Zohar se pehley chaar aur uskey baad do rakatein , maghrib ke baad do rakaat , Isha ke baad do aur Namaze-Fajr se pehley do rakatein.'' Tirmizi aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai ke unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo musalman aadmi har roz faraaiz ke ilawa Allah ki raza ki khatir baara rakatein nafl ada karta hai to Allah uskey liye jannat main eik ghar bana deta hai, ya uskey liye jannat main eik ghar bana diya jata hai.'' rawahu Muslim aur Tirmizi."
1160,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Zohar se pehley do rakatein padhein aur uskey baad , maghrib ke baad do rakatein Aap ke ghar padhein aur do rakatein Isha ke baad aap ke ghar mein padhein , aur unhoney bayan kiya, Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ( jo ke aap ki behan thin ( ne mujhey hadees bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr tulu ho janey par halki si do rakatein padha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
1161,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume ke baad ghar tashrif ley ja kar sirf do rakatein padha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
1162,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaqiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nafl Namaz ke mutalliq Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha to unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar se pehley chaar rakatein merey ghar mein padhtey , phir Namaz padhaaney tashrif ley jatey , phir aa kar do rakatein padhtey , phir aap namaze-Maghrib padhatey , phir ghar tashrif la kar do rakatein padhtey , phir Namaz Isha padhatey aur merey ghar tashrif la kar do rakatein padhtey , aap witr samet no rakaat Namaz tahajjud padha kartey they, aap raat der tak khadey ho kar Namaz padhtey aur der tak beth kar Namaz padhtey , jab aap khadey ho kar qirat kartey to rukoo w sujood bhi khadey ho kar kartey , aur jab aap beth kar qirat kartey to rukoo w sujood bhi beth kar hi kartey, aur jab Fajr tulu ho jati to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do rakatein padhtey . Muslim , aur Imam Abu-Dawood ne ye izafa naqal kya hai : phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-Fajr padhaaney ke liye tashrif ley jatey. rawahu Muslim w Abu-Dawood ."
1163,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nawaafil mein se Fajr ki do rakaaton ka bahut khayal rakhtey they. muttafaq aleh."
1164,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Fajr ki do rakatein , duniya aur jo kuch duniya mein hai, se behtar hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1165,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' namaze-Maghrib se pehley do rakatein padho , namaze-Maghrib se pehley do rakatein padho .''teesri martaba is dar sey ke log usey sunnat na bana lein, farmaya : ''jo koi chahey ( padhey ( .'' muttafaq aleh."
1166,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jo shakhs Juma ke baad Namaz padhna chahey to wo chaar rakaat padhey .'' Muslim aur unhi ki dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jab tum mein se koi Juma padhey to wo uskey baad chaar rakatein padhey . rawahu Muslim ."
1167,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs Zohar se pehley chaar rakaat aur uskey baad chaar rakaat hamesha ada karta hai to Allah usey jahannam par haram qarar dey deta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
1168,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Zohar se pehley chaar rakaaton ke liye , jin mein salam na phera gaya ho, aasman ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain.''"
1169,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zawal aaftaab ke baad namaze-Zohar se pehley chaar rakatein padha kartey they, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye wo ghadi hai jab aasman ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain, lihaza mein pasand karta hun ke is waqt mera koi amal Saleh ooper jaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
1170,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah, Asr se pehley chaar rakatein padhney waley shakhs par rehem farmaey.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood."
1171,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Asr se pehley chaar rakatein padha kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muqarrab farishton, aur unki ittiba karney waley musalmanon aur mominon par salam bhej kar farq kya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1172,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Asr se pehley do rakatein padha kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1173,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera bayan kartey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs maghrib ke baad chhe rakatein padhey aur wo unke darmiyan koi buri baat na karey to uskey liye baara saal ki ibadat ke barabar sawab likh diya jata hai.'' Tirmizi, unhoney kaha : ye hadees gharib hai, ham usey sirf umr bin abi khas-am se marwi (bayan) hadees ke hawaley se jantey hain jabkey maine Muhammad bin Ismail (Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu)) ko farmatey huey suna : wo munkar hadees hai, aur unhoney usey bahut ziyada zaeef qarar diya hai."
1174,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs maghrib ke baad bees rakatein padhta hai to Allah uskey liye jannat mein ghar bana deta hai."
1175,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bhi Isha padh kar merey paas tashrif latey to aap chaar ya chhe rakaat Namaz nafl ada kartey they."
1176,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sitaron ke doobney ke baad se murad Fajr se pehley ki do rakatein aur sajdon ke baad se maghrib ke baad do rakatein hain.''"
1177,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' zawal aaftaab ke baad Zohar se pehley chaar rakaat ka sawab Namaz tahajjud ki chaar rakaat ke sawab ke barabar hai, us waqt her chiz Allah ki tasbih bayan karti hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : '' unke saye daain se aur baain se laut'tey rehtey hain, Allah ke samney jhuktey aur aajizi ka izhar kartey hain.''"
1178,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Asr ke baad do rakatein merey yahan kabhi tarak nahin kin. Bukhari. Muslim, aur sahih Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai, unhoney farmaya is zaat ki qism jisney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wafat di! aapney zindagi bhar ye do rakatein nahin chodin. muttafaq aleh."
1179,"Hazrat mukhtar bin Fulful (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se namaze-Asr ke baad nafl Namaz padhney ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney farmaya : umr (Raziallahu anhu) namaze-Asr ke baad nafl Namaz padhney par haathon par maara kartey they, aur ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein ghurub aaftaab ke baad namaze-Maghrib se pehley do rakatein padha kartey they, raawi kehtey hain maine un se puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen padha kartey they? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen unhen padhtey dekha kartey they lekin aapney hamen hukm farmaya na mana farmaya. rawahu Muslim ."
1180,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Madina mein they, jab Muazzan namaze-Maghrib ke liye Azan kehta to Sahaba sutonon ki taraf dodtey aur do rakatein padhtey, yahan tak ke koi ajnabi shakhs masjid mein aata to wo un rakaaton ko padhney walon ki kasrat dekh kar samajhta ke Namaz ho chuki hai. rawahu Muslim ."
1181,"Hazrat Marsad bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Aqba Johni (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya to maine kaha : kya bano Tameem ke mutalliq main tumhen tajjub angez baat na bataaun ke wo namaze-Maghrib se pehley do rakatein padhtey hain, to Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ham bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein un par amal paira they, maine kaha : ab tumhen kon si chiz maane (rukawat) hai? unhoney farmaya : mashghooliyat . Bukhari ."
1182,"Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bano Abdul-Ash'hal qabiley ki masjid mein tashrif laye to aapney wahan namaze-Maghrib ada ki, jab wo Namaz padh chukey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey baad unhen nawafil padhtey huey dekha to farmaya : ''ye gharon ( mein padhi janey) wali Namaz hai.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi aur Nasai ki riwayat mein hai : log khadey ho kar nafl padhney lagey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ye Namaz gharon mein padha karo.'' ."
1183,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maghrib ke baad do rakaat mein qirat lambi kya kartey they yahan tak ke namazi chaley jatey. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1184,"Hazrat Mak-hool (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs maghrib ke baad kalam karney se pehley do rakatein padhta hai.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' chaar rakatein padhta hai, to uski Namaz illiyeen mein buland ki jati hai.'' ye riwayat mursal hai."
1185,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi isi tarah marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney izafa naqal kya hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : '' maghrib ke baad do rakatein padhney mein jaldi kya karo, kyonkey wo farz Namaz ke sath buland ki jati hain.'' ye dono riwaayatein rizeen ne riwayat ki hain, Behaqi ne Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) zayed alfaz Shobil-emaan mein isi tarah riwayat kiye hain."
1186,"Hazrat Amr bin ata (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Naafe bin Juber ne unhen Saaib ke paas bheja taake wo un se us chiz ke mutalliq puchey jo Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se dorane-namaz dekhi, Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : haan, maine Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath maqsoora (hukkaam ke liye khas kamra) mein Namaz Juma ada ki, jab Imam ne salam phera to maine apni usi jagah khadey ho kar Namaz shuru kar di, jab wo apney ghar tashrif ley gaey to unhoney meri taraf pegham bhejtey huey farmaya : aainda aisey na karna , tum ne aisey kyon kya? jab tum Namaz Juma padh lo to phir tum kalam kar leney ya wahan se chaley janey tak koi Namaz na padho , kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen hukm farmaya tha ke ham ( farz ( Namaz ke sath koi nafl na milaaein yahan tak ke ham baat cheet kar lein ya wahan se kahin aur chaley jaeyn . rawahu Muslim."
1187,"Hazrat Ata (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Makka mein Namaz Juma ada farmatey to thoda sa aagey badh kar do rakatein padhtey , phir aagey badh kar chaar rakatein padhtey aur jab Madina mein hotey to Juma padh kar apney ghar tashrif ley jatey aur do rakatein padhtey aur masjid mein na padhtey , jab un se puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi kya kartey they. Abu-Dawud, aur Tirmizi ki eik riwayat mein hai : unhoney bayan kya, maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney Juma ke baad do rakatein padhein phir uskey baad chaar rakatein padhin. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
1188,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Isha se farigh ho kar tulu Fajr tak giyara rakatein padha kartey they, aap her do rakaat ke baad salam phertey they, aur eik rakat witr padhtey they, aap is mein itna lamba sajda farmatey ke aap ke sar uthaney se pehley koi shakhs pachas aayaat ki tilawat kar leta, jab Muazzan namaze-Fajr ki Azan se farigh ho jata aur Fajr wazeh ho jati to aap halki si do rakatein padhtey aur phir daain pehlu par let jatey yahan tak ke Muazzan khidmat mein hazir ho kar iqaamat ke liye darkhast karta to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( Namaz padhaaney ke liye ( tashrif ley jatey. muttafaq aleh."
1189,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki do rakatein padh letey to agar main bedaar hoti to aap mujh se baat waghera kar letey warna let jatey. rawahu Muslim ."
1190,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki do rakatein padh letey to aap apney daain pehlu par let jatey they. muttafaq aleh."
1191,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko witr aur Fajr ki do rakaaton samet 13 rakaat Namaz tahajjud padha kartey they. rawahu Muslim ."
1192,"Hazrat Masruq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki raat ki Namaz ke barey mein daryaft kya, to unhoney farmaya : Fajr ki do rakaaton ke ilawa saat , no aur giyara rakaat thi. Bukhari ."
1193,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz tahajjud ke liye raat ko khadey hotey to aap do halki rakaaton se apni Namaz ki shuruat kya kartey they. rawahu Muslim ."
1194,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi raat ko qiyam karey to do halki rakaaton se aaghaz karey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1195,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine apni khaala Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan eik raat basar ki, jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke yahan they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney ehle khana ke sath kuch der baat cheet ki aur phir so gaey, jab aakhiri tihai raat ya kuch raat baqi reh gaee to aap uth kar beth gaey, aur aasman ki taraf nazar utha kar ye aayat tilawat farmaai : '' be-shak zamin w aasman ki takhleeq mein aur shabb w roz ke aaney janey mein aql mandon ke liye nishaniyan hain.'' yahan tak ke aapney sura mukammal farmaai , phir aap mishkeezey ki taraf gaey, phir uska munh khol kar tab mein pani liya aur ifraat w tafrit ke baghair khub achi tarah wuzu kya, phir aap khadey ho kar Namaz padhney lagey , main bhi khada hua aur wuzu karkey aap ke baain janib khada ho gaya, aapney mujhey kaan se pakad kar ghumaa kar apney daain janib kar liya , aapney tera rakaat Namaz mukammal ki, phir aap let gaey, aur so gaey yahan tak ke aap kharratey bhadney lagey, aur jab aap so jatey to kharratey bhartey, phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Namaz ki ittilaa di, pas aapney aur wuzu na kya aur aap ye dua kya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! merey dil mein , meri aankhon mein , merey kaanon-mein , merey daain , merey baain , merey ooper , merey nichey , merey aagey aur merey peechey aur merey liye Noor kar dey .'' aur un mein se baaz ne ye izafa naqal kya hai : ''meri zaban mein Noor kar dey .'' aur ye bhi zikr kya hai : ''merey patthey , gosht , mera khoon , merey baal aur mera badan noorani bana dey.'' muttafaq aleh. aur saheehain ki riwayat mein hai : '' aur merey nafs mein Noor aur bahut hi Noor bakhsh.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein jo Muslim mein hai : ''aey Allah ! to mujhey Noor ata farma .''"
1196,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan soey , aap bedaar huye, miswak ki aur wuzu kya, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : '' be-shak aasmano aur zamin ki takhleeq mein '' , '' .'' aakhir sura tak . phir aap khadey huey do rakatein padhein un mein qiyam aur rukoo w sujood lamba kya, phir aap aa kar so gaey yahan tak ke aap kharratey bhadney lagey , phir aapney teen martaba aisey kartey huey chhe rakatein padhein , aap her martaba miswak kartey , wuzu kartey aur un aayaat ki tilawat farmatey they, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen witr padhey . rawahu Muslim ."
1197,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : main aaj raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz tahajjud dekhunga. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do halki si rakatein padhin, phir do rakatein bahut hi lambi padhin, phir do rakatein padhein jo pehli do se qadrey mukhtasar thin, phir do rakatein un se kam lambi padhein , phir do rakatein un se kam lambi padhein , phir aapney witr padha , ye tera rakatein huin . rawahu Muslim w Malik w Abu-Dawood . Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye qol : '' aapney rakatein padhein aur wo pehli do se qadrey mukhtasar thin.'' chaar martaba zikr kya hai, aur sahih Muslim mein aur afrad Muslim mein kitab al-Humaidi aur muattaa malik, sunan abi Dawud aur Jaameul-usool mein isi tarah mazkur hai."
1198,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Umr-raseeda aur bojhal ho gaey to aap ziyada tar beth kar Namaz padha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
1199,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main un eik jaisi suraton ko janta hun jinhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mila kar padha kartey they. un mein se aakhiri do suraten Ha-Mim, Dukhan aur Naba hain. muttafaq aleh."
1200,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tahajjud padhtey huey dekha, aapney teen baar Allahu-akbar kaha aur phir dua padhi , phir aapney rukoo kya to aap ka rukoo qiyam ki tarah ( taweel ( tha, aap apney rukoo mein ye dua kya kartey they : '' paak hai mera rab azmat wala .'' phir aapney rukoo se apna sar uthaya to aap ka qiyam rukoo ki tarah tha, aap wahan ye dua kartey they : ''merey rab ke liye her qism ki hamd hai.'' phir aapney sajda kya, aap ke sujood bhi aap ke qiyam ke barabar they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney sujood mein ye dua kya kartey they, '' paak hai mera rab bahut buland .'' phir aapney sujood se sar uthaya , aap apney sajdon ke darmiyan apney sujood ke barabar hi bethtey they, aur ye dua kya kartey they : ''merey rab ! mujhey bakhsh dey .'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaar rakatein padhein aur aapney un mein Sura Baqra, Aale-Imran, Nisa, al-Maaida ya al-Anaam tilawat farmaeyn. Shoba ko al-Maaida ya al-Anaam mein shak hua hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja w Nasai ."
1201,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs das aayaat ka ehtimam karta hai wo Ghafeleen mein nahin likha jata, jo so aayaat (ki tilawat w hifz aur amal) ka ehtimam karta hai to wo itaat guzaaron mein likh diya jata hai aur jo shakhs hazar aayaat ka ehtimam karta hai to wo dheron ajr w sawab paney walon mein likh diya jata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1202,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tahajjud mein qirat kartey waqt kabhi apni aawaz buland kartey aur kabhi past kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1203,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is qadr buland aawaz se qirat kartey they ke aap ghar ke andar qirat kartey to sehan mein mojud shakhs aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat sun sakta tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1204,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik raat tashrif laye to dekha ke abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) past aawaz se Namaz padh rahey they. aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey to wo buland aawaz se Namaz padh rahey they. raawi bayan kartey hain, jab wo dono Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ikhattey huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ''main tumharey paas se guzra aur tum aahista aawaz se Namaz padh rahey they.'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine jis se sargoshi ki usko suna diya. (yani Allah paak ko) aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Alaihissalam) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''main tumharey paas se guzra tha aur tum buland aawaz se Namaz padh rahey they.'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main soey logon ko jaga raha tha aur shetan ko bhaga raha tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' abu-Bakar ! tum apni aawaz kuch buland karo, aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : tum apni aawaz kuch past rakho .'' Abu-Dawud, aur Imam Tirmizi ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
1205,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik hi aayat tilawat kartey huey kar di. aur wo aayat ye thi : ''agar to unhen azab dey to wo terey bandey hain, aur agar to unhen bakhsh dey to to ghalib hikmat wala hai.'' rawahu Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
1206,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi subh ki do rakatein padhey to wo apney daain pehlu par let jaey.''"
1207,"Hazrat Masruq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se daryaft kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke nazdik sab se ziyada pasandida amal kon sa tha? unhoney farmaya : jis ko hamesha kiya jaaey. maine puchha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ke kis waqt tahajjud padha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : jab aap murgh ki aawaz suntey tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tahajjud padha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
1208,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko raat tahajjud padhtey huey dekhna chahtey to ham aapko (is haalat mein) dekh letey they, aur agar ham aap ko soyaa hua dekhna chahtey to ham aap ko) soyaa hua ( dekh letey they. rawahu Nasai ."
1209,"Hazrat Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kisi sahabi ne bayan kya, ke main eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha, us doran maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz dekhney ke liye aap ko ghor se dekhta rahunga yahan tak ke main aapka amal dekh sakun , jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz Isha padh li to aap raat der tak soey rahey, phir bedaar huey to ufuq par nazar dal kar ye aayat karima tilawat farmaai : ''hamarey parwardigar ! to ne ye nahaq paida nahin farmaya .'' yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) yahan tak pahunchey : '' be-shak to wada khilafi nahin karta.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney bistar ki taraf haath badhaya aur wahan se miswak nikali, phir kisi bartan se piyaley mein pani dala aur miswak ki, phir Namaz padhi yahan tak ke maine kaha : aap jitni der soey they is qadr Namaz padhi phir aap let gaey yahan tak ke maine (dil mein) kaha : aapney jis qadr Namaz padhi usi qadr so gaey, phir aap bedaar huey to pehli martaba ki tarah amal dohraya, aur aapney wohi aayaat tilawat kin , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fajr se pehley teen martaba aisey kya. rawahu Nasai ."
1210,"Hazrat Yala bin Mumallak se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat aur Namaz ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney farmaya : tum unki Namaz ke mutalliq poochh kar kya karogey ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padha kartey they, phir aapney jitni der Namaz padhi hoti , itni der so jatey they, phir jis qadr soey usi qadr Namaz padhtey , phir jitni der Namaz padhi hoti usi qadr so jatey they yahan tak ke subh ho jati , phir unhoney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat ke mutalliq bataya to unhoney farmaya ke aap ki qirat ka eik eik harf wazeh hota tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Nasai ."
1211,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tahajjud padhtey to ( Allahu-akbar kehney ke baad) ye dua padhtey : aey Allah ! her qism ki hamd terey hi liye hai, zamin w aasman aur jo kuch un mein hai unhen tu hi qaaim rakhney wala hai, her qism ki tareef terey hi liye hai, zamin w aasman aur jo kuch un mein hai uska tu hi Noor hai, her qism ki tareef terey liye hai zamin w aasman aur jo kuch is mein hai uska tu hi Malik hai, her qism ki tareef terey hi liye hai to haq hai, tera wada haq hai, teri mulaqat haq hai, teri baat haq hai, jannat haq hai, jahannam haq hai, tamam Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) haq hain, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haq hain, aur qiyamat haq hai, aey Allah ! main terey samney jhuk gaya, tujh par eman laya, tujh par tawakkul kya, teri taraf ruju kya, maine teri hi tofiq se jhagda kya, maine tujhey hi apna haakim tasawwur kya, pas to merey agley pichley , zahir w poshida aur jinhen to mujh se ziyada janta hai wo sarey gunah maaf farma dey , tu hi taraqqi aur tanazzuli deney wala hai, sirf tu hi mabud hai aur terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin .'' muttafaq aleh."
1212,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat tahajjud ke liye khadey hotey to aap apni Namaz ki shuruat is dua se kartey they : ''aey Allah ! Jibraeel, mekael aur Israafeel ke rab ! zamin w aasman ko adam se wajood mein laney waley hazir w ghayeb ke janney waley, tu hi apney bandon ka un baton mein faisla farmaeyga jin mein wo ikhtilaf kartey hain, un ikhtilafi baton main apni tofiq se tu hi meri rahnumai farma, be-shak tu hi jisey chahta hai sidhi raah ki taraf raahnumai farmata hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1213,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs raat ko uth kar ye dua padhey : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ke liye badshahat hai, aur her qism ki hamd usi ke liye hai aur wo her chiz par qadir hai, Allah paak hai, hamdulillah hi ke liye hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, Allah bahut bada hai, gunah se bachna aur neki karna mehaz Allah ki tofiq se mumkin hai, phir wo ye kahey : merey rab mujhey bakhsh dey .'' ya farmaya : '' phir usney dua ki to uski dua qubul ki jati hai, agar wo wuzu karey aur Namaz padhey to uski Namaz qubul ki jati hai.'' Bukhari."
1214,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko bedaar hotey to aap ye dua padhtey : (لا الہ الا انت ، ، ، ، ، انک انت الوھاب) ''terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, to paak hai, aey Allah! apni hamd ke sath, main apney gunahon ki tujh se maghfirat talab karta hun, aur teri rehmat ka tujh se sawal karta hun, aey Allah! merey ilm mein izafa farma, be-shak tu hi ata farmanewala hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1215,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman Allah ka zikr kartey huey ba wuzu so jaey aur phir wo raat ke kisi waqt bedaar ho kar Allah se kisi khair w bhalai ka sawal karey to Allah wohi khair usey ata farma deta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood."
1216,"Hazrat Shuraiq al-Hozni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas hazir ho kar un se daryaft kya, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko bedaar hotey to aap kis ( zikr ( se aaghaz farmatey they? unhoney farmaya : tum ne aisi chiz ke barey mein mujh se sawal kya hai jiskey mutalliq tum se pehley kisi ne mujh se daryaft nahin kya, jab aap raat ko bedaar hotey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) das martaba ( Allahu-akbar), das martaba (''Alhamdulillah'') , das martaba ( '' Subhanallahi w bihamdihi) '' , das martaba (''subhanal malikul Quddus) das martaba (''astaghfirullah'') aur das martaba (''la Ilaa-h illallah'') padhtey , phir das martaba dua farmatey : ''aey Allah main duniya mein roze-qiyamat ki sakhtiyon aur takleefon se teri panah chahta hun.'' phir aap Namaz ( tahajjud ( shuru farmatey .) rawahu Abu-Dawood ( ."
1217,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ke liye uthtey to Allahu-akbar keh kar ye dua padhtey : '' paak hai to aey Allah ! apni hamd ke sath , ba barkat hai naam tera , buland hai shaan teri aur terey siwa koi mabude-bar-haq nahin, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''Allah bahut hi bada hai.'' phir farmatey : ''main Allah samee w aleem ki panah ka talabgaar hun shetan mardud sey, uskey waswasey, uskey kibr aur uskey jadu se.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai aur Abu-Dawood ne ( غیرک (ke baad ye izafa naqal kya hai, ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) teen martaba farmatey : (la ilaa-h illallah) , aur hadees ke aakhir mein hai : phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qirat kartey."
1218,"Hazrat Rabeea bin Kab Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hujrey ke qarib raat basar kya karta tha, jab aap raat tahajjud ke liye uthtey to main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko der tak ye padhtey huey sunta .'' paak hai tamam jahano ka rab .'' aur : '' paak hai Allah apni hamd ke sath .'' Nasai . Tirmizi mein bhi isi tarah hai. aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Nasai w Tirmizi."
1219,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi so jata hai to shetan uski guddi par teen girhein laga deta hai, wo her gireh par ye fusoon phunk deta hai abhi to bahut raat hai, so jaao, agar to wo bedaar ho kar Allah ka zikr karta hai to eik gireh khul jati hai, phir agar wuzu kar leta hai to dusri gireh khul jati hai aur agar Namaz bhi padh ley to teesri gireh bhi khul jati hai, aur wo subh ko hashshaash bashshaash hota hai, jabkey dusri surat mein wo ghamgin w pareshan aur susti ka shikar hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1220,"Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is qadr qiyam farmatey ke aap ke paaon sooj jatey , aap se arz kya gaya, aap ye ( taweel qiyam ( kyon kartey hain? jabkey aap ki agli pichli sab laghzishein maaf kar di gaee hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to phir kya main shukr guzar banda na banun.'' muttafaq aleh."
1221,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik aadmi ka tazkira kartey huey bataya gaya ke wo shakhs subh honey tak soya rehta hai aur Namaz bhi nahin padhta, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shetan aisey aadmi ke kaan ya farmaya uskey kanon mein peshab kar deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1222,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik raat ghabraey huey bedaar huey to farmaya : ''Subhanallah! aaj raat kis qadr khazaney nazil kiye gaey aur kis qadr fitney ( azab ( nazil kiye gaey, un hujrey waaliyon ko kon jagaaeyga?'' yani aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni pak biviyon ke barey mein farma rahey they : '' taake wo Namaz tahajjud padhein, kitni hi aurten hain jo duniya main to libas pehney huey hain lekin wo aakhirat mein barahna hongi.'' Bukhari."
1223,"Hazrat abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her raat jab aakhiri tihai raat baqi reh jati hai to hamara rab tabarak w taala aasmane-duniya par nuzool farmata hai, aur poochhtey hai : koi hai jo mujh se dua karey, main uski dua qubul karun, koi hai jo mujh se maangey, main usey ata karun aur koi hai jo mujh se maghfirat talab karey to main usey bakhsh dun.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''phir wo apney dono haath phela kar farmata hai : koi hai jo ata karney waley sakhi aur insaf karney waley ko qarz ata karey (ye silsila jari rehta hai) yahan tak ke Fajr tulu ho jati hai.''"
1224,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak raat main eik aisi ghadi hai ke us waqt koi musalman shakhs duniya w aakhirat ki jo bhi chiz Allah se maangta hai to wo usey wohi chiz ata farma deta hai, aur ye her raat hota hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1225,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Dawud (Alaihissalam) ki Namaz aur Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza Allah ko intehai mehbub hai, aap aadhi raat sotey aur tihai raat qiyam kartey they phir raat ka chata hissey sotey they aur eik din roza rakhtey aur eik din iftaar kartey (yani chhodtey ( they.'' muttafaq aleh."
1226,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ka ibtidai (shuruati) hissey sotey aur aakhiri hissey ( tahajjud padhtey huey ( jaagtey they, phir agar aapney shohar-bivi wala talluq qaaim karna hota to qaaim kartey, phir so jatey, agar aap pehli Azan ke waqt junbi hotey to aap jaldi se ghusl farmatey aur agar junbi na hotey to Namaz ke liye wuzu kartey, phir do rakatein padhtey. muttafaq aleh."
1227,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Namaz tahajjud padha karo, kyonkey wo tum se pehley nekon ki rawish hai, tumharey rab ka qurb hasil kerney, gunahon ki maafi aur gunahon se baaz rehney ka zaria hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
1228,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen qism ke logon par Allah khush hota hai : wo aadmi jo Namaz tahajjud padhta hai, wo log jo Namaz ke liye saf-bandi kartey hain, aur wo log jo dushman ke khilaf ladney ke liye saf bandi kartey hain.''"
1229,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' raat ke aakhiri hissey mein rab taala bandey ke intehai qarib hota hai, agar tum us waqt Allah ko yad karney walon mein shamil ho sako to ho jaao .'' aur Imam Tirmizi maine farmaya : ye hadees sanad ke lihaz se Hasan sahih gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1230,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah us bandey par rehem farmaai jo raat uth kar tahajjud padhey , apni ehliya ko jagaaey aur wo Namaz padhey , lekin agar wo inkar karey to uskey chehrey par pani chhidkey. Allah us aurat par rehem farmaai jo raat ko uth kar tahajjud padhey , apney khawind ko uthaey aur wo Namaz padhey , lekin agar wo inkar karey to wo uskey chehrey par pani ke chheentey maarey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
1231,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey, arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)! kon si dua ziyada qubul hoti hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' raat ke aakhiri hissey mein aur farz namazon ke baad ki gaee dua .''"
1232,"Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat mein kuch aisey kamrey hain (jo is qadr shaffaaf hain) ke unka zahir unke baatin se aur unka baatin unke zahir se nazar aata hoga, Allah ne unhen aisey logon ke liye tayyar kya hai jo naram guftgu kartey hain, khana khilatey hain, kasrat se ( nafl ( rozey rakhtey hain aur Namaz tahajjud padhtey hain jabkey log so rahey hotey hain.'' ( Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
1233,"aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah riwayat kya hai, aur unki riwayat mein hai : '' jisney achi guftgu ki .''"
1234,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' Abdullah ! falan shakhs ki tarah na ho jana , wo tahajjud padha karta tha lekin ab usney tahajjud padhna chhod di hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1235,"Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke liye raat ki eik ghadi thi jis mein wo apney ehle khana ko jagaatey huey farmatey they : aale-Dawud! khadey ho jaao aur Namaz padho, kyonkey us ghadi mein Allah azz-w-jall jadugar aur mehsul wasul karney waley ki dua ke siwa her dua qubul farmata hai.''"
1236,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' farz Namaz ke baad raat ke aakhiri hissey mein padhi gaee Namaz sab se behtar hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
1237,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya : falan shakhs raat ko tahajjud padhta hai aur jab subh hoti hai chori karta hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak wo an-qareeb tumhari batai hui baat ( Namaz ( usey rok degi.'' ( rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
1238,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi raat ke waqt apni ehliya ko jagata hai to wo dono Namaz padhtey hain ya wo dono ikhattey do rakatein padhtey hain to wo dono zaakreen aur zaakiraat mein likh diye jatey hain.''"
1239,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haameleen Quran aur tahajjud guzar log meri ummat ke shurfa hain.'' ."
1240,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unke walid umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) jis qadr Allah chahta Namaz tahajjud padhtey rehtey yahan tak ke jab raat ka aakhiri hissa hota to aap apney ehle khana ko Namaz ke liye uthatey to unhen kehtey : Namaz ( padho ya Namaz ka waqt ho gaya hai) . phir aap ye aayat tilawat farmatey : '' apney ghar walon ko Namaz ka hukm den , aur is par qaaim rahen , ham aap se rozi ke Talib nahin, balke ham aap ko rizq detey hain, aur aaqibat to perhez gaaron hi ke liye hai.'' rawahu Malik."
1241,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi mahiney is qadr iftaar kartey ke ham khayal kartey ke aap is maah roza nahin rakhengey . aur kabhi is qadr rozey rakhtey yahan tak ke ham khayal kartey ke aap us maah bilkul iftaar (naagha) hi nahin karengey, aisey hi agar aap ko Namaz tahajjud padhtey huey dekhna chaho to aap ko Namaz padhtey huey dekh saktey ho aur agar tum aap ko soya hua dekhna chaho to soya hua dekh saktey ho.''"
1242,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ko wo amal sab se ziyada mehbub hai jo hamesha kiya jaaey chahey wo thoda hi ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
1243,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aisey aamaal kya karo jinki tum taqat rakhtey ho, kyonkey Allah nahin uktaata lekin tum ukta jaaogey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1244,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs itni muddat hi Namaz padhey jo raghbat aur khushi ke sath padhi jaey aur jab baar malum ho to ( chhod kar) beth jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1245,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko Namaz padhtey huey ungh aaye to wo so jaey yahan tak ke neend puri ho jaey, kyonkey jab tum mein se koi Namaz padhtey huey ungh raha ho to usey pata nahin hota ke wo maghfirat talab kar raha hai ya apney liye baddua kar raha hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1246,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Deen aasan hai, jo shakhs Deen par sakhti kerega to wo is par ghalib aa jaeyga, tum beech ka rasta ikhtiyar karo, qarib raho aur khushkhabri qubul karo . neez din ke pehley pahar , uskey aakhiri pehar aur raat ke kuch waqt ki ibadat ke zariey madad talab karo.'' Bukhari ."
1247,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs raat ko apna wazeefa ya uska kuch hissey na kar sakey to phir agar wo namaze-Fajr aur namaze-Zohar ke darmiyan wohi wazifa kar ley to uskey liye utna hi sawab likh diya jata hai goya usney usey raat ke waqt kya hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1248,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khadey ho kar Namaz padho, agar istataat na ho to phir beth kar aur agar uski bhi istataat na ho to phir pehlu ke bal (Namaz padho).'' Bukhari ."
1249,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney beth kar Namaz padhney waley shakhs ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo khada ho kar Namaz padhta to wo behtar hai, aur jo shakhs beth kar Namaz padhey to uskey liye khadey ho kar Namaz padhney waley se nisf ajr hai, aur jo shakhs let kar Namaz padhey to uskey liye beth kar Namaz padhney waley se nisf ajr hai.'' Bukhari ."
1250,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs ba wuzu bistar par letey aur Allah ka zikr kartey huey so jaey to phir wo raat ko jab bhi karwat badaltey huey Allah se duniya w aakhirat ki khair talab karey to Allah usey wohi ata farma deta hai.'' Imam nauwi (Raziallahu anhu) ne ibn suni ki riwayat sey, , kitab azkaar ''main riwayat kya hai."
1251,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hamara rab do aadmiyon par khush hota hai, eik wo shakhs jo apney naram w garm bistar aur apney chaheeton aur ehle w ayaal mein se uth kar Namaz padhta hai. Allah farishton se farmata hai : merey us bandey ko dekho ke wo merey yahan jo ajr w sawab hai uski raghbat aur merey azab ke khof ki wajeh se apney naram w garm bistar aur apney chaheeton aur ehle w ayaal se alag ho kar Namaz ke liye utha hai, aur eik wo aadmi jo Allah ki raah mein jihad karta hai to wo apney sathiyon samet maidane-jang se peechey hat jata hai, lekin phir ye jaan kar ke peechey hatney par usey kya gunah milega aur pesh qadmi mein usey kitna sawab milega , to wo palat kar aata hai yahan tak ke usey Shahid kar diya jata hai to Allah farishton se farmata hai : merey is bandey ko dekho ke wo mujh se milney waley ajr w sawab ki raghbat aur merey azab ke khof ki wajeh se palat kar aaya yahan tak ke usey Shahid kar diya gaya.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah) ."
1252,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mujhey kisi ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi ka beth kar Namaz padhna, aadhi Namaz ki tarah hai.'' wo bayan kartey hain, main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine aap ko beth kar Namaz padhtey huey paya to maine apna haath aap ke sar par rakh diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Abdullah bin Amr ! tumhen kya hua ?'' maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataya gaya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' aadmi ka beth kar Namaz padhna , nisf Namaz ki tarah hai.'' jabke aap beth kar Namaz padh rahey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' theek hai, lekin main tum mein se kisi ki tarah nahin hun.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1253,"Hazrat Salim bin abi Ja'ad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Khuza'aa qabiley ke eik aadmi ne kaha : kaash! mein Namaz padh kar rahat hasil karta , goya unhon (yani haazirine-majlis ( ne uski is baat ko aibdar jana, (is par) unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' Bilal! Namaz ke liye iqaamat kaho aur uskey zariey hamen rahat pahunchao.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1254,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : raat ki Namaz do do rakaat hai, jab tum mein se kisi ko subh ho janey ka andesha ho to wo eik rakat padh ley to wo uski Namaz ko witr ( taaq ( bana degi.'' muttafaq aleh."
1255,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' witr ( ki Namaz (raat ke aakhiri hissey ki eik rakat hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1256,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) 13 rakaat Namaz tahajjud padha kartey they, un mein se paanch witr padhtey aur tashahud ke liye sirf aakhiri rakaat mein bethtey they. muttafaq aleh."
1257,"Hazrat Saad bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya to maine arz kya, ummul-momenin ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke akhlaq ke mutalliq mujhey bataeyn , unhoney farmaya : kya tum Quran nahin padhtey ? maine arz kya : kyon nahin, zarur padhta hun. unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka akhlaq Quran hi tha, maine arz kya, ummul-momenin ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke witr ke mutalliq mujhey bataeyn , unhoney farmaya : ham aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye aap ki miswak aur wuzu ke pani ka intizam kartey , phir jab Allah chahta to aap ko raat ke waqt jaga deta , aap miswak kartey aur wuzu kartey aur 9 rakatein padhtey aur aap sirf aathwin rakaat mein) tashahud ( bethtey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ka zikr kartey, uski hamd bayan kartey aur us se dua kartey, phir aap salam pherey baghair khadey ho jatey aur naween rakaat padhtey , phir beth jatey , Allah ka zikr kartey , uski hamd bayan kartey aur us se dua kartey phir salam phertey to hamen sunatey, phir salam pherney ke baad beth kar do rakatein padhtey , beta! ye 11 rakatein huin, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) boodhey ho gaey aur jism bhari ho gaya to aapney 7 rakatein witr padhey, aur do rakatein wesey hi ( beth kar) padhein jaisey ( boodhey honey sey) pehley padhtey they, pas beta ! ye 9 ho gaeen, aur jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padhtey to usey hamesha ikhtiyar karna aap ko bahut pasand tha, aur jab kabhi neend ke ghalbey ya kisi takleef ki wajeh se Namaz tahajjud na padhtey to phir aap din ke waqt baara rakatein padhtey they, aur main nahin jaanti ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik raat mein pura Quran padha ho, ya aapney puri raat tahajjud padhi ho ya aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ramazan ke ilawa pura mahina rozey rakhey hun. rawahu Muslim."
1258,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''witr ko apni aakhiri Namaz banaao.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1259,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''subh ho janey se pehley witr padhney mein jaldi karo.'' rawahu Muslim."
1260,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko andesha ho ke wo raat ke aakhiri hissey mein nahin uth sakega to wo raat ke awwal hissey mein witr padh ley , aur jisey raat ke aakhiri hissey mein jaagney ki ummid ho to wo raat ke aakhiri hissey mein witr padhey , kyonkey raat ke aakhiri hissey mein padhi janey wali Namaz ke waqt farishtey hazir hotey hain, aur ye afzal hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1261,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne raat ke tamam oqaat mein witr padhey hain, raat ke awwal hissey mein , uskey beech mein , uskey aakhiri hissey mein aur aakhiri daur mein aapki Namaze-witr sehri (aakhir shab) ke waqt hoti thi. muttafaq aleh."
1262,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, merey khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey teen kamon ka hukm farmaya, her maah teen din ke rozey rakhney, chaasht ki do rakatein padhney aur soney se pehley witr padhney ka hukm farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
1263,"Hazrat Ghuzaif bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se arz kya, mujhey bataeyn , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusle-janabat raat ke awwal hissey mein kartey they ya raat ke aakhiri hissey mein ? unhoney farmaya : kabhi raat ke pehley hissey mein ghusl kya aur kabhi raat ke pichley hissey mein , maine kaha : Allahu-akbar , her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney Deen mein wusat rakhi , maine puchha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ke awwal hissey mein witr padha kartey they ya raat ke aakhiri hissey mein ? unhoney farmaya : aapney kabhi raat ke awwal hissey mein witr padhey aur kabhi raat ke aakhiri hissey mein , maine kaha : Allahu-akbar , her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney Deen mein wusat rakhi , maine puchha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( Namaz tahajjud mein) buland aawaz se qirat kartey they ya past aawaz se ? unhoney farmaya , kabhi buland aawaz se aur kabhi past aawaz sey, maine kaha : Allahu-akbar , her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney Deen mein wusat rakhi .'' Abu-Dawud, aur ibne-Maja ne aakhiri baat riwayat ki hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja w Nasai ."
1264,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Qais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se daryaft kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kitni rakatein witr padha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : chaar aur teen ( saat ( , chhe aur teen ( no ( , aath aur teen ( giyara (aur das aur teen ( terah) rakaat witr padha kartey they, aap saat se kam aur tera se ziyada rakatein nahin padha kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1265,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' witr her musalman par wajib hai, jisey pasand ho ke wo paanch witr padhey to wo paanch padhey , jo teen padhna pasand karey to wo teen padhey aur jisey eik witr padhna pasand ho to wo eik padhey .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
1266,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah witr ( apni zaat w sifaat mein yakta ( hai, wo witr ko pasand farmata hai, pas Quran walo witr padha karo.'' zaeef ."
1267,"Hazrat khaarija bin Huzafa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye to unhoney farmaya : '' be-shak Allah ne tumhen eik mazeed Namaz ata farmaai hai aur wo tumharey liye surkh oonton se behtar hai, aur wo Namaz witr hai jisey Allah ne Namaz Isha aur tulu Fajr ke beech padhna muqarrar kya hai.''"
1268,"Hazrat Zaid bin Aslam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs witr padhna bhool jaey to wo subh honey ke baad witr padhey .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
1269,"Hazrat Abdul-Azeez bin Juraij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se daryaft kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witr mein kon si suraten padha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : aap pehli rakaat mein, Sura Aala, dusri mein Kafirun aur teesri mein Ikhlas aur muawwizatain padha kartey they."
1270,Hazrat Imam Nasai (Raziallahu anhu) ne is hadees ko Abdur-Rehman bin Abza se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Nasai .
1271,Hazrat Imam Ahmed (Raziallahu anhu) ne is hadees ko Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya. rawahu Ahmed .
1272,"Hazrat Imam Darmi ne ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai, Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne '' muawwizatain '' ka zikr nahin kya. rawahu Darmi ."
1273,"Hazrat Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey kuch kalmaat sikhaey jinko mein qunoot witr mein padhta hun ''aey Allah! mujhey hidayat de-kar un logon ki catagory mein shamil farma jinhen to ne hidayat se nawaza, aur mujhey bhi (un logon mein) aafiyat ata farma jinko to ne aafiyat ata ki jin logon ko tu ney apna dost banaya hai un mein mujhey bhi shamil karkey apna dost bana ley, jo kuch tu ney mujhey ata farmaya hai is mein merey liye barkat dal dey, jis shar ka to ne faisla farmaya hai us se mujhey bacha ley, be-shak tu hi hamara faisla sadir farmata hai terey khilaf faisla sadir nahin kya ja sakta, aur jiska to wali w sar parast bana wo kabhi ruswa nahin ho sakta, hamarey rab! to bada hi barkat wala aur buland w baala hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi."
1274,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witr padh kar salam phertey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : (subhanal-malikul-Quddus)'' paak hai badshah nihayat paak.'' Abu-Dawud, Nasai, aur unhoney ye izafa kya hai : teen martaba lambi aawaz se farmatey. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
1275,aur Abdur-Rehman bin Abza an ابیہ ki sanad se Nasai ki riwayat mein hai : jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) salam phertey to teen martaba (subhanal-malikul-Quddus) farmatey aur teesri martaba apni aawaz buland farmatey. rawahu Nasai .
1276,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witr ke aakhir par ye dua kya kartey they : ''aey Allah! main teri raza ke zariey teri narazi sey, terey darguzar ke zariey teri saza se panah chahta hun, main tujh se teri panah chahta hun, jaisey to ne apni zaat ki sana farmaai hai wesay mein koshish ke bawajud teri sanaa bayan nahin kar sakta. '' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
1277,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya kya ameerul-momeneen Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein aap ke paas koi jawab ya fatwa hai ke wo sirf eik witr padhtey hain? unhoney farmaya : wo durust hain kyonkey wo eik faqeeh shakhs hain. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ibn Muleka (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Muawiya ne Namaz Isha ke baad eik rakat witr padhi , aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam aap ke paas they, unhoney ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aa kar unhen bataya to unhoney farmaya : unhen chhod do kyonkey unhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat ikhtiyar karney ka sharf hasil hai. Bukhari ."
1278,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' witr haq ( wajib ( hai, jo shakhs witr na padhey wo ham mein se nahin, witr haq hai, pas jo shakhs witr na padhey wo ham mein se nahin, witr haq hai pas jo shakhs witr na padhey wo ham mein se nahin .''"
1279,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs neend ya bhool ki wajeh se witr na padhey to jab usey yad aaye ya jab wo bedaar ho to witr padh ley.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
1280,"Hazrat Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko riwayat pahunchi ke kisi shakhs ne Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se witr ke barey mein daryaft kya, kya wo wajib hai? to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne witr padhey aur musalmanon ne bhi witr padhey , wo aadmi bar-bar mujh se poochhtey raha aur Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) yehi jawab detey rahey : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne witr padhey aur musalmanon ne bhi witr padhey ."
1281,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) teen witr padha kartey they, aur un mein her rakaat mein teen Suraton ke hisab se mufassal Suraton mein se no suraten padha kartey they aur sab se aakhir par Sura ikhlas padha kartey they."
1282,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Makka mein tha, aasman abr aalud tha, unhoney subh ke dar ke peshe-nazar eik rakat witr padha, phir jab mausam saaf ho gaya to unhoney dekha ke abhi to raat baqi hai, to unhoney eik rakat padh kar Namaz ko juft bana liya , phir unhoney do rakatein ( tahajjud ( padhein , phir jab subh honey ka andesha hua to unhoney eik rakat witr padha . rawahu Malik."
1283,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth kar Namaz padhtey huey qirat kartey they, phir jab tees ya chaalis aayaat ke barabar tilawat baqi reh jati to aap khadey ho jatey aur khadey ho kar qirat kartey , phir rukoo kartey , phir sajda kartey aur phir dusri rakaat mein bhi isi tarah kartey they. rawahu Muslim ."
1284,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witr ke baad do rakatein padha kartey they. Tirmizi, aur ibne-Maja ne ye izafa naqal kya hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth kar hi do khafeef rakatein padha kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja."
1285,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik witr padha kartey they phir aap beth kar do rakatein padhtey, aur jab aap rukoo karna chahtey to phir khadey ho kar rukoo kartey they. rawahu ibne-Maja ."
1286,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye bedaari eik mushkil aur giraan kaam hai, jab tum mein se koi shakhs witr padh ley to wo do rakaat ada karey, agar wo raat ke waqt bedaar ho jaey ( to phir wo Namaz tahajjud padhey ( warna wo do rakatein uskey liye kafi hongi.'' rawahu Darmi ."
1287,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye do rakatein witron ke baad beth kar ada kartey they, aur aap un mein Sura Zilzal aur Sura Kafirun padha kartey they. rawahu Ahmed ."
1288,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ( dorane-namaz ( kisi ke liye baddua ya kisi ke liye dua ka irada farmatey to aap rukoo ke baad dua kartey, kabhi-kabhi jab aap (Sami-Allahu-liman hamida, ربنا لک الحمد ( farmatey to phir yun dua farmatey : ''aey Allah ! Waleed bin Waleed , Salma bin Hisham aur Ayash bin abi Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) ko) kuffar ki qaid sey) rihai ata farma, aey Allah ! qabila Muzar ki sakht giraft farma , un par Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke daur jaisa qehat musallat farma .'' aap buland aawaz se ye dua kya kartey they, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baaz namazon mein aisey bhi kaha kartey they : ''aey Allah! Arab ke falan falan qabiley par lanat farma.'' yahan tak ke Allah ne ye aayat nazil farma di : ''aap ko us mamley mein koi ikhtiyar hasil nahin .'' muttafaq aleh."
1289,"Hazrat Aasim ahwal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se Namaz mein qunoot ke mutalliq puchha ke wo rukoo se pehley tha ya uskey baad? unhoney farmaya : rukoo se pehley tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( farz Namaz) mein rukoo ke baad sirf eik maah qunoot kya, wo isliye ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sattar Sahaba kiram ko , jo ke qurra ke naam se mashhoor they, bheja to unhen Shahid kar diya gaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rukoo ke baad eik maah tak qunoot kya aur unke qaatilon ke liye badduaa kartey rahey. muttafaq aleh."
1290,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Zohar, asr, maghrib, Isha aur Fajr ki aakhiri rakaat mein rukoo ke baad eik maah tak musalsal duaaey qunoot farmaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bano Sulaim, Raal, Zakwan aur Usba qabaayel ke liye baddua kartey they aur jo aap ke peechey hotey they wo Aameen kehtey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1291,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik maah tak duaaey qunoot farmaey, phir usey tarak kar diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
1292,"Hazrat abu-Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain maine apney walid se kaha : abba jaan! aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) , umr (Raziallahu anhu) aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechey (Madina mein) aur taqriban paanch saal yahan koofa mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechey namazein padhein hain, kya wo qunoot kya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : beta! ye (musalsal) kartey rehna) bidat hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
1293,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon ko Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki imaamat par ikhatta kya, wo unhen bees rakaat Namaz (tarawih) padhaya kartey they, wo sirf nisf baqi mein qunoot kartey they aur jab aakhiri das din hotey to wo masjid mein na aatey balke ghar mein Namaz tarawih padhtey, to namazi kehtey : abi (Raziallahu anhu) bhag gaey ."
1294,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se qunoot ke mutalliq puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rukoo ke baad qunoot kya, aur eik riwayat mein hai : rukoo se pehley bhi aur baad bhi . rawahu ibne-Maja ."
1295,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne masjid mein chatai ka eik hujra bana liya, aur aapney chand raaten is mein Namaz padhi , yahan tak ke log ziyada tadaad mein jama ho gaey, phir eik raat unhoney aap ki aawaz mehsus na ki aur unhoney guman kya ke aap so chukey hain, kuch log khaansney lagey taake aap bahar tashrif ley ayen , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo kuch tum kartey rahey maine usey dekha yahan tak ke mujhey andesha hua ke usey tum par farz na kar diya jaey, aur agar tum par farz kar di jati to tum uska ehtimam na kar saktey , logo ! apney gharon mein Namaz padho , kyonkey farz Namaz ke ilawa aadmi ka ghar Namaz padhna afzal hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1296,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) koi qatae hukm diye baghair qiyam Ramazan ki targheeb diya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : ''jo shakhs eman aur sawab ki niyat se Ramazan ka qiyam karey to uskey pichhley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai to maamla isi tarah tha, phir abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat ke shuru mein maamla isi tarah tha. rawahu Muslim ."
1297,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi masjid mein Namaz ada karey to wo uska kuch hissey nafl waghera apney ghar mein bhi ada karey, kyonkey Allah uski Namaz ki wajeh se uskey ghar mein khair w barkat farmaeyga .'' rawahu Muslim ."
1298,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rozey rakhey , aapney us maah mein hamen tarawih na padhaai yahan tak ke saat din baqi reh gaey to aapney hamen tarawih padhaai yahan tak ke tihai raat beet gaee , jab chauthi raat hui to aapney hamen tarawih na padhaai, jab paanchwin raat hui to aapney hamen tarawih padhaai yahan tak ke aadhi raat beet gaee. maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! kaash! ke aap us raat ke qiyam ko badha detey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi Imam ke sath Namaz padhta hai yahan tak ke wo farigh hota hai to uskey liye puri raat ka sawab likh diya jata hai.'' jab chauthi raat aai to aapney hamen Namaz tarawih na padhaai yahan tak ke tihai raat baqi reh gaee. jab teesri raat aai to aapney apney ehle w ayaal aur logon ko ikhatta kya aur hamen Namaz tarawih padhaai, (aur itna lamba qiyam farmaya ( yahan tak ke hamen apni sehri faut ho janey ka andesha hua ( raawi kehtey hain ( maine kaha : '' falah '' se kya murad hai? farmaya : sehri, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mahiney ke baqi dinon mein hamen tarawih na padhaai. Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai , aur ibne-Maja ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya, albatta Imam Tirmizi ne'' aapney mahiney ke baqi dinon mein hamen tarawih nahin padhaai'' ka zikr nahin kya."
1299,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain maine eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (bistar par) na paya, aap achcha baqee (qabristaan) tashrif ley gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumhen andesha tha ke Allah aur uskey Rasool tum par zulm karengey .'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! maine samjha ke aap apni kisi zauja mohtarma ke paas tashrif ley gaey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala nisf Shoban ki raat aasman duniya par nazil hota hai aur wo (us raat ( kalab qabiley ki bakriyon ke baalon se bhi ziyada logon ki maghfirat farma deta hai.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, aur rizeen ne ye izafa naqal kya hai : ''Allah aisey logon ki maghfirat farmata hai jo jahannam ke mustahiq they.'' aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine Muhammad yani Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ko is hadees ko zaeef qarar detey huey suna ."
1300,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' farz Namaz ke ilawa aadmi ka apney ghar mein Namaz padhna meri is masjid mein Namaz padhney se afzal hai.'' muttafaq aleh, rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
1301,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abdul-Qaari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main eik raat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath masjid (nabwi) mein gaya to wahan log mutafarriq taur par eik-eik, do-do aur kahin chand afrad ki jamaat ki surat mein Namaze-Taraawih padh rahey they, ye surat dekh kar umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar main unhen eik Imam ki iqtida (pairvi) par ikhatta kar dun to wo behtar hoga, phir unhoney pukhta azm kiya aur unhen Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) par jama kar diya, raawi bayan kartey hain : main kisi aur raat phir unke sath aaya to log apney qaari ki imaamat mein Namaz padh rahey they,  (ye dekh kar) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye naee baat (ba-jamaat taraawih) bahut achchhi hai. aur wo Namaz jis se tum so jatey ho wo us Namaz ke padhney se afzal hai, (raawi kehta hai) us se umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki murad raat ka aakhiri hissey hai, jabkey log awwal raat mein Namaz padhtey they. Bukhari."
1302,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) aur Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmaya ke wo logon ko Ramazan mein giyara rakaat Namaz tarawih padhaein , qaari (eik rakat) mein do so aayat tilawat karta tha yahan tak ke ham lambey qiyam ki wajeh se lathiyon ka sahara liya kartey they, aur ham tulu Fajr se thoda sa pehley farigh hotey they. rawahu Malik."
1303,"Hazrat Aaraj (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ham ne Ramazan mein har shakhs ko kafiron par lanat kartey huey paya , aur qaari aath rakaaton mein Sura Baqra padhtey they, aur jab usey baara rakaaton mein padhtey to phir log usey kami samajhtey they. rawahu Malik."
1304,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Bakr bayan kartey hain, maine Ubai (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna : ham Ramazan mein Taraawih se us waqt farigh hua kartey they ke ham sehri ke faut ho janey aur Fajr ke tulu ho janey ke khof ke peshe-nazar khaadimon ko khaney ke mutalliq jaldi karney ka hukm detey they. rawahu Malik."
1305,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aap jaanti hain ke nisf Shoban ki raat kya waqey hota hai?'' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! is mein kya waqey hota hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us saal paida honey waley aur us saal faut honey waley her shakhs ka naam us raat likh diya jata hai, usi raat unke aamaal ooper chadhtey hain aur usi raat unka rizq nazil kya jata hai.'' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki rehmat ke baghair koi bhi shakhs jannat mein nahin jaeyga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen baar farmaya : ''Allah ki rehmat ke baghair koi bhi shakhs jannat mein nahin jaeyga.'' maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! aap bhi nahin? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney sar par haath rakh kar farmaya : ''main bhi nahin, jab tak Allah apni taraf se mujhey dhanp na ley.''"
1306,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala nisf Shoban ki raat apney bandon par khususi taur par mutawajjeh hota hai aur wo mushrik ya keena parwar ke siwa apni tamam makhluq ko bakhsh deta hai.''"
1307,"Hazrat Imam Ahmed ne Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai, unki riwayat mein hai,''keena parwar aur khud kushi karney waley ke siwa ( sabko bakhsh deta hai) .''"
1308,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya: ''jab nisf (aadhe) Shoban ki raat ho to tum us raat qiyam karo, aur us din ka roza rakho , kyonkey us raat aaftaab ke ghurub hotey hi Allah Taala aasmane-duniya par nuzool farma kar poochhtey hai : ''sun lo ! koi maghfirat ka talabgaar hai taake main usey bakhsh dun, sun lo ! koi rizq ka Talib hai taake main usey rizq ata farmaoon , sun lo ! koi aafiyat chahta hai taake main usey aafiyat ata farmaoon, sun lo ! in-in chizon ka koi Talib hai? ye silsila tulu Fajr tak jari rehta hai.''"
1309,"Hazrat Umme-Haani (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh Makka ke roz unke ghar tashrif laye to aapney ghusl kiya aur aath rakatein padhein, maine us se halki Namaz kabhi nahin dekhi albatta Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rukoo aur sujood mukammal farmatey they, aur unhoney eik dusri riwayat mein farmaya : aur wo Namaz chaasht thi. muttafaq aleh."
1310,"Hazrat Muaza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se daryaft kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaasht ki kitni rakatein padha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : chaar rakatein, aur jis qadr Allah chahta badha detey they. rawahu Muslim."
1311,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se har eik par uskey tamam jodon ka sadqa karna zaroori hai, har qism ki tasbih (Subhanallah kehna) sadqa hai, har qism ki hamd sadqa hai, har martaba (la-ilaah-illallah) kehna sadqa hai, neki ka hukm karna sadqa hai, burai se rokna sadqa hai, aur jo shakhs chaasht ki do rakatein padh leta hai to wo uskey liye kafi ho jati hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
1312,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kuchh logon ko Namaze-chaasht padhtey huey dekha to unhoney farmaya : unhen ilm hai ke is waqt ke ilawa Namaz (chaasht) padhna afzal hai, kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Namaze-Awwaabeen ka waqt wo hai jab oont ke bachchey ke paaon (shiddat haraarat se ret garm ho janey ki wajeh sey) garmi mehsus keren.'' rawahu Muslim."
1313,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah tabarak w taala se riwayat kiya ke usney farmaya : ''ibne-Adam ! din ke awwal waqt merey liye chaar rakatein padh , to main tujhey din ke aakhir waqt tak kafi ho jaaunga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
1314,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi ne usey riwayat kiya hai jabkey Imam Abu-Dawood aur Imam Darmi ne Naeem bin Hamaaz Ghatfaani se riwayat kiya hai aur Imam Ahmed ne un (teeno Sahaba kiraam) se riwayat kiya hai.
1315,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''insan mein teen-sau-saath jod hain, aur har jod ke badley sadqa karna is par lazim hai.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Nabi itni taqat kon rakhta hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''masjid se balgham ko saaf kar dena , raasta se kisi takleef ko door kar dena (sadqa hai) , isliye agar to na paey to chaasht ki do rakatein terey liye kafi hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1316,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs chaasht ki baara rakatein padhta hai to Allah uskey liye jannat mein soney ka eik mehal tayyar kar deta hai.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur ham usey sirf isi tareeq se jantey hain."
1317,"Hazrat Muaz bin Anas Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Namaze-Fajr padhney ke baad chaasht ki do rakatein padhta hai aur wo us doran khair ke siwa koi baat nahin karta , to uskey gunah , chahey (chaahe) samandar ki jhaag ke bhi barabar hon tab bhi wo maaf kar diye jatey hain.''"
1318,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs chaasht ki do rakaaton ki pabandi karta hai to uskey gunah chahey (chaahe) samandar ki jhaag ke barabar hon tab bhi wo maaf kar diye jatey hain.''"
1319,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke wo chaasht ki aath rakatein padha karti thin, phir wo farmati hain, agar merey waliden bhi zinda kar diye jaeyn to main (unki khatir) us (Namaz chaasht) ko tarak nahin karungi."
1320,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz chaasht padha kartey they, yahan tak ke ham kehtey : ab Aap isey nahin chodengey , aur (kabhi) isey chhod detey to ham kehtey : ab Aap isey nahin padhengey."
1321,"Hazrat Muwarriq Ajli (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se daryaft kiya, aap Namaze-chaasht padhtey hain? unhoney farmaya : nahin, maine puchha : umr (Raziallahu anhu) (padhtey they)? unhoney farmaya : nahin, maine puchha : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) (padhtey they) unhoney farmaya : nahin, maine puchha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (padhtey they)? unhoney farmaya : mera khayal hai nahin padhtey they. Bukhari."
1322,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Fajr ke waqt Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''Bilal ! mujhey us amal ke barey mein bataao jo tum ne haalate-Islam mein kiya ho aur jis par tumhen sawab ki bahut ziyada ummid ho kyonkey maine jannat mein apney aagey terey jooton ki aawaz suni hai.'' unhoney arz kiya : mujhey apney jis amal par sawab ki bahut ziyada ummid hai (wo ye hai) ke main raat ya din mein jis waqt bhi wuzu karta hun to main us wuzu ke baad jis qadr muqaddar ho nafl Namaz padhta hun. muttafaq aleh."
1323,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maamlat ke barey mein hamein us ehtimam ke sath istikhaara sikhatey they jis tarah Aap hamein Quran ki sura sikhatey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''jab tum mein se koi kisi kaam ka irada karey to wo farz Namaz ke ilawa do rakatein Namaz padhey phir ye dua padhey : aey Allah ! be-shak main (is kaam mein) tujh se terey ilm ki madad se khair maangta hun aur (iskey husool ke liye) tujh se teri qudrat ke zariey qudrat maangta hun aur main tujh se tera fazale-azeem maangta hun, be-shak to (har chiz par) qadir hai aur main ( kisi chiz par) qadir nahin, to janta hai jabkey main kuch bhi nahin janta , aur to tamam poshida chizon ka janney wala hai, aey Allah ! agar to janta hai ke ye kaam merey liye merey Deen , meri zindagi aur merey anjam kaar.'' ya farmaya : ''meri duniya aur meri aakhirat ke liye behtar hai to usey merey liye muqaddar kar , aasan kar aur phir is mein merey liye barkat paida farma , aur agar terey ilm mein ye kaam merey liye merey Deen , meri zindagi aur merey anjam kaar.'' ya farmaya : ''meri duniya aur meri aakhirat ke lihaz se bura hai to usey mujh se aur mujhey is se pher dey aur merey liye khair aur bhalai muqaddar farma wo jahan kahin bhi ho, phir mujhey iskey sath razi kar dey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur wo apni hajat ka naam ley.'' Bukhari."
1324,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey hadees bayan ki, aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne sach farmaya , unhoney bayan kiya, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab koi shakhs kisi gunah ka irtikab (iraada) karta hai, phir wuzu karkey Namaz padh kar Allah se maghfirat talab karta hai to Allah usey maaf kar deta hai.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : (والذین اذا فعلوا فاستغفروا لذنوبھم) ''aur wo log jab koi bura kaam kar guzartey hain ya apni jaan par zulm kar bethtey hain, to Allah ko yad kartey hain, phir us se apney gunahon ki maghfirat talab kartey hain.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja , albatta ibne-Maja ne aayat zikr nahin ki."
1325,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko koi aham masla darpesh hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) fauran nafl Namaz ka ehtimam farmatey."
1326,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne subah ke waqt Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : ''kis amal ki wajeh tum mujh se pehley jannat mein chaley gaey mein jab bhi jannat mein gaya to maine tumharey jooton ki aawaz apney aagey suni.'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main jab bhi Azan kehta hun to do rakatein padhta hun, aur jab mera wuzu toot jata hai to main fauran wuzu karta hun aur main samajhta hun ke Allah ka shukr ada karney ke liye do rakatein padhna mujh par lazim hain (lihaza main do rakatein padhta hun) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhi do ki wajeh se (tum us maqam ko pahunchey ho).'' rawahu Tirmizi."
1327,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko Allah se koi hajat aur zarurat ho ya kisi insan se koi kaam ho to wo achchhi tarah wuzu karkey do rakatein padhey , phir Allah Taala ki sanaa bayan karey aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par durood padhey phir yun dua karey : ''Allah Haleem aur karim ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, arshe-azeem ka Rab paak hai, her qism ki hamd Allah ke liye hai jo tamam jahano ka Rab hai, main tujh se un aamaal aur asbab ki darkhast karta hun jo teri rehmat aur teri maghfirat ko wajib aur muakkad kar den, main har neki ko ghanimat janney aur har gunah se bachney ki tujh se darkhast karta hun, sab se ziyada rehem farmaney waley ! merey tamam gunah maaf farma dey , merey tamam gham door kar dey aur har zarurat jo teri raza ka baais baney usey pura farma dey.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja , aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1328,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''aey chacha jaan Abbas ! kya main aap ko kuchh ata na karun? kya main aap ko kuchh inayat na karun? kya main aap ko koi khabar na dun? kya main aap ko das khaslatein ata na karun ke jab aap un par amal karen to Allah aap ke agley pichhley, qadim aur naye, ghalti se kiye gaey ya amadan , chhotey, badey, poshida aur zahir tamam gunah maaf farma dey, wo ye ke aap chaar rakaat Namaz padhein , her rakaat mein Sura Fatiha aur koi dusri sura padhein , jab aap pehli rakaat mein qirat se farigh ho jaeyn aur abhi qiyam mein hon to aap pandarah martaba ''Subhanallahi wl-hamdulillahi wla Ilaah illallah walla hu akbar'' padhein , phir aap rukoo karen aur rukoo mein yehi tasbih das martaba padhein , phir rukoo se sar uthaeyn aur das martaba yehi kalimaat padhein , phir sajda karen aur sajda mein das martaba yehi kalimaat padhein , phir sajde se sar uthaeyn aur das martaba yehi kalimaat padhein, phir sajda karen aur das martaba yehi kalimaat padhein aur phir sajde se sar uthaeyn aur das martaba yehi kalimaat padhein , is tarah her rakaat mein pachhattar martaba kalimaat hongey, aap ye amal chaar rakaaton mein dohraaein , agar aap her roz isey padh saken to padhein , agar aisey na ho sakey to phir her Juma (yani hafte main eik baar) padhein, agar aisey na kar saken to phir saal main eik martaba padhein , agar aisey bhi na kar saken to phir apni zindagi main eik baar hi padh lein.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja aur al-Behaqi."
1329,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi ne Abu-Raafe se isi tarah riwayat kiya hai.
1330,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' bandey se roze-qiyamat uskey aamaal mein se sab se pehley Namaz ka hisab liya jaeyga, agar wo sahih aur durust hui to wo falah aur najat pa gaya aur agar wo sahih aur durust na hui to phir wo nakam aur na murad hoga, agar uskey faraaiz mein koi kami hui to Rab Tabarak w Taala farmaeyga : dekho , kya merey bandey ke kuchh nawaafil hain, to is tarah faraaiz ki kami ko un (nawaafil) se pura kar diya jaeyga, phir baqi aamaal ka hisab isi tarah hoga.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''phir Zakat ka hisab bhi isi tarah hoga aur phir baqi aamaal ka hisab bhi isi (mazkur misal ki) tarah hoga.''  'حسن واللفظ مرکب' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1331,Hazrat Imam Ahmed ne (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke as-haab mein sey) kisi eik se riwayat kiya hai.
1332,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''banda jab do rakatein padhta hai to Allah us taraf khususi tawajjoh farmata hai aur jab tak banda Namaz padhta rehta hai to neki (rehmat) us bandey ke sar par saya karti rehti hai, aur banda Allah ke kalam yani Quran ke zariey jis qadr Allah ka qurb hasil kar sakta hai wesa kisi aur chiz ke zariey hasil nahin kar sakta.''"
1333,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madina mein Zohar chaar rakaat (puri Namaz) ada ki aur zal-Hulaifa mein Asr do rakaat (qasr Namaz) ada ki. muttafaq aleh.
1334,"Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab Khuzaae (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein meena ٰmein do rakatein padhaeen, halanke us se pehley ham kabhi na to itni Kasir tadaad mein they aur na kabhi is qadr pur-amn they. muttafaq aleh."
1335,"Hazrat Ya'ala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Allah Taala ne to farmaya : '' (انتقصروا الذین کفروا) agar tumhen andesha ho ke kafir tumhen kisi musibat mein dal dengey to tum Namaz mein kuchh kami kar lo.'' ab to log pur-amn hain (kisi qism ka koi andesha nahin) , umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jaisey aap ko tajjub hua hai wesay mujhey bhi tajjub hua tha. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya tha : ''eik qism ka sadqa hai jo Allah ne tum par kiya hai, tum uski taraf se sadqa qubul karo.'' rawahu Muslim."
1336,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein Madina se Makka ke liye rawana huey to Aap hamarey Madina wapis pahunchney tak do-do rakatein (Namaze-qasr) padhatey rahey, un se puchha gaya ke tum ne Makka mein kuchh qiyam bhi kiya tha? unhoney farmaya : ham ne wahan das roz qiyam kiya. muttafaq aleh."
1337,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik safar kiya (fatah Makka ka safar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Unais din qiyam kiya aur Aap do-do rakatein padhatey rahey . ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ham Madina aur Makka ke darmiyani fasley par Unais din tak do-do rakatein padhtey hain, jab ham us se ziyada qiyam kartey hain to ham chaar rakatein (puri Namaz) padhtey hain. Bukhari."
1338,"Hazrat Hafs bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Makka ke raaste mein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha, aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Zohar do rakaat padhaai , phir apni qiyam gaah mein aa kar beth gaey, aapney kuchh logon ko qiyam kartey (Namaz padhtey) huey dekha to farmaya : ye log kya kar rahey hain? maine kaha : nafl padh rahey hain, unhoney farmaya : agar maine nafl padhney hotey to main apni Namaz puri padhta, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath raha hun wo safar mein do rakaaton se ziyada nahin padha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
1339,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar kartey to Zohar aur Asr ko aur maghrib aur Isha ko mila kar padhtey they. Bukhari."
1340,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dorane-safar apni sawari par jis taraf wo rukh karti , Namaz padha kartey they. aur Aap rukoo aur sujood ke liye sar ka ishara farmatey they. Aap faraaiz ke ilawa Namaze-tahajjud aur Namaze-witr apni sawari par ada kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
1341,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (dorane-safar) her tarah ki Namaz padhi. aapney qasr bhi padhi aur puri bhi. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
1342,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain main ghazawaat mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shareek raha . aur Fateh Makka ke moqe par bhi mein Aap ke sath mojud tha. aapney Makka mein atthaara roz qiyam farmaya , Aap do rakatein padh kar farmatey : ''ehle-Makka tum chaar rakatein padho, kyonkey ham to musafir hain.''"
1343,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain maine dorane safar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Zohar do rakaat padhein aur uskey baad do rakatein padhin. eik dusri riwayat mein hai : maine safar aur hazar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi hai. maine hazar mein aap ke sath Zohar chaar rakatein padhein aur uskey baad do rakatein padhin. aur maine dorane safar aap ke sath Zohar do rakaat padhi aur do rakatein uskey baad padhin. aur Asr do rakaat padhi aur uskey baad kuchh na padha. jabkey maghrib safar aur hazar dono haalaton mein teen rakaat padhin. safar ho ya hazar un mein kami nahin ki jati . aur ye din ke witr hain. aur uskey baad do rakatein padhin.
1344,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwae-tabuk (ke safar) mein jab Aap ke kooch karney se pehley Suraj dhal jata to Aap Zohar aur Asr ko jama kar letey aur agar Suraj dhalney se pehley kooch kartey to Zohar ko muakhkhar (der) kartey yahan tak ke Asr ke liye padaaw daltey. isi tarah maghrib mein kartey ke jab kooch karney se pehley Suraj ghurub ho jata to Aap maghrib aur Isha ikhatti padh letey aur agar ghuroobe-aaftaab se pehley kooch kar letey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maghrib ko muakhkhar farmatey yahan tak ke Namaz Isha ke liye padaaw daltey. phir unhen jama farma letey. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi ."
1345,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dorane-safar nafl padhney ka irada farmatey to aap apni sawari par qibla rukh ho kar takbir keh kar Namaz padhtey aur sawari jis rukh chahti chalti jati . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1346,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney kisi kaam ke liye mujhey bheja . jab main aaya to aap apni sawari par mashriq ki taraf Namaz padh rahey they. aur aap rukoo ki nisbat sujood ke liye ziyada jhuk kar ishara kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1347,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Mina mein do rakatein (yani Namaz qasr ( padhin. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni khilaafat ke ibtidaai (shuruati) salon mein do rakatein hi padhin. phir uskey baad Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne chaar rakatein padhin. jab ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Imam ke sath Namaz padhtey to aap chaar rakatein ( mukammal Namaz) padhtey aur jab akeley padhtey to phir do rakatein padhtey they. muttafaq aleh."
1348,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, shuru mein Namaz do rakatein farz ki gaee thi. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hijrat ki to do se chaar rakatein farz kar di gaee. aur Namaz safar ko pehli haalate-farziyat par barqarar rakha gaya. Zohri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko kya hua ke wo puri padhti hain? unhoney bataya ke unhoney bhi Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki tarah taaweel ki hai. muttafaq aleh."
1349,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Allah ne tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaban par hazar mein chaar rakatein, safar mein do rakatein aur haalate-khof main eik rakat farz ki. rawahu Muslim."
1350,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz safar do rakaat laagu kin aur wo do rakaat (sawab ke lihaz sey) puri hain, kam nahin jabkey dorane-safar witr padhna sunnat hai."
1351,"Hazrat Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain mujhey ye hadees pahunchi hai ke ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Makka aur Taaif , Makka aur Asfan aur Makka aur Jadda ke darmiyan masafat jitney fasley par qasr padha kartey they. aur Imam Malik ne farmaya : aur ye chaar burd masafat hai. rawahu Malik."
1352,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath atthaara martaba shareek safar raha , maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Suraj dhalney ke baad namaze-Zohar se pehley do rakatein chhodtey huey kabhi nahin dekha . Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1353,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) apney bete Ubaidullah ko dorane-safar nafl padhtey huey dekhtey to aap is par rok tok nahin kartey they."
1354,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( ham duniya mein) sab se aakhir par aaye hain lekin qiyamat ke roz sab se aagey hongey . taaham unhen ham se pehley kitab di gaee aur hamen unke baad di gaee . phir yehi yani Juma ka din un par farz kya gaya tha. magar unhoney is mein ikhtilaf kya, aur Allah ne hamen iski raahnumai farma di isi liye baqi log ham se peechey ho gaey. yahood kal (hafte ke roz) aur Esai us se agley roz ( itwaar ke roz ibadat kartey hain ( .'' aur Muslim ki eik riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ( ham duniya mein) sab se aakhir par hain lekin roze-qiyamat sab se pehley hongey . aur sab se pehley ham jannat mein jaeyngey .'' baqi riwayat unhoney aakhir tak hadees saabiq ki tarah bayan ki . muttafaq aleh."
1355,Hazrat sahih Muslim hi ki Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees mein hai. unhoney bayan kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hadees ke aakhir par farmaya : '' ham duniya walon mein sab se aakhir par aaye lekin roze-qiyamat muqaddam hongey aur sari makhluq se pehley hamarey mutalliq faisla kya jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim .
1356,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tamam dinon se behtareen din, Juma ka din hai, isi din Adam (Alaihissalam) paida kiye gaey usi roz jannat mein dakhil kiye gaey usi roz us se nikaley gaey aur qiyamat bhi Juma hi ke roz qaaim hogi .'' rawahu Muslim ."
1357,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Juma ke din eik aisi ghadi hai ke jab koi musalman banda us ghadi mein Allah se koi khair talab karta hai to Allah usey wohi chiz ata farma deta hai.'' Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne izafa naqal kya hai farmaya : '' wo mukhtasar ghadi hai.'' saheehain ki riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Juma main eik aisi ghadi hai ke jab musalman theek us ghadi mein Namaz ke doran ya Namaz ki jagah Namaz ke intizar mein beth kar Allah se koi khair talab karta hai to Allah usey wohi chiz ata kar deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1358,"Hazrat abu-Barda bin Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine apney walid ko bayan kartey huey suna, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko : '' Juma ki us ghadi ka waqt bayan kartey suna ke wo Imam ke khutba ke liye bethney se lekar Namaz se farigh honey tak hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1359,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main taur ki taraf gaya to main Kab ahbaar se mila , main uskey sath beth gaya. usney mujhey Torah ke barey mein bataya aur maine usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ahadis sunaain, maine usey jo kuch bataya wo wohi kuch tha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tamam dinon se behtar din , Juma ka din hai. is mein Adam (Alaihissalam) ki takhleeq hui, isi roz zamin par utarey gaey, isi roz unki tauba qubul ki gaee, isi roz faut huye, isi roze-qiyamat qaaim hogi, jin w ins ke siwa tamam janwer Juma ke din tulu Fajr se tulu aaftaab tak qiyamat qaaim honey ke khof se cheekhtey rehtey hain, us main eik ghadi hai ke jab musalman banda aen us ghadi mein dorane-namaz Allah se jo maangta hai to Allah usey wohi chiz ata kar deta hai.'' Kab ne kaha : purey saal main eik din aisa hota hai. maine kaha, nahin balke her Juma ke roz hota hai. Kab ne Torah padhi to usney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sach farmaya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) se mila to maine Kab ahbaar ke sath apni majlis ke barey mein aur maine Juma ke mutalliq jo usey bataya tha uskey mutalliq unhen bataya, ke Kab ne kaha : wo purey saal main eik din hota hai. Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya , Kab ne jhoot bola, maine unhen bataya ke Kab ne phir Torah padhi to usney kaha : balke wo her Juma ke roz hota hai. phir Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Kab ne sach kaha . phir Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya mujhey malum hai ke wo kon si ghadi hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya maine kaha, mujhey uskey mutalliq khabar deney mein bukhl na karen. Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya wo Juma ke din ki aakhiri ghadi hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya maine kaha wo Juma ke din ki aakhiri ghadi kaisey ho sakti hai. jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' koi musalman banda Namaz mein usey paata hai.'' to Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye nahin farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi jagah beth kar Namaz ka intizar karta hai to wo Namaz padhney tak (hukman) Namaz hi mein hota hai.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain maine kaha kyon nahin. unhoney farmaya, bas! ye wohi hai. malik, Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai, aur Imam Ahmed ne '' Kab ne sach kaha'' tak riwayat kya hai."
1360,Hazrat Anas Bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us ghadi ko talash karen jiskey barey mein ummid ki jati hai ke wo Juma ke roz baad namaze-Asr se ghurub aaftaab tak hoti hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi.
1361,"Hazrat Aus bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Juma ka din tumharey dinon mein se afzal din hai. us din Adam (Alaihissalam) ki takhleeq hui, usi mein unki rooh qabz ki gaee, pehli baar Soor phunka jana dusri baar Soor phunka jana hoga, us roz mujh par kasrat se durood padho, kyonkey tumhara durood mujh par pesh kya jata hai.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! hamara durood aap par kaisey pesh kya jata hai, jabkey aap to (mitti mein) boseedah ho chukey hongey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah ne Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) ke jismon ko zamin (yani mitti ( par haram kar diya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi w al-Behaqi."
1362,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' yoame-mauood se yoame-qiyamat, yoam mash-hood se yoam Arfa aur shaahid se Juma ka din murad hai. wo tamam dinon se afzal hai. is mein Allah se koi khair talab karta hai to Allah uski dua ko qubul farmata hai. aur wo ( banda momin ( jis chiz se panah talab karta hai to wo usey us se panah dey deta hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Imam Tirmizi ne kaha : ye hadees gharib hai. aur ye sirf Musa bin Ubeda ke wastey se maroof hai, jabkey wo zaeef hai."
1363,"Hazrat abu-Lubaba bin Abdul-Munz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Juma ke din Allah ke yahan sayedul-ayyaam aur baqi dinon se azeem tar hai. wo Allah ke yahan yomul-azha aur yomul-Fitr se bhi azeem tar hai. usko paanch khususiyaat hasil hain : Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko usi roz takhleeq farmaya , Allah ne usi roz Adam (Alaihissalam) ko zamin par utaara, Allah ne usi roz Adam (Alaihissalam) ko wafat di, us main eik aisi ghadi hai ke is mein banda jo bhi halal chiz talab karta hai. wo usey mil jati hai. aur usi roze-qiyamat qaaim hogi , muqarrab farishtey , aasman w zamin , hua , pahad aur samandar Juma ke din se khaaif rehtey hain.''"
1364,"Hazrat Imam Ahmed ne Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai ke eik Ansari shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya hamen Juma ke din ke mutalliq bataeyn ke is mein kya khabar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us mein paanch khususiyaat hain, '' , .'' aur baqi hadees aakhir tak ( isi tarah ( bayan ki ."
1365,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya gaya, Juma ke din ke naam ki wajehe-tasmiya (naam rakhney ki wjah) kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kyonkey us roz aap ke baap Adam ke khameer ko tayyar kya gaya, isi mein pehli aur dusri baar Soor phunka jana hai. isi mein hashr ka maidan sajega . aur iski aakhiri teen ghadiyon main eik aisi ghadi hai ke jo shakhs is mein dua karta hai to uski dua qubul ki jati hai.''"
1366,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : Juma ke roz mujh par kasrat se durood bheja karo. kyonkey wo mash'hood hai, is par farishtey hazir hotey hain. jab tum mein se koi shakhs mujh par durood padhta hai to uska durood mujh par pesh kya jata hai yahan tak ke wo us se farigh ho jaey.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, aur wafat ke baad? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) ke jismon ko khana zamin (mitti) par haram kar diya hai. Allah ke Nabi (Alaihissalam) zinda hotey hain aur unhen rizq diya jata hai.''"
1367,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman Juma ke din ya Juma ki raat faut ho jata hai to Allah usey qabr ki aazmaish se bacha leta hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. aur iski sanad muttasil nahin."
1368,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, ke unhoney ye aayat tilawat ki : '' aaj ke din maine tumharey liye tumhara Deen mukammal kar diya hai.'' to us waqt unke paas eik Yahudi tha, usney kaha : agar ye aayat ham par nazil hoti to ham us ( yome-nuzool ( ko eid bana letey. ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye to eidain ke roz nazil hui hai, Juma ke din aur Arfa ke din. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1369,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab maah rajab shuru hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua farmatey : ''aey Allah! hamarey liye rajab w Shoban mein barkat farma aur hamen Ramazan tak pahuncha.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''Juma ki raat, chamak daar raat hai aur Juma ka din taro-taza din hai.''"
1370,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member ki sidhiyon par farmatey huey suna : ''log Jumey chhodney se baaz aa jaeyn warna Allah unke dilon par mohar laga dega aur phir wo ghafilon mein se ho jaeyngey .'' rawahu Muslim ."
1371,"Hazrat Abu-Ja'ad Zamri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs adam tawajjoh ki bina par teen Jumey chhodey to Allah Taala uskey dil par mohar laga deta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi."
1372,Hazrat Imam Malik ne usey Safwan bin saleem (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai.
1373,Hazrat Imam Ahmed ne abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai.
1374,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs bila uzr Juma chhod dey to wo eik Dinar sadqa karey agar wo na paey to nisf deenar.''"
1375,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Azan suney is par Juma farz hai.''"
1376,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs raat apney ehle w ayaal ke paas wapis aa sakta ho is par Juma farz hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : is hadees ki asnaad zaeef hain."
1377,"Hazrat Tariq bin Shahab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her musalman par ba-jamaat Juma ada karna farz hai. siwaye chaar ke, ghulam, aurat, bachey, ya mareez ke.'' Abu-Dawood aur Sharahus-sunnah mein masaabeh ke alfaz se banu-Wayel ke eik shakhs ki sanad se marwi (bayan) hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1378,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Juma se peechey reh janey waley logon ke barey mein farmaya : ''maine irada kya ke main kisi aadmi ko hukm dun wo logon ko Namaz padhaaey , phir main Juma se peechey reh janey waley logon ko gharon samet aag laga dun .'' rawahu Muslim ."
1379,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs bila uzr Juma tarak kar dey to usey aisi kitab mein munafiq likh diya jata hai jo mitaai ja sakti hai na tabdeel ki ja sakti hai.'' aur baaz riwayaat mein teen jumon ka zikr hai.
1380,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah aur yoam aakhirat par eman rakhta ho jabkey mareez ya musafir ya aurat ya bacha ya mamlook na ho is par Juma ke roz Juma padhna farz hai. aur jo shakhs khel ya tijarat ki wajeh se la-parwaai bartey to Allah us se be niaz ho jata hai. jabkey Allah Taala be niaz qabil tareef hai.''
1381,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Juma ke din ghusl karey aur khub achi tarah jitni ho sakey safai karey aur tel lagaey aur apney ghar mein mojud khushbu lagaey, phir apney ghar se ( Juma ke liye ( rawana ho, aur) masjid mein aa kar) do bethey huey aadmiyon ko (unki jagah sey) na hataaey, phir jis qadr maqdoor ho Namaz padhey aur jab Imam khutba shuru kar dey to phir khamosh ho jaey to uskey us hazir aur doosrey Juma ke darmiyan waley gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain.'' Bukhari ."
1382,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ghusl karkey Juma ke liye aaye aur jitni muqaddar mein ho Namaz padhey. phir khutba mukammal honey tak khamosh rahey aur phir Imam ke sath Namaz padhey to uskey us aur doosrey Juma ke darmiyan waley aur mazeed teen din ke gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain.'' rawahu Muslim .
1383,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs wuzu karey aur achi tarah wuzu karkey Juma ke liye aaye aur khamoshi se ghor ke sath khutba suney to uskey us aur doosrey Juma ke darmiyan waley aur mazeed teen din ke gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain. aur jo kankariyon se khelta rahey to usney laghw kaam kya.'' rawahu Muslim."
1384,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Juma ka din hota hai to farishtey masjid ke darwazey par khadey ho jatey hain aur aaney walon ko tarteeb waar likhtey jatey hain. aur sab se pehley aaney wala us shakhs ki tarah (ajr w sawab paata) hai. jo oont ki qurbani karta hai. phir uskey baad wala us shakhs ki tarah hai jo gaaey ki qurbani karta hai. phir uskey baad wala bhed ki qurbani karney waley ki tarah . phir murghi aur phir uskey baad aaney wala aisey jaisey koi anda sadqa karey. jab Imam member par aa jata hai to wo apney rajister band kar detey hain aur ghor se khutba suntey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
1385,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum ne doran khutba kisi sath waley shakhs se ( bas itna ( keh diya ke khamosh ho jaao to tum ne laghw kaam kya. '' muttafaq aleh."
1386,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs Juma ke roz apney kisi bhai ko , uski jagah se us maqsad se na uthaey ke khud uski jagah par beth jaey balke wo yun kahey : wusat paida karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1387,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Juma ke din ghusl karkey , achcha libas pehan kar aur agar khushbu ho to usey laga kar Juma ke liye aaye aur logon ki gardanen na phalaangey . phir jis qadr Allah ne uskey muqaddar mein kya hai Namaz padhey. aur phir jab Imam (member par) aa jaey to Namaz mukammal ho janey tak khamoshi ikhtiyar karey to ye (sara ehtimam) uskey us aur sabiqa Juma ke beech honey waley gunahon ka kaffara hoga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1388,"Hazrat Aus bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Juma ke roz khub achi tarah ghusl karey, pedal chal kar awwal waqt masjid mein ja kar Imam ke qarib beth kar khub ghor se khutba suney aur us doran koi laghw kaam na karey to usey her qadam ke badley eik saal ke rozey aur eik saal ke qiyam ka sawab milta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja."
1389,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum mein se koi shakhs dorane-kaam pehenney waley kapdon ke ilawa, Juma ke din ke liye eik alag soot bana sakta ho to wo bana ley, is par koi harj nahin.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
1390,Hazrat Imam Malik ne usey Yahya bin Saeed se riwayat kya hai.
1391,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' zikr ( Juma (ke liye aao, Imam ke qarib ho kar betho, kyonkey aadmi door hota chala jata hai yahan tak ke uska jannat mein dakhila muakhkhar kar diya jata hai agar-che ke jannat mein chala jaeyga.''"
1392,"Hazrat Sehal bin Muaz bin Anas Johni (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Juma ke roz logon ki gardanen phalaangta hai to wo jahannam ki taraf pul banata hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1393,"Hazrat Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Juma ke roz dorane-khutba got maar kar bethney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
1394,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ko Juma ke roz (doran khutba) ungh aaye to wo apni jagah badal ley.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
1395,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya hai ke koi shakhs kisi shakhs ko uski jagah se utha kar khud wahan beth jaey. Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya, dorane-Juma? unhoney farmaya : Juma mein aur Juma ke ilawa bhi. muttafaq aleh."
1396,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen qism ke log Jume ke liye aatey hain : eik to wo jisney wahan pahunch kar laghw (fizul aur bekaar) harkat ki to usey us se bas yehi kuchh milta hai. doosra shakhs dua karney ke liye hazir hota hai. wo Allah se dua karta hai agar wo chahey to usey ata karey aur agar chahey to mana farma dey . jabkey teesra shakhs ghor se khutba sunta hai aur laghw (fizul aur bekaar) harkaat se bachta hai kisi musalman ki gardan phalaangtaa hai na kisi ko eza (takleef) pahunchata hai. to wo uskey liye sabiqa Juma aur mazeed teen din (kal das din) ke liye kaffara bin jata hai. aur ye isliye ke Allah Taala farmata hai : ''jo shakhs eik neki karta hai to usey uska das guna ajr milta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1397,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs dorane-khutba baat karta hai to wo kitaben uthaey huey gadhey ki tarah hai. aur jo shakhs usey kehta hai khamosh ho jaao to uska Juma nahin.''"
1398,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Sabaaq (Raziallahu anhu) mursal riwayat bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi Jume mein farmaya : ''musalmano ! Allah ne is din ko eid qarar diya hai. isliye tum achchhi tarah ghusl karo aur jis shakhs ke paas khushbu ho to wo usey laga ley , uskey liye koi muzaaeqa (haraj) nahin aur miswak karo.'' rawahu Malik aur ibne-Maja ."
1399,Aur yehi hadees ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se muttasil marwi (bayan) hai. rawahu ibne-Maja.
1400,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalmanon par haq hai ke wo Jume ke roz ghusl karen aur un mein se her koi apney ehle khana ki khushbu istimal karey. aur agar wo khushbu na paey to phir uskey liye pani hi khushbu hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1401,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zawal aaftaab ke waqt Juma padha kartey they. Bukhari.
1402,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad bayan kartey hain, ham Jume se pehley qailula kartey they na khana khatey they. muttafaq aleh."
1403,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab sardi ziyada hoti to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz (Juma) jaldi padh letey aur jab garmi ziyada hoti to Aap Namaz (Juma) thandey waqt mein padhtey they. Bukhari."
1404,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein Jume ke roz jab Imam member par beth jata tab pehli Azan kahi jati thi, isliye jab Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aaya. aur log ziyada ho gaey to unhoney maqame-zauraa par teesri Azan ka izafa farmaya. Bukhari."
1405,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume ke do khutbey diya kartey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke darmiyan bethtey they. aap Quran padhtey aur logon ko waaz aur nasihat farmatey they. Aap ka khutba aur Namaz mutwassit (darmiyaani) hoti thi. rawahu Muslim."
1406,"Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' beshak aadmi ki Namaz ka lamba hona aur uskey khutbey ka mukhtasar hona uskey faqeeh honey ki alamat hai. tum Namaz lambi karo aur khutba mukhtasar karo, aur beshak baaz bayan sahar angez hotey hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1407,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farmatey to Aap ki aankhen surkh ho jatin , aawaz buland ho jati aur ghussa shadeed ho jata, yahan tak ke ye kaifiyat ho jati goya aap kisi hamla-aawar lashkar se aagah kartey huey farma rahey hon : ''wo subah ya Sham tum par hamla-aawar honey wala hai.'' aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''mujhey (aisey waqt mein) mab-us kiya gaya hai (bheja gaya hai) ke main aur qiyamat is tarah hain.'' Aap darmiyani ungli aur angusht shahadat ko baham (aapas mein) milaate. rawahu Muslim."
1408,"Hazrat Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par ye aayat padhtey huey suna : ''wo (jahannami) kahengey aey Malik ! (darbaan dozakh) tera Rab hamein maut hi dey-dey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1409,"Hazrat Umme-Shaam bin Harisa bin Noman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Sura Qaaf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sun-sun kar yad ki, Aap her Juma jab member par logon se khitab farmatey to isey padha kartey they. rawahu Muslim."
1410,Hazrat Amr bin Hurais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jume ke din khitab farmaya to Aap ke sar par siyah pagdi thi jabkey aapney uskey dono kinarey (pallu) apney kandhon ke darmiyan latkaaey huey they. rawahu Muslim.
1411,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khutbe ke doran farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs Jume ke din dorane-khutbe mein masjid mein aaye to wo do mukhtasar rakatein padhey.'' rawahu Muslim."
1412,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Namaz (Juma) ki eik rakat pa ley to usney Namaz pa li.'' muttafaq aleh."
1413,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do khutbey diya kartey they. jab Aap member par chadhtey to Muazzan ke farigh honey tak member par bethtey they. phir khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmatey. phir beth jatey is doran aap koi baat na kartey, phir khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmatey. Bukhari."
1414,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par chadhtey to ham aap ki taraf mutawajjeh ho jatey they. Tirmizi aur unhoney farmaya : ham sirf Muhammad bin Fazal ki sanad se is hadees ko jantey hain, jabkey wo zaeef aur soo hifz (ghalat yaad) hai."
1415,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmaya kartey they phir Aap bethtey , phir khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmatey, agar koi shakhs tumhen ye bataey ke Aap beth kar khutba irshad farmaya kartey they to usney ghalat-bayani ki, Allah ki qism ! main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath do hazar se zayed namazein padh chuka hun. rawahu Muslim."
1416,Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo masjid mein dakhil huey to Abdur-Rehman bin Umme-Hakam beth kar khutba dey rahey they. unhoney (usey betha hua dekh kar) kaha : is khabees shakhs ko dekho ke wo beth kar khutba dey raha hai. jabkey Allah Taala ne farmaya hai : ''jab unhoney tijarat aur khel dekhi to wo us taraf bhag gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khadey huey chhod gaey.'' rawahu Muslim.
1417,"Hazrat Umara bin Rubiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Bashir bin Marwan ko member par apney dono haath uthaey huey dekha to unhoney farmaya : Allah un dono haathon ko tabah karey, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap sirf apney haath se is tarah ishara kiya kartey they. aur unhoney apni angusht shahadat se ishara kiya. rawahu Muslim."
1418,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume ke roz member par chadhey to farmaya : ''beth jaao.'' ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye baat suni to baab masjid (ke darwaaze) par hi beth gaey, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen dekha to farmaya : '' Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ! aagey aa jaao.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1419,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Jume ki eik rakat pa ley to wo uskey sath eik aur rakat mila ley , aur jiski dono rakatein faut ho jaeyn to wo chaar rakatein padhey.'' ya farmaya : ''zohar padhey.'' rawahu Dar-Qutni."
1420,"Hazrat Salim bin Abdullah bin umr apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : main Najad ki taraf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik ghazwe mein shareek tha, ham dushman ke muqabil saf aaraa huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein Namaz padhaaney ke liye khadey huey to eik jamaat aap ke sath khadi ho gaee aur eik jamaat dushman ke samney rahi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke sath shareek afrad ne eik rukoo kiya aur do sajdey kiye , phir wo log un logon ki jagah chaley gaey jinhon ne Namaz nahin padhi thi, wo aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke sath bhi eik rukoo aur do sajdey kiye. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam pher diya, un mein se har eik khada hua to unhoney apney taur par eik-eik rukoo kiya aur do-do sajdey kiye , aur Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kiya hai. aur unhoney izafa naqal kiya hai : jab khof us se ziyada ho to phir piyaada ya sawar qibla rukh ho ya qibla rukh na ho jis tarah mumkin hota Namaz padhtey. Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain. mera khayal hai ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi se riwayat kiya hai. Bukhari."
1421,"Hazrat Yazid bin Roomaan (Raziallahu anhu) , Saleh bin Khuwaat (Raziallahu anhu) se aur wo us shakhs se riwayat kartey hain jisney ghazwae-zatur-riqaa mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaze-khof ada ki : eik jamaat ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath saf banai jabkey dusri jamaat dushman ke samney thi, jo jamaat aap ke sath thi unko eik rakat padhaai , phir Aap khadey rahey, aur us jamaat ne apney taur par Namaz puri ki aur ja kar dushman ke samney saf bana li phir dusri jamaat aai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni Namaz ki baqi rakaat unhen padhaai , phir aap bethey rahey, aur unhoney apney taur par Namaz mukammal ki, phir aapney unke sath salam phera . Bukhari , Muslim . Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik dusri sanad se Qasim an Saleh bin Khuwaat an Sehal bin Abi Hashma ke wastey se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai. muttafaq aleh."
1422,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein rawana huey yahan tak ke ham zatur-riqaa pahunchey , Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai : jab ham koi saye-daar darkht paatey to usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye chhod diya kartey they, wo bayan kartey hain : eik mushrik aadmi aaya, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki talwaar darkht ke sath latak rahi thi. usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki talwaar pakad kar niyaam se nikali aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kehney laga : kya Aap mujh se dartey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin.'' usney kaha : Aap ko mujh se kon bachaeyga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah mujhey tum se bachaeyga .'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ne usey daraya dhamkaayaa to usney talwaar niyaam mein dal di aur usey (darkht ke sath hi) latka diya, raawi bayan kartey hain Namaz ke liye Azan di gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik jamaat ko do rakatein padhaeen, phir wo jamaat peechhey hat gaee aur aapney dusri jamaat ko do rakatein padhaeen, raawi bayan kartey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki chaar rakatein ho gaeen aur jinhon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi thi unki do do rakatein huin . muttafaq aleh."
1423,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaze-khof padhaai , ham ne aap ke peechhey do safein banaeen jabkey dushman hamarey aur qibla ke darmiyan tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne takbir kahi to ham sab ne bhi takbir kahi , phir aapney rukoo kiya to ham sab ne rukoo kiya, phir aapney rukoo se sar uthaya to ham sab ne bhi rukoo se sar uthaya , phir Aap aur aap ke sath wali saf sajde mein chali gaee , aur dusri saf dushman ke samney Sina taane rahi , jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sajdey kar chukey to aap ke sath wali saf khadi ho gaee to pichhli saf sajde ke liye jhuki phir wo sajda karkey khadey ho gaey to pichhli saf aagey badhi aur agli saf peechhey aa gaee , phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rukoo kiya aur ham sab ne bhi rukoo kiya, phir Aapney rukoo se sar uthaya to ham sab ne bhi rukoo se sar uthaya , phir Aap ke sath wali saf jo ke pehli rakaat mein peechhey thi, sajdey mein chaley gaey aur pichhli saf dushman ke samney Sina taane rahi. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke sath wali saf sajdey kar chuki to pichhli saf sajdey mein chali gaee , phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam phera , aur ham sab ne bhi salam phera. rawahu Muslim."
1424,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maqame-batan nakhl mein logon ko haalate-khof mein namaze-Zohar padhaai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik jamaat ko do rakatein padhaein , phir salam pher diya, phir dusri jamaat aai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen bhi do rakatein padhaein aur phir salam pher diya."
1425,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zajnan aur Asfan ke darmiyan padaaw dala to mushrekin ne kaha : Namaze-Asr unhen apney waliden aur apni aulad se bhi ziyada mehbub hai, isliye tum pukhta azm karkey eik hi baar un par hamla kar do, usi beech mein Jibrael (Alaihissalam) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye to unhoney Aap ko hukm diya ke aap apney Sahaba ko do hisson mein taqseem kar den, aap unhen is tarah Namaz padhaein gey ke eik jamaat unke peechhey khadi ho aur wo unka bachaaw karey aur unke aslaha ka khayal rakhey , isliye unki to eik rakat hogi , aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki do rakatein hongi. rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai."
1426,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-fitr aur eidul-azha ke liye eid gaah tashrif ley jatey to Aap sab se pehley Namaz padhtey , phir Namaz se farigh ho kar logon ke samney khadey ho kar waaz aur nasihat farmatey, log apni safon mein bethey rehtey , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ehkam jari kartey , agar koi lashkar rawana karna hota to usey rawana farmatey ya kisi chiz ke barey mein hukm farmana hota to aap uskey mutalliq hukm farmatey, phir Aap ghar tashrif ley jatey. muttafaq aleh."
1427,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eidain ki Namaz kaee martaba padhi jin mein Azan aur iqaamat nahin thi. rawahu Muslim."
1428,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) eidain ki Namaz khutbe se pehley padha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
1429,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya, kya aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaze-eid padhi hai? unhoney farmaya : haan , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Namaze-eid ke liye) tashrif laye to aapney Namaz padhaai , phir khutba irshad farmaya , aur unhoney Azan aur iqaamat ka zikr nahin kiya, phir Aap khawatin ke paas tashrif ley gaey to unhen waaz aur nasihat ki aur unhen sadqe ke mutalliq hukm farmaya , maine unhen dekha ke wo apney kanon aur apni gardanon se zewar utaar kar Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawaley kar rahi hain, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghar ki taraf chaley gaey. muttafaq aleh."
1430,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eidul-fitr ki Namaz do rakatein padhi , aapney un do rakaaton se pehley koi Namaz padhi na uskey baad. muttafaq aleh."
1431,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, hamein hukm diya gaya ke ham eidain ke roz haaiza aur parda nasheen aurton ko ghar se nikalen taake wo musalmanon ki jamaat (Namaz) aur dua mein shareek hon, lekin haaiza aurten jaey Namaz se door rahen , kisi khatoon ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! agar ham mein se kisi ke paas chadar na ho? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey sath wali usey apni chadar mein shareek kar ley.'' muttafaq aleh."
1432,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ayyaame-tashreeq (ke dinon) mein unke paas aaye to unke yahan do bachchiyaan daf baja rahi thin, aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : wo jang Bua'aas mein ansaar ke kaarnaamon ke barey mein geet ga rahi thin, jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney ooper eik kapda lapet rakha tha, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne un bachchiyon ko daantaa to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney chehrey se kapda utha kar farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar ! unhen chhod do ye to ayyaame eid (ka din) hain.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''Abu-Bakar ! her qom ki eid hoti hai aur ye hamari eid hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1433,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-fitr ke roz taaq adad (odd number) mein khajuren tanaawul farma (khaa) kar eid gaah jaya kartey they. Bukhari."
1434,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain. jab eid ka din hota to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (eid gaah aatey jatey) raasta tabdeel kiya kartey they. Bukhari.
1435,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, qurbani ke din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khitab kiya to farmaya : ''aaj ke din ham pehley Namaz padhengey phir wapis ja kar qurbani karengey. jisney aisey kiya to usney sunnat ke mutabiq kiya, aur jisney hamarey Namaz padhney se pehley qurbani kar li to wo gosht ki bakri hai (mehaz gosht khaney ke liye zibeh ki gaee hai) usney apney ehle aur ayaal ke liye jaldi zibeh kar li, is mein qurbani ka koi sawab nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
1436,"Hazrat Jundub bin Abdullah Bajli (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Namaze-eid se pehley qurbani kar ley to wo uski jagah dusri qurbani karey, aur jo shakhs Namaze-eid ke baad zibeh karey to usey Allah ke naam par zibeh karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1437,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Namaze-eid se pehley zibeh kar liya to usney mehaz apni zaat ki khatir zibeh kiya, aur jisney Namaze-eid ke baad zibeh kiya to uski qurbani mukammal hui aur usney musalmanon ke tareeqey ke mutabiq ki .'' muttafaq aleh."
1438,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) gaey aur oont eid gaah mein zibeh kiya kartey they. Bukhari."
1439,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to un (ehle-Madina) ke do din they jin mein wo khel kood kiya kartey they. aapney daryaft farmaya : ''ye do din kya hain?'' unhoney arz kiya : ham daure-jahiliyat mein in do dino mein khel kood kiya kartey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne unke badley main tumhen do behtareen din eidul-azha aur eidul-fitr ke ata farma diye hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1440,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-fitr ke roz kuchh kha kar eid gaah jaya kartey they aur eidul-azha ke roz Namaze-eid padhney ke baad kuchh khaya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi , ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
1441,"Hazrat Kasir bin Abdullah apney baap se aur wo (Kaseer) ke dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz eidain mein pehli rakaat mein qirat se pehley saat aur dusri rakaat mein qirat se pehley paanch takbeerein kahin. rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
1442,"Hazrat Jaafar bin Muhammad (Raziallahu anhu) mursal riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz eidain aur Namaze-istisqaa mein saat aur (doosri rakaat mein) paanch takbeerein kahin , unhoney khutbe se pehley Namaz padhi aur buland aawaz se qirat ki."
1443,"Hazrat Saeed bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) aur Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-azha aur eidul-fitr ki namazon mein kaisey takbir kaha kartey they? to Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Aap Namaze-janaza ki takbeeron ki tarah chaar takbeerein kaha kartey they. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : inhoney sach farmaya."
1444,Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eid ke roz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik kamaan pesh ki gaee to aapney is par tek laga kar khutba irshad farmaya.
1445,Hazrat Ata (Raziallahu anhu) mursal riwayat bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab khutba irshad farmatey to Aap apney chhotey neze par tek lagatey they.
1446,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine eid ke roz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi , to aapney khutbe se pehley Azan aur iqaamat ke baghair Namaz padhi, jab aap Namaz padh chukey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) par tek laga kar khadey huye, Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki, logon ko waaz aur nasihat ki, unhen yad dahani karaai , aur apni itaat ki targheeb di, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath khawatin ki taraf gaey to unhen Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karney ka hukm farmaya aur waaz aur nasihat ki aur yaad-dahani karaai. rawahu Nasai."
1447,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz eid ke liye tashrif ley jatey to aap eik raastey se jatey aur doosrey raastey se wapis aatey. rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi ."
1448,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eid ke roz barish ho gaee to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Namaz eid masjid mein padhaai.
1449,Hazrat Abul-Huwairis (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) ke naam Najran khat likha ke eidul-azha ki Namaz jaldi padho aur eidul-fitr ki Namaz der se padho aur logon ko waaz w nasihat karo.
1450,"Hazrat abu-Umair bin Anas apney chacha se riwayat kartey hain, jinhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka sahabi honey ka sharf hasil hai, ke kuch Sawar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney kaha : ham gawahi detey hain ke ham ne kal chaand dekha tha, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen roza iftaar karney ka hukm farmaya, aur unhen farmaya ke kal eidgaah pahunchein. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
1451,"Hazrat ibne-Juraij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Ata (Raziallahu anhu) ne ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke wastey se mujhey bataya , unhoney farmaya : eidul-fitr aur eidul-azha ke liye Azan nahin kahi jati thi. phir maine kuchh muddat baad Ata se is barey mein daryaft kiya, to unhoney mujhey batatey huey kaha : Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya ke Namaz eidul-fitr ke liye , Imam ke aaney se pehley ya uskey aaney ke baad koi Azan nahin hoti thi, Azan aur iqaamat wali koi chiz hi nahin thi, us roz Azan thi na iqaamat. rawahu Muslim."
1452,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-azha aur eidul-fitr ke liye tashrif latey to Aap sab se pehley Namaz padhtey, jab Aap Namaz padh letey to aap khadey ho kar logon ki taraf mutawajjeh hotey , jabkey log apni apni jagah par bethey hotey they, agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne koi lashkar bhejna hota to logon se uska tazkira farmatey, ya uskey ilawa koi aur zarurat hoti to Aap uskey mutalliq unhen hukm farmatey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''sadqa karo, sadqa karo, sadqa karo.'' aur khawatin sab se ziyada sadqa kiya karti thin, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghar tashrif ley jatey , ye mamool aisey hi raha yahan tak ke Marwan bin Hakam ka daure-hukoomat aaya to main Marwan ki kamar par haath rakh kar Namaze-eid ke liye rawana hua yahan tak ke ham eid gaah pahunch gaey, wahan dekha ke Kasir bin Salat (Raziallahu anhu) ne garey aur inton se eik member tayyar kar rakha tha, Marwan mujh se apna haath khinch raha tha goya wo mujhey member ki taraf ley jana chahta tha jabkey main usey Namaz ki taraf lana chahta tha, jab maine uska ye azm dekha to maine kaha : Namaz se ibtida (shuruat) karna kahan chala gaya? usney kaha : nahin, Abu-Saeed ! jaisa ke aap jantey hain wo tariqa tark ho chuka , maine kaha : hergiz nahin, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! merey ilm ke mutabiq tum khair aur bhalai par nahin ho, unhoney teen martaba aisey hi farmaya phir wo member se door chaley gaey. rawahu Muslim."
1453,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ''Bismillahi wallahu-akbar '' padh kar apney daste-mubarak se chitkabrey , seengon waley do mendhey zibeh kiye. raawi bayan kartey hain, maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke Aapney unke pehlu par apna qadam rakha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) padh rahey they : (Bismillahi wallahu-akbar). muttafaq aleh."
1454,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne seengon wala mendhaa laney ka hukm farmaya jiski taangein , pet aur aankhen siyah thin, usey Aap ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya taake aap usey qurban karen, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha ! chhuri laao.'' phir farmaya : ''usey pathar par tez karo.'' maine aisey hi kiya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chhuri pakad kar mendhey ko litaya aur zibeh karney ka irada farmaya to yun dua ki : ''Allah ke naam par, aey Allah ! isey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), aale Muhammad aur ummate Muhammad ki taraf se qubul farma.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey zibeh kiya. rawahu Muslim."
1455,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sirf do daant wala janwer zibeh karo, agar tumhen (us ka milna) mushkil ho to phir eik saal ka mendhaa zibeh karo.'' rawahu Muslim."
1456,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen kuchh bakriyan Deen taake wo qurbani ke liye Aap ke Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) mein taqseem kar di jaeyn. (taqseem ke baad) bakri ka eik saal ka bachcha baqi reh gaya to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska tazkira kiya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum usey zibeh kar lo.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein : maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! merey hissey mein jazaa (eik saal se zayed umr ka janwer) aaya hai, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum usey zibeh kar lo.'' muttafaq aleh."
1457,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) gaey aur oont eid gaah mein zibeh kiya kartey they. Bukhari."
1458,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gaaey aur oont saat saat aadmiyon ki taraf se qurbani ke liye kafi hai.'' Muslim , Abu-Dawood aur alfaze-hadees Abu-Dawood ke hain. rawahu Muslim w Abu-Dawood."
1459,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab zul-hijja ka ashra shuru ho jaey aur tum mein se koi qurbani karney ka irada rakhta ho to wo apney baalon aur jild se koi chiz na utarey.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''wo apney baal katwaaey na nakhun.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''jo shakhs Zul-hijja ka chaand dekh ley aur wo qurbani karney ka irada rakhta ho to wo apney baal katwaaey na nakhun.'' rawahu Muslim."
1460,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''baqi dino mein kiye gaey amal ki nisbat un das dinon (dinon) mein kiya gaya amal Allah ko intehai pasandida hai.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki raah mein jihad karna bhi itna pasandida nahin? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jihad bhi nahin, siwaey iske ke koi shakhs apney maal aur jaan ke sath jihad ke liye jaey aur uski koi chiz wapis na aaye.'' Bukhari."
1461,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eidul-azha ke roz seengon waley chitkabrey do khassi mendhey zibeh kiye , jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen qibla rukh kiya to ye dua padhi : ''be-shak maine Ibrahim jo ke yaksoo they ke Deen par hotey huey apney chehrey ko us zaat ki taraf mutawajjeh kiya jisney zamin aur aasman ko paida farmaya , aur main mushrikon mein se nahin hun, be-shak meri Namaz , meri qurbani , mera jeena aur mera marna Allah ke liye hai jo ke tamam jahano ka parwardigar hai, uska koi shareek nahin, mujhey isi ka hukm diya gaya hai, aur main musalmanon (itaat guzaaron) mein se hun, aey Allah ! (ye qurbani ka janwer) teri ata hai aur terey hi liye hai, isey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur unki ummat ki taraf se qubul farma , Allah ke naam se aur Allah bahut bada hai.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zibeh farmaya. Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja , Darmi . aur Ahmed, Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney daste Mubarak se zibeh kiya, aur ye dua padhi : ''Allah ke naam sey, aur Allah sab se bada hai, aey Allah ! ye meri aur meri ummat ke us shakhs ki taraf se hai jisney qurbani nahin ki.''"
1462,"Hazrat Hanash (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko do mendhey zibeh kartey huey dekha to maine un se daryaft kiya, ye kya hai? unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya tha ke main unki taraf se qurbani karun, so mein unki taraf se qurbani karta hun. Abu-Dawood . aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kiya hai."
1463,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hukm farmaya ke ham (qurbani ke janwer ki) aankh aur kaan ghor se dekh liya karen, aur ham aisa janwer zibeh na karen jis ka kaan samney se kataa ho ya peechhey se kataa ho, aur is mein koi surakh tak na ho. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai , Darmi , ibne-Maja aur ibne-Maja ki riwayat (al-izn) tak khatam ho jati hai."
1464,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein aisey janwer ki qurbani karney se mana farmaya jis ka seeng tootaa hua ho ya uska kaan kataa hua ho. rawahu ibne-Maja."
1465,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya ke kin janweron ki qurbani mein ehtiyat karni chahiye? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney haath ke isharay se chaar ka zikr farmaya : ''aisa langda jis ka langdaapan zahir ho, aisa kaanaa jis ka kaanaa pan zahir ho, mareez jis ka mareez hona zahir ho, aur laaghir jiski haddiyon mein goodaa na ho.'' rawahu Malik, Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi ."
1466,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) seengon wala, mota taza sehat mand aur kaali aakhon wala, siyah munh wala aur kaali taangon wala mendhaa qurbani kiya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
1467,"Hazrat bano Sulaim qabiley se talluq rakhney waley Majaashea' (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''jahan do daant waley bakrey ki qurbani kifaayat karti hai wahan eik saal ke mendhey ki qurbani bhi kifaayat karti hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
1468,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''eik saal ke mendhey ki qurbani achhi qurbani hai.''"
1469,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath safar kar rahey they ke eidul-azha aa gaee to ham gaaey mein saat afrad shareek huey aur oont mein das . Tirmizi, Nasai , ibne-Maja , Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1470,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qurbani ke din , ibne-Adam ka qurbani karna Allah ko intehai mehbub hai, be-shak wo (janwer) roze-qiyamat apney seengon , baalon , aur khuron samet aaeyga , be-shak qurbani ke janwer ka khoon zamin par girney se pehley hi Allah ke yahan qubul ho jata hai, isliye tum khush dili se qurbani kiya karo.''"
1471,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zul-hijja ke das dino ki ibadat Allah ko intehai mehbub hai is ashre ke har din ke rozey ka sawab saal bhar ke rozon aur iski har raat ka qiyam , shabbe-qadr ke qiyam ke barabar hai.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : iski sanad zaeef hai."
1472,"Hazrat Jundub bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaze eidul-azha ada ki, aapney sirf Namaz padh kar salam hi phera tha (abhi khutba irshad nahin farmaya tha) ke aapney qurbani ka gosht dekha jisey aap ke Namaz padhney se pehley hi zibeh kar diya gaya tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (ye dekh kar) farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne hamarey Namaz padhney se pehley janwer zibeh kiya hai wo iski jagah doosra janwer zibeh karey.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ke din Namaz padhaai , phir khutba irshad farmaya , phir janwer zibeh kiya, aur farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne hamarey Namaz padhney se pehley qurbani ki hai. wo uski jagah eik aur janwer zibeh karey, aur jisney janwer zibeh nahin kiya, wo Allah ke naam par janwer zibeh karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1473,Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : qurbani ke din ke do din baad tak qurbani karna jayez hai. rawahu Malik.
1474,Hazrat Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi isi tarah ki riwayat mujhey pahunchti hai. rawahu Malik.
1475,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madina mein das saal qiyam farmaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qurbani kartey rahey."
1476,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye qurbani kiya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey baap Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki sunnat hai.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey liye is mein kya (sawab) hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''har baal ke badley eik neki.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! oon ke barey mein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''oon ke har reshey par eik neki.''"
1477,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''faraa' koi chiz hai na Ateera.''  ''faraa' '' oont ke pehley bachchey ko kehtey hain jisey mushrekin apney buton ke naam par zibeh kiya kartey they, jabkey ''Ateera'' us bakri ko kehtey hain jiski rajab ke mahiney mein qurbani ki jati thi. muttafaq aleh."
1478,"Hazrat Mikhnaf bin Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Arafat mein waquf kiye huey they, maine wahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''logo ! har ehle-khana  par her saal eik qurbani karna aur eik Ateera wajib hai. kya tum jantey ho Ateera kya hai? wohi jisey tum rajbiya kehtey ho.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai , ibne-Maja , aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib , zaeef snad mein se hai. Imam Abu-Dawood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Ateera mansookh ho chuka hai."
1479,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main is ummat ke liye Azahaa ke din ko Eid qarar dun.'' kisi aadmi ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn agar main doodh deney wali bakri , jo ke mujhey kisi ne Atiya ki hai, ke siwa koi janwer na paaon to kya main usey zibeh kar dun? farmaya : ''nahin, lekin tum (eid ke roz) apney baal aur nakhun ktaaw, munchhein katrwaao aur zere-naaf baal moond lo , Allah ke yahan ye tumhari mukammal qurbani hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
1480,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein Suraj girahan hua to aapney manadi karney waley ko bheja ke wo yun aelan karey : Namaz ke liye jama ho jaao, (jab log jama ho gaey) aap aagey badhey aur do rakaaton mein chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdey kiye , Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine is se lamba rukoo aur sujood kabhi nahin dekha. muttafaq aleh."
1481,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaze-khusoof mein buland aawaz se qirat farmaai . muttafaq aleh."
1482,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein Suraj girahan hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sahaba kiram ke sath Namaz padhi to aapney taqriban Sura Baqra ki qirat ke barabar taweel qiyam farmaya, phir taweel rukoo farmaya , phir khadey huey to aapney taweel qiyam farmaya lekin wo pehley qiyam se kam tha, phir aapney taweel rukoo farmaya, lekin ye pehley rukoo se kam tha, phir khadey huye, phir sajda kiya, phir khadey huey to aapney taweel qiyam farmaya , jabkey wo pehley qiyam se kam tha, phir taweel rukoo farmaya , lekin wo pehley rukoo se kam tha, phir khadey huey to taweel qiyam farmaya lekin wo pehley qiyam se kam tha, phir taweel rukoo farmaya lekin wo pehley rukoo se kam tha, phir sajda kiya, phir jab Namaz se farigh huey to Suraj girahan khatam ho chuka tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak aaftaab aur maahtaab (suraj aur chaand) Allah ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain, ye kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki wajeh se nahin gahnaatey, jab tum , dekho to Allah ka zikr karo.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham ne aap ko dekha ke jaisey Aap apni isi jagah se koi chiz pakadna chahtey hain. phir ham ne aap ko ultey paaon wapis aatey huey dekha, aapney farmaya : ''maine jannat dekhi , maine us se angooron ka guchchaa lena chaha , agar main usey ley leta to tum rehti duniya tak usey khatey rehtey, aur maine jahannam dekhi , maine aaj ke din ki tarah ka khofnak manzar kabhi nahin dekha, aur maine wahan aksariyat aurton ki dekhi.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye kyon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unki nashukri ki wajeh se .'' arz kiya gaya, kya wo Allah ki nashukri karti hain? farmaya : ''shohar ki nashukri karti hain, wo (khaawind ke) ehsan ki nashukri karti hain, agar tum ne un mein se kisi se zindagi bhar husne-suluk kiya ho, phir agar wo tumhari taraf se koi nagawar chiz dekh ley to wo kaheygi : maine to tumhari taraf se kabhi koi khair dekhi hi nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
1483,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki tarah jaisi marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney farmaya : phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sajda kiya, to sajdon ko lamba kiya, phir Aap Namaz se farigh huey to Suraj girahan khatam ho chuka tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khutba irshad farmaya Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki, farmaya : ''aaftaab aur maahtaab (suraj aur chaand) Allah ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain.'' ye kisi ki maut aur hayaat se nahin gahnaaey, isliye jab tum ye dekho to Allah se duayen karo, uski kibriyaai (badhaaee) bayan karo, Namaz padho aur sadqa karo.'' phir farmaya : ''Ummate-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! Allah ki qism ! Allah se badh kar koi ghairat mand nahin hai ke uska banda ya uski londi zina karey. ummate-Muhammad ! Allah ki qism ! agar tum is baat ko jaan lo jo main janta hun, to tum bahut hi kam hanso aur bahut ziyada ro'oo.'' muttafaq aleh."
1484,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Suraj girahan hua to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghabrahat ke aalim mein khadey huey jaisey qiyamat aa gaee ho, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein tashrif laye aur is qadr qiyam aur rukoo aur sajdon ko taweel karkey Namaz padhi ke maine aap ko aisey kartey huey kabhi nahin dekha, aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye nishaniyan jo Allah bhejta hai ye kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki wajeh se nahin hoten, lekin unke zariey Allah apney bandon ko darata hai, jab tum is tarah ki koi chiz dekho to tum uskey zikr , us se dua karney aur us se maghfirat talab karney ki taraf tawajjoh karo (aur uski panah hasil karo).'' muttafaq aleh."
1485,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke bete Ibrahim ki wafat ke roz , Suraj girahan hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sahaba ko chhe rukoo aur chaar sajdon ke sath (do rakaat) Namaz padhaai. rawahu Muslim."
1486,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Suraj girahan hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aath rukoo aur chaar sajdon ke sath Namaz padhaai. rawahu Muslim."
1487,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi isi tarah marwi (bayan) hai. rawahu Muslim.
1488,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zindagi mein Madina mein teer andazi kar raha tha ke achcha Suraj girahan hua, maine wo teer (udhar hi) phenkey aur kaha : Allah ki qism main dekhunga ke Suraj girahan ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kya naee taalim irshad farmatey hain, wo bayan kartey hain, main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to dekha ke aap haath uthaey khadey Namaz padh rahey hain, aap tasbih aur tahleel, takbir aur tahmeed aur dua karney lagey, yahan tak ke Suraj girahan khatam ho gaya to aapney do suraten padhein aur do rakatein ada farmaeen. Sahih Muslim aur Sharahus-sunnah mein Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai jabkey Masaabeh ke nuskhon mein Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai. (rawahu Muslim والبغوی فی shareh (dar) السنہ)."
1489,"Hazrat Asma binte-Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Suraj girahan ke moqe par ghulam azad karney ka hukm farmaya. Bukhari."
1490,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Suraj girahan ke moqe par hamein Namaz padhaai to hamen aap ki aawaz sunai nahin deti thi. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
1491,"Hazrat Ikrima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko bataya gaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki falan zauja (biwi) mohtarma wafat pa gaee hain. to wo (ye sun kar) fauran sajda rez ho gaey, un se arz kiya gaya, aap is waqt sajda kartey hain? unhoney bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum koi nishani dekho to sajda karo.'' aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaaje mutah'raat (biwiyon) ke faut ho janey se badi nishani kon si ho sakti hai? rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
1492,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein Suraj girahan hua to aapney Sahaba ko Namaz padhaai isliye aapney (pehli rakaat mein) lambi sura tilawat farmaai , paanch rukoo aur do sajdey kiye , phir dusri rakaat ke liye khadey huey to is mein bhi lambi sura tilawat farmaai , paanch rukoo aur do sajdey kiye , phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qibla rukh beth kar dua kartey rahey yahan tak ke Suraj girahan khatam ho gaya."
1493,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein Suraj girahan hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do do rakatein padhtey aur (do rakaat Namaz padhney ke baad) Suraj girahan ke mutalliq poochhtey yahan tak ke Suraj girahan khatam ho gaya. Abu-Dawood aur Nasai ki riwayat mein hai ke jab Suraj girahan hua to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamari Namaz ki tarah hamein Namaz padhaai , aap rukoo aur sujood farmatey they aur Nasai ki dusri riwayat mein hai : Suraj girahan lag chuka to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jaldi ke sath masjid mein tashrif laye, Namaz padhaai yahan tak ke Suraj girahan khatam ho gaya, phir farmaya : ''ehle jahiliyat kaha kartey they : Suraj aur chaand ehle zamin ki kisi azeem shakhsiyat ki wafat par hi gahnaatey hain, jabkey Suraj aur chaand kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki wajeh se nahin gahnaatey , balke wo to Allah ki makhluq hain, Allah apni makhluq mein jo chahey so karta hai. un dono mein se jo bhi gahanaa jaey to Namaz padho yahan tak ke wo (girahan) khatam ho jaey ya Allah koi naya maamla zahir farma dey.''"
1494,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko koi khushi ka maamla darpesh hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ka shukr ada karney ke liye sajda rez ho jaya kartey they. Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1495,"Hazrat Abu-Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi chhotey se qad waley (boney) shakhs ko dekha to Aap sajda rez ho gaey. Daarqutni ne usey mursal riwayat kiya hai, aur Sharahus-sunnah mein Masaabeeh ke alfaz hain."
1496,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Madina janey ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Makka se rawana huey . jab ham azwzaa ke qarib pahunchey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sawari se nichey utrey , kuchh der tak haath utha kar khadey dua kartey rahey, phir sajda-rez ho gaey, phir kafi der baad aap khadey huey aur kuchh der tak haath uthaey aur phir sajda-rez ho gaey, phir kafi der baad khadey huey aur kuchh der tak haath uthaey aur phir sajda-rez ho gaey, aapney farmaya : ''maine apney Rab se darkhast ki aur apni ummat ke liye shafaat ki to usney mujhey meri ummat ke barey main eik tihai shafaat ki ijazat ata farmaee, to main apney Rab ka shukr ada karney ke liye apney Rab ke huzur sajda-rez ho gaya, phir maine sar uthaya to apni ummat ke liye apney Rab se sawal kiya to usney mazeed meri eik tihai ummat ki shafaat ki mujhey ijazat ata farmaee to main shukr ke taur par apney Rab ke huzur sajda-rez ho gaya, phir maine sar uthaya to maine apni ummat ke liye apney Rab se darkhast ki to usney aakhiri tihai ki shafaat ki mujhey ijazat ata farmaee to main apney Rab ka shukr ada karney ke liye uskey huzur sajda-rez ho gaya.''"
1497,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) barish talab karney ke liye logon ke sath eid gaah ki taraf tashrif laye to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do rakaat Namaz padhaai , jis mein buland aawaz se qirat ki, Aap qibla rukh ho kar haath utha kar dua kartey rahey, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qibla rukh huey to apni chadar ko palat liya. muttafaq aleh."
1498,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sirf barish talab karney ke moqe par haath utha kar dua kiya kartey they. Aap unhen is qadr uthatey ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aaney lagti. muttafaq aleh."
1499,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne barish talab ki to aapney haathon ki pusht ko aasman ki taraf karkey ( halaat ki tabdili (ka ishara kya. rawahu Muslim .
1500,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab barish dekhtey to farmatey : ''aey Allah ! nafa mand barish barsa.'' Bukhari."
1501,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, ke barish honey lagi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney jism se kuch kapda uthaya yahan tak ke kuch qatrey wahan girey to ham ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! aapney aisey kyon kya? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kyonkey ye abhi naee naee apney rab se aai hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1502,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eid gaah tashrif laye to aapney barish talab ki, aur jis waqt qibla rukh huey to apni chadar palti, aapney uskey daain kinarey ko apney baain kandhey par aur baain kinarey ko apney daain kandhey par kar liya, phir Allah se dua ki . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1503,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhoney bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne barish ke liye dua ki to aap par kaali chadar thi, aapney uskey nichley hissey ko ooper karna chaha , lekin bhari honey par aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey apney kandhon par hi badal liya . rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood ."
1504,"Hazrat Umer maula abi Laham (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Zaura ke qarib maqam ehjaarizzait ke paas khadey hokar barish talab kartey huey dekha, aap apney chehrey ke samney haath buland kiye huey barish ke liye dua kar rahey they, aur wo (haath) aap ke sar se buland nahin they. Abu-Dawood . Imam Tirmizi aur Imam Nasai ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
1505,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) puraney kapdey pehan kar , tawazeh ikhtiyar karkey khushu w khuzoo aur aajizi kartey huey barish talab karney ke liye nikley. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja."
1506,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) barish talab kartey to ye dua padha kartey they : ''aey Allah ! apney bandon aur janweron ko sairab farma, apni rehmat ko aam kar dey aur apney murda shehron ko zindagi ata farma.''"
1507,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko haath ooper utha kar ye dua kartey huey dekha : ''aey Allah ! hamen pani pila , ham par aisi barish nazil farma jo hamari piyas bujha dey, halki phuwaarein bin kar ghalla uganey wali, nafa deney wali, nuqsan pahunchaney wali na ho, jald aaney wali ho, der laganey wali na ho.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : fauran hi aasman par badal chha gaey . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1508,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Sahaba ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se qehat saali ki shikayat ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne member ka hukm farmaya to usey aap ke liye eidgaah mein rakh diya gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sahaba se eik moayan din ka wada farmaya, wo us roz bahar nikley, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain jab Suraj ka kinara zahir hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi tashrif ley gaey, aap member par beth gaey Allah ki kibriyaai aur hamd bayan ki, phir farmaya : ''tum ne apney ilaqon ki qehat-saali aur bar-waqt baarishon ke na honey ki shikayat ki hai, Allah ne tumhen hukm diya hai ke tum us se dua karo aur usney dua ki qubuliyat ka tum se wada kar rakha hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yun dua ki : '' her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jo tamam jahano ka rab hai, jo bahut meharban nihayat rehem wala, roze-jaza ka Malik hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo jo chahta hai kar guzarta hai, aey Allah! to Allah hai, terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, to ghani hai aur ham fuqara, ham par barish barsa , aur jo to ( barish ( nazil farmaai usey hamarey liye eik muddat tak quwat aur (maqasid tak) pahunchney ka zaria bana.'' phir aapney haath buland kiye aur unhen buland kartey rahey yahan tak ke aap ke baghlon ki safedi nazar aaney lagi, phir aapney logon ki taraf apni peeth kar di aur apni chadar palti, aur aapney abhi tak haath uthaey rakhey, phir logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye, aur nichey utar kar do rakatein padhin, pas Allah ne badal ki eik tukdi bheji, garaj chamak paida hui to phir Allah ke hukm se barish honey lagi, aap abhi apni masjid tak tashrif nahin laye they ke naaley bahney lagey jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen apni jhonpdiyon ki taraf dodtey huey dekha to aap hansney lagey yahan tak ke aap ki daadhein nazar aaney lagin. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah her chiz par qadir hai aur be-shak main Allah ka banda aur uska Rasool hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1509,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) qehat saali ka shikar hotey to Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib ke zariey barish talab kartey they aur yun arz kartey : aey Allah ! ham terey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki dua ke zariey barish talab kartey they to ham par barish barsata tha, aur ab ham terey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chacha ki dua ke wasila se barish talab kartey hain, to ham par barish nazil farma, chunanche barish honey lagti. Bukhari."
1510,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) mein se eik Nabi logon ke sath barish talab karney ke liye rawana huey unhoney achcha dekha ke eik chewnti apni naheef si taangein aasman ki taraf ooper uthaey huey ( dua kar rahi ( hai pas us Nabi (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : wapis palat jaao , us chewnti ki wajeh se tumhari dua qubul ho gaee hai.'' rawahu Dar-Qutni ."
1511,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''baade-Sabaa ke zariey meri nusrat ki gaee jabkey Qome-Aad baad Zabur (maghribi hawa) ke zariey halak kar di gaee .'' muttafaq aleh."
1512,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi is tarah hanstay huey nahin dekha ke aap ke galey ka kawwa nazar aa jaey aap to bas tabassum farmaya kartey they, jab aap hawa ya aandhi dekhtey to uskey ( khof ke) asraat aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chehrey par numaya ho jatey they. muttafaq aleh."
1513,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab tez aandhi chalti to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua padha kartey they : ''aey Allah main iski khair ka is mein jo khair hai uska aur uskey sath jo bheja gaya hai uski khair ka tujh se sawal karta hun aur main uskey shar se is mein jo shar hai uska aur jo uskey sath bheja gaya hai uskey shar ki tujh se panah chahta hun.'' aur jab aasman par barish ke aasaar zahir hotey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka rang tabdeel ho jata, aap kabhi ghar se bahar aatey aur kabhi andar jatey, kabhi aagey aatey aur kabhi peechey hat-tey, aur jab barish ho jati to phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se khof zaayel hota, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unki ye keyfiyat pehchan kar aap se puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Aaisha ! shayad ke ye aisey na ho jaisey qome-Aad ne kaha tha : jab unhoney azab ko abr ki surat mein apney maidaanon ke samney aatey dekha to kehney lagey : ye badal hai jo ham par barsega.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : jab aap badal dekhtey to farmatey : ''usey rehmat bana dey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1514,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ghaib ki kunjiyan paanch hain.'' phir aapney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : '' be-shak qiyamat ka ilm usi ke paas hai aur wohi barish barsata hai,'' Bukhari ."
1515,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qehat saali (sukha) ye nahin hai ke barish na ho, balke qehat saali ye hai ke tum par baar-baar bahut ziyada barish to ho lekin zamin koi chiz na ugaey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1516,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' hawa, Allah ki rehmat hai kabhi ye rehmat ke sath aati hai aur kabhi ye azab ke sath, pas usey bura bhala na kaho, aur uski khair ke mutalliq darkhast karo aur uskey shar se ( Allah Taala ki) panah talab karo . rawahu Shafai w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi ."
1517,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas hawa ko maloon kaha to aapney farmaya : ''hawa ko laan-taan na karo kyonkey wo to hukm ki paband hai, jo shakhs kisi aisi chiz par lanat bhejna hai jo uski ehle nahin to phir lanat us shakhs par lot aati hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1518,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hawa ko bura bhala na kaho , pas jab tum nagawar chiz dekho, to yun kaho : aey Allah! be-shak ham us hua ki khair, is mein mojud khair, us chiz ki khair ka tujh se sawal kartey hain jis ka usey hukm diya gaya hai. ham uskey shar, is mein mojud shar aur jis chiz ka usey hukm diya gaya, uskey shar se teri panah chahtey hain.''"
1519,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain jab kabhi bhi hua chalti to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney ghutnon ke bal beth kar yun dua kartey : ''aey Allah! usey rehmat bana, usey azab na bana, aey Allah! usey baade-rehmat bana aur usey baaise-azab hawa na bana.'' ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ki kitab mein hai : ''ham ne un par eik sakht aandhi bheji.'' aur : ''ham ne un par eik sakht aandhi bheji.'' ''ham ne abr uthaney wali huwayen bhejin.'' aur : ''wo tumhen khushkhabri sunaney ke liye huwayen bhejna hai.''"
1520,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aasman par badal dekhtey to aap apna kaam kaaj chhod kar uski taraf mutawajjeh ho jatey aur dua farmatey : ''aey Allah! main is mein mojud shar mein teri panah chahta hun.'' agar wo usey door kar deta to aap Allah ki hamd w sana bayan kartey, aur agar barish hoti to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua farmatey : ''aey Allah! hamen nafa-mand sairaabi ata farma.'' Abu-Dawud, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Shafai. alfaz Imam Shafai (Raziallahu anhu) ke hain. ."
1521,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) garaj aur kadak ki aawaz suntey to dua farmatey they : ''aey Allah! hamen apney ghazab se qatl na karna na apney azab se halak karna aur hamen us se pehley hi aafiyat ata farmana.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
1522,Hazrat Aamir bin Abdullah bin Zuber se riwayat hai ke jab wo garaj ki aawaz suntey to baat-cheet tarak kar detey aur farmatey : garaj aur farishtey uskey khof se uski hamd bayan kartey hain. rawahu Malik.
